\id 1SA
\h 1 Ṣamwil
\toc1 1 Ṣamwil
\toc2 1 Ṣamwil
\toc3 1 Ṣm.
\mt1 1 Ṣamwil
\c 1
\s1 Taẓaǧit n Ḥanna
\m 
\v 1 Tuɣa din ijj n weryaz zi Ramatayim-Ṣufim, zeg idurar n Ifrayim, qqaren as Ilqana, mmis n Yaruḥam, mmis n Alihu, mmis n Tuḥu, mmis n Ṣuf, ijj n \add weryaz\add* zi Ifrayim. \x ◘ \xo 1:1 \xt 1 Im. 6:11, 12\x*
\v 2 Netta tuɣa ɣares tnayen n temɣarin. Icten qqaren as Ḥanna u tenneɣnit qqaren as Faninna. Faninna tuɣa ɣares iḥenjiren, \add maca\add* Ḥanna war ɣares tuɣi bu iḥenjiren.
\v 3 Aryaz-a tuɣa ittgeɛɛad aseggʷas x useggʷas zi tendint nnes ḥima ad isjed u ad iqeddem tiɣarṣa i SIDI n řɛeskarat \add ɣar Taddart n SIDI\add* di Cilu. Dinni tuɣa tnayen n iḥenjiren n Ɛali, Ḥufni d Finaḥas. Nitni d ikehhanen n SIDI. \x ◘ \xo 1:3 \xt Uf. 23:14; Aɛwd. 16:16. \x*
\m 
\v 4 Deg wass řami dd-yiwi Ilqana taɣarṣt, imsar aqa iwca tiseqqar \add n tɣarṣt\add* i temɣart nnes Faninna u i marra iḥenjiren nnes d tḥenjirin nnes,
\v 5 \add maca\add* i Ḥanna iwca as tnayen n tseqqar, maɣar netta tuɣa ittexs Ḥanna, waxxa SIDI tuɣa ibelleɛ as řemřawet.
\v 6 Taɣrimt nnes tuɣa tseɛɛar i-tt aṭṭas maḥend ad tt tessfugem, minzi SIDI tuɣa ibelleɛ as řemřawet.
\m 
\v 7 Ammu i igga \add Ilqana\add* aseggʷas x useggʷas. Uca meřmi ma tᵉttgeɛɛed \add Ḥanna akides\add* ɣar Taddart n SIDI, tseɛɛar i-tt \add Faninna\add* u nettat tru, war tecci walu.
\v 8 \add Xenni\add* inna aryaz nnes Ilqana: “Ḥanna, mayemmi tᵉttrud, mayemmi war tᵉttᵉtted ca u mayemmi uř nnem icḍen? Ma necc war d am cniɣ x ɛecra n iḥenjiren?” \x ◘ \xo 1:8 \xt Raɛ. 4:15. \x*
\m 
\v 9 \add Deg ijj n wass\add*, awarni umi tecca u teswa di Cilu, tekkar Ḥanna. Tuɣa akehhan Ɛali iqqim x řkursi ɣar tefřawt \add n uɣezḍis n tewwart\add* n Zzawect n SIDI.
\v 10 \add Tuɣa\add* řeɛmar \add n Ḥanna\add* yarzeg, tᵉẓẓuǧ ɣar SIDI, tru aṭṭas.
\v 11 Nettat tegga ijj n lwaɛd, tenna: “\add A\add*, SIDI n řɛeskarat, mařa Cek texzared s tidett ɣar řemḥayen n tayya nnec u txarrṣed dayi u war tᵉttᵉttud tayya nnec, ad tewced i tayya nnec ijj n uḥenjir d awtem, \add xenni\add* ad t wceɣ i SIDI min ɣa yekk iddar uca uřa d ijj n řmus war ittḥeffi i uzeǧif nnes.” \f ◼ \fr 1:11 \fk aḥenjir\ft - s Tɛibranit ‘zzariɛet’. \fk min ɣa yekk iddar\ft - s Tɛibranit ‘marra ussan n tudart nnes.’\f*  \x ◘ \xo 1:11 \xt Řqḍ. 13:5. \x*
\v 12 Umi tekka aṭṭas tᵉttẓaǧa zzat i wudem n SIDI, imsar, aqa Ɛali iḥḍa aqemmum nnes.
\v 13 Tuɣa Ḥanna tessiweř deg wuř nnes, iyencicen nnes ttenhezzan waha, \add maca\add* tmijja nnes tuɣa war tᵉttwaseř. Ɛali ittɣiř as tescar.
\v 14 Inna as Ɛali: “Mecḥař \add ɛad\add* i ɣa teqqimed tescared? Kkes xam ssekra nnem!”
\v 15 Ḥanna tarra-dd xas, tenna: “Lla, sidi inu, necc d ict n temɣart s buḥbeř icḍen. Necc war swiɣ binu uřa d ccrab, maca farrɣeɣ uř inu zzat i wudem n SIDI. \x ◘ \xo 1:15 \xt Izhd. 62:9. \x*
\v 16 War ḥesseb ca tayya nnec d ict n tyeǧit i war tsekkʷi, maɣar ař i řexxu ssiwřeɣ \add waha\add* zi řhemm inu ameqqran u zi tiqqest \add n wuř\add* inu.”
\v 17 Ɛali yarra-dd xas, inna: “Uyur di řehna uca AREBBI n Israil ad am iwc min zzayes tᵉttared.”
\v 18 Nettat tenna: “Iři ad taf tayya nnec d aḥinni zzat i tiṭṭawin nnec!” \add Xenni\add* tuyur temɣart abrid nnes, tecca u tuɣa aɣembub nnes war icḍin ɛad.
\v 19 Ɣar tuffut n ṣṣbeḥ kkaren zic, bendqen zzat i wudem n SIDI uca ɛeqben ɣar taddart nsen di Rama. Tuɣa Ilqana iṭṭeṣ ak-d Ḥanna, tamɣart nnes, uca SIDI ixarreṣ dayes, di Ḥanna.
\b
\s1 Axřaq n Ṣamwil
\m 
\v 20 Umi ɛdun wussan awarni řami teksi Ḥanna s ddeyset, turuw-dd ijj n uḥenjir. Tegga as Camwil, \add umi nettat tenna\add*: “Maɣar necc ttareɣ t zi SIDI.”
\v 21 Uca aryaz nni, Ilqana, igeɛɛed \add ɛawed\add* ak-d marra \add inni n\add* taddart nnes, ḥima ad yawi taɣarṣt n kuř aseggʷas d tɣarṣt nnes n lwaɛd i SIDI.
\v 22 \add Maca\add* Ḥanna war kidsen tgiɛɛid ca, maca tenna i weryaz nnes: “Xmi d as ɣa kkseɣ uṭṭuḍ i useymi, \add xenni\add* ad t-i-dd-awyeɣ \add din\add*, uca ad iḍhar \add uḥenjir\add* zzat i wudem n SIDI u netta ad iqqim dinni i řebda.”
\v 23 Aryaz nnes, Ilqana, inna as: “Egg min tᵉttwařid mliḥ di tiṭṭawin nnem. Qqim da \add di taddart\add* ař d as i ɣa tekksed uṭṭuḍ. Ad iqfeř SIDI awař nnes!” Ammu i teqqim temɣart di taddart uca tessuṭṭuḍ aḥenjir nnes ařami i d as tekkes uṭṭuḍ.
\v 24 Awarni řami i d as tekkes uṭṭuḍ, tiwyi t akides ak-d třata n ifunasen imeẓyanen d ijj n ifa n waren d ict n txancet n binu. Nettat tiwyi t ɣar Taddart n SIDI di Cilu. Tuɣa-t aḥenjir \add ɛad\add* d ameẓyan. \x ◘ \xo 1:24 \xt Lk. 2:41. \x*
\v 25 Nitni ɣarṣen i ufunas ameẓyan uca iwyen aḥenjir ɣar Ɛali.
\v 26 Nettat tenna: “A, sidi inu, s tidett am iddar řeɛmar nnec, \add a\add* sidi inu, necc d tamɣart nni tuɣa i da ibedden ɣar uɣezdis nnec, ḥima ad ẓẓaǧeɣ ɣar SIDI.
\v 27 Necc ttareɣ aḥenjir-a u SIDI isřa i tutra inu nni zzayes ttareɣ.
\v 28 S uyenni aqa sellmeɣ t i SIDI marra ussan min ɣa yekk iddar. Aqa immewc i SIDI.” Uca netta ibendeq \add din\add* zzat i wudem n SIDI.
\b
\b
\c 2
\s1 Izři n Hanna
\m 
\v 1 \add Xenni\add* teẓẓuǧ Ḥanna, tenna:
\m \qt “Uř inu ittesřiwřiw\qt*
\m \qt s řefraḥet di SIDI.\qt*
\m \qt Icc inu ittwassgeɛɛed di SIDI.\qt*
\m \qt Aqemmum inu yarzem d arzam\qt*
\m \qt x řɛedyan inu,\qt*
\m \qt maɣar farḥeɣ x usenjem nnec.\qt*\x ◘ \xo 2:1 \xt Lk. 1:46. \x*
\m 
\v 2 \qt Uřa d ijj d amqeddes am SIDI,\qt*
\m \qt maɣar war din iǧi ḥed mɣir Cek,\qt*
\m \qt u war din teǧi teṣḍart\qt*
\m \qt am AREBBI nneɣ!\qt* \x ◘ \xo 2:2 \xt Aɛwd. 3:24; Izhd. 86:8. \x*
\m 
\v 3 \qt War tarennim tessawařem\qt*
\m \qt ammu s nnfaxet, \qt*
\m \qt war dd-tteffiɣ uřa d ca n tuffet\qt*
\m \qt zeg uqemmum nwem,\qt*
\m \qt maɣar SIDI d ijj n Arebbi\qt*
\m \qt issen \tl marra\tl*,\qt*
\m \qt timegga \tl nnes\tl* ttwaweznent.\qt*
\m 
\v 4 \qt Řqews n ayt n bu-teɣruḍt ittwarẓa,\qt*
\m \qt \tl maca\tl* inni inqarḍen\qt*
\m \qt ḥezzmen s jjhed.\qt*
\m 
\v 5 \qt Inni ijjiwnen arehnen ixef nsen\qt*
\m \qt i weɣrum,\qt*
\m \qt \tl maca\tl* inni iǧuẓen,\qt*
\m \qt war qqimen ɛad \tl ǧuzen\tl*.\qt*
\m \qt Tenni war ittirwen\qt*
\m \qt turuw-dd sebɛa n iḥenjiren,\qt*
\m \qt tenni ɣar iǧa ubarru n iḥenjiren, tisřaw.\qt* \x ◘ \xo 2:5 \xt Izhd. 34:11; Igjd. 5:6; Lk. 1:53. \x*
\m 
\v 6 \qt AREBBI ineqq u ittic tudart, \qt*
\m \qt Netta isshekkʷwa ɣar řaxart\qt*
\m \qt u issgeɛɛad-dd \tl ssenni\tl*.\qt*\x ◘ \xo 2:6 \xt Aɛwd. 32:39; Ḥiz. 37:11-14\x*
\m 
\v 7 \qt SIDI ittarra \tl ijj\tl* d amezřuḍ\qt*
\m \qt u \tl ijj nneɣni\tl* yarra i-t d bu-wagřa,\qt*
\m \qt isshekkwa d issgeɛɛad.\qt*
\m 
\v 8 \qt Amuqřiř issekkar i-t zi tɛejjajt,\qt*
\m \qt řmeskin ijebd i-t-i-dd zeg wefraḍ,\qt*
\m \qt maḥend ad \tl ten\tl* issɣim\qt*
\m \qt ɣar tarwa n taṣiřet, \qt*
\m \qt \tl maḥend\tl* ad iwc\qt*
\m \qt ijj n řkursi n řɛezz d řwart,\qt*
\m \qt minzi dsusa n temmurt \tl iǧan\tl* n SIDI\qt*
\m \qt u Netta issbedd xasen ddunect.\qt*\x ◘ \xo 2:8 \xt Ayub 36:15; Izhd. 113:7, 8; Lk. 1:52; Izhd. 24:2; 102:26; 104:5. \x*
\m 
\v 9 \qt Netta i issřeqqan\qt*
\m \qt x iṣuraf n imtiqqan nnes,\qt*
\m \qt \tl maca\tl* iɛeffanen\qt*
\m \qt ad ttwassbekmen di taǧest,\qt*
\m \qt minzi aryaz war ittiři ca d bu teɣruḍt\qt*
\m \qt zi jjehd \tl n yixef\tl* nnes.\qt*
\m 
\v 10 \qt Wenni ittemcubbucen ak-d SIDI,\qt*
\m \qt ad ittwarẓ.\qt*
\m \qt Ad xasen isshemhem deg ujenna.\qt*
\m \qt SIDI ad iḥkem tineggura n ddunect,\qt*
\m \qt ad iwc tizemmar i ujeǧid\qt*
\m \qt uca ad issgeɛɛed icc n lmasiḥ nnes.”\qt*\x ◘ \xo 2:10 \xt 1 Ṣm. 7:10; Izhd. 2:6; 89:25. \x*
\b
\s1 Iḥenjiren n Ɛali
\m 
\v 11 Iɛqeb Ilqana \add ɛawed\add* ɣar taddart nnes ɣar Rama, \add maca\add* aḥenjir isexxar i SIDI zzat i wudem n ukehhan Ɛali.
\v 12 \add Maca\add* tarwa n Ɛali tuɣa d tarwa i war isekkwin. Nitni war ssinen ca SIDI.
\v 13 Ikehhanen nnumen ad ggen ak-d řgens \add ammu\add*: mařa yiwi ijj n weryaz ict n tɣarṣt, \add xenni\add*, umi tuɣa aysum \add ɛad\add* ittnenna, yusa-dd ijj n umsexxar n ikehhanen ak-d ict n furcita n třata n icukḍan deg ufus nnes,
\v 14 ijju tt di řburmet niɣ deg uṭenjir niɣ di marmita niɣ di teydurt u marra min ɣa teksi furcita, iksi t ukehhan i yixef nnes. Ammu i t ggin ɣar marra \add ayt n\add* Israil inni dd-yusin ɣar Cilu.
\v 15 Ammu ɛawed, qbeř ɣa bexxaren tadunt, yusa-dd ijj n umsexxar n ikehhanen, inna i weryaz nni dd-iwyen taɣarṣt: “Ewc ayi aysum ḥima ad t qřiɣ i ukehhan, minzi netta war xak iksi ca aysum ittwanennan, maca mɣir aziza.” \f ◼ \fr 2:15 \fk aziza\ft - niɣ ‘war ittwanennin’.\f*
\v 16 Mařa yarra-dd xas weryaz: “Amezwar ittxeṣṣa ad bexxaren tadunt marra, xenni ksi min ixs wuř nnec i yixef nnec!”, inna as \add umsexxar n ukehhan\add*: “Lla, ittxeṣṣa ad t tewced řexxu, mařa lla, ad t ksiɣ s uɣiř!”
\v 17 Ddenb n imsexxaren tuɣa imɣar aṭṭas zzat i wudem n SIDI, maɣar iryazen sseḥqaren tawhibt \add n řɣiǧet\add* n SIDI.
\b
\m 
\v 18 \add Maca\add* Camwil tuɣa ittsexxar zzat i wudem n SIDI, aqa-t d ijj n uḥenjir iḥezzmen s yijj n upalṭu \add n ukehhan\add* n řeqṭen.
\v 19 Yemmas tegga as ijj n useřham uca tᵉttawyi as t-i-dd zeg useggʷas ɣar useggʷas, xmi tᵉttgeɛɛed ak-d weryaz nnes ḥima ad tawi din taɣarṣt n kuř aseggʷas.
\v 20 Igga Ɛali lbaraka di Ilqana d temɣart nnes, inna: “Iři ad ac iwc SIDI zi temɣart-a ijj n uḥenjir deg wemcan n \add uḥenjir\add* i tsellem nettat, \add deg wemcan n uḥenjir\add* i immewcen i SIDI.” \add Xenni\add* ɛeqben nitni ɣar wemcan n tzeddiɣt nnes. \f ◼ \fr 2:20 \fk ijj n uḥenjir\ft - s Tɛibranit ‘ict n zzariɛet’. \fk deg wemcan n \bdit uḥenjir\bdit*\ft - s Tɛibranit ‘deg wemcan n tutra’.\f*
\v 21 SIDI maca ixzar ɣar Ḥanna u nettat teksi s ddeyset uca turuw-dd třata n iḥenjiren d tnayen n tḥenjirin, am tuɣa imeqqar Camwil ameẓyan ɣar SIDI.
\m 
\v 22 Idweř Ɛali iwsar aṭṭas. Netta isřa x marra min ggin iḥenjiren nnes i marra Israil uca \add isřa ɛawed\add* aqa nitni ṭṭṣen ak-d temɣarin i tuɣa ttsexxarent ɣar wadaf n Uqiḍun n Umsagar. \x ◘ \xo 2:22 \xt Uf. 38:8\x*
\v 23 Netta inna asen: “Mayemmi tᵉtteggem aya ammu, ařami i ttesřiɣ zi marra řgens-a x tmegga nwem tiɛeffanin?
\v 24 Lla, a iḥenjiren inu, aya war iǧi d ijj n řexbar iḥřa i sřiɣ. Kenniw tᵉttarram řgens-a n SIDI ad iwḍa di xeṭṭu.
\v 25 Mařa ijj n bnadem ixḍa ak-d ijj bnadem \add nneɣni\add*, \add xenni\add* ad xas iḥkem AREBBI, maca mařa ijj n bnadem ad ixḍa x SIDI, wi xas ɣa iwten?” \add Waxxa amenni\add* nitni war sřin ca ɣar babatsen, maɣar SIDI tuɣa ixs ad ten ineɣ. \f ◼ \fr 2:25 \fk ɣar babatsen\ft - s Tɛibranit ‘ɣar tmijja n babatsen’.\f*
\v 26 \add Maca\add* Camwil ameẓyan tuɣa imeqqar uca yarni ittas-dd x řxaḍar i SIDI uřa ɣar iwdan. \x ◘ \xo 2:26 \xt Lk. 2:52. \x*
\b
\s1 Awař n Arebbi x Ɛali d tarwa nnes
\m 
\v 27 Uca yusa-dd ijj n weryaz n SIDI ɣar Ɛali, inna as: “Ammu i iqqar SIDI: ‘Ma war i d ssecneɣ ixef inu nican i taddart n babac umi ten tuɣa di Miṣra, di taddart n firɛun? \x ◘ \xo 2:27 \xt Řex. 7:25. \x*
\v 28 Necc farzeɣ t zi marra tiqebbař n Israil d akehhan i Necc maḥend ad igeɛɛed ɣar uɛalṭar inu ḥima ad din issarɣ řebxur \add u\add* maḥend ad yarḍ apalṭu \add n ukehhan\add* zzat i wudem inu. Necc wciɣ \add ɛawed\add* i taddart n babac marra tiɣarṣa n tmessi n ayt n Israil. \x ◘ \xo 2:28 \xt Lawi 10:14. \x*
\v 29 Mayemmi tɛeffsem kenniw x tɣarṣt inu d tewhibt \add n řɣiǧet\add* i zi umureɣ \add maḥend ad tent twehhbem\add* di Tzeddiɣt \add inu\add*, u \add mayemmi\add* tᵉttweqqarem iḥenjiren nwem aṭṭas xafi umi tmesřem kenniw ixef nwem s mummu n marra tiwhibin \add n řɣiǧet\add* n řgens inu Israil?’ \x ◘ \xo 2:29 \xt Aɛwd. 32:15. \x*
\v 30 S uya iqqar SIDI, AREBBI n Israil: ‘Necc nniɣ nican: Taddart nnec d taddart n babac ad uyurent zzat i wudem inu i řebda!’, \add maca\add* řexxu iqqar SIDI: ‘Aya aqa iggʷej xafi, maɣar inni d ayi ittweqqaren, ad ten weqqareɣ, \add maca\add* inni i d ayi isseḥqaran, ad ttwaḥesben d imuqřiřen. \x ◘ \xo 2:30 \xt Uf. 28:43; 29:9. \x*
\v 31 Xzar ad asen wussan, ad qeḍɛeɣ aɣiř nnec d uɣiř n taddart n babac ařami war ittiři \add ɛad\add* d awessar di taddart nnec.
\v 32 Cek ad texzared \add belli ad dd-yas\add* ijj n weɣrim \add n\add* Tzeddiɣt, waxxa Netta ittegg tcuni-ya marra i Israil, uca ɛemmarṣ ad yiři \add ɛad\add* ijj n uwessar di taddart nnec, marra ussan.
\v 33 War qeṭṭɛeɣ ca kuř aryaz i ɣ̮arek iǧan x uɛalṭar inu, ařami ɣa uḥřent tiṭṭawin nnec qaɛ, ad tefna řeɛmar nnec uca marra arraw n taddart nnec ad mmten d iryazen.
\v 34 D ta i d ak ɣa tiři d řeɛřamet nni dd ɣa tas x tnayen n iḥenjiren nnec, Ḥufni d Finaḥas: ad mmten s tnayen deg ijj n wass. \x ◘ \xo 2:34 \xt 1. Sm. 4:11\x*
\v 35 Necc maca ad ggeɣ i Ixef inu ijj n ukehhan d amtiqqi. Netta ad igg ɛlaḥsab uř d řeɛmar inu. Necc ad as ssbeddeɣ ict n taddart temten uca netta ad yuyur řebda zzat i wudem n lmasiḥ inu.
\v 36 Uca ad imsar, belli marra wi ɣa iqqimen zi taddart nnec, ad dd-yas ad as ibendeq i yict n tuqiyyat n nnuqart niɣ i yict n tecnift n weɣrum, ad yini: ‘Arni ayi mɣir ɣar ict n řxedmet n tsexxart n ikehhanen, maḥend ad ɣari yiři ijj n uřeqqim n weɣrum i macca.’”
\b
\b
\c 3
\s1 Tařaɣit n Arebbi x Ṣamwil
\m 
\v 1 Camwil ameẓyan tuɣa ittsexxar i SIDI zzat i wudem n Ɛali. Deg wussan nni tuɣa awař n SIDI iqqiǧet. War tuɣi tᵉtteffiɣ ca n řewḥiy.
\v 2 Deg wass nni, umi Ɛali iṭṭeṣ deg wemcan nnes uca dewřent tiṭṭawin nnes arxunt ařami tuɣa war izemmar ad ittwařa \add ɛad\add*, imsar - \x ◘ \xo 3:2 \xt 1 Ṣm. 4:15. \x*
\m 
\v 3 \add ɛad\add* qbeř ixsi řefnar n AREBBI u Camwil tuɣa iṭṭeṣ di Zzawect n SIDI mani teǧa Ttabut n AREBBI -
\v 4 aqa SIDI iřaɣa i Camwil. Uca yarra-dd xas Camwil: “Necc aqa ayi da!”
\v 5 Netta yuzzeř ɣar Ɛali, inna: “Danita i ǧiɣ, cek třaɣid ayi-dd.” \add Maca\add* netta inna: “Necc war xak dd-řaɣiɣ ca, ɛqeb, ad tezzřed!” Uca iɛqeb, izzeř.
\m 
\v 6 SIDI iřaɣa i Camwil twařa nneɣnit uca ikkar-dd Camwil, yuyur ɣar Ɛali, inna: “Necc aqa ayi da, minzi cek třaɣid ayi-dd.” Yarra-dd xas netta: “Necc war xak dd-řaɣiɣ ca, mmi, ɛqeb, ad tezzřed!”
\v 7 Camwil ɛad war issin SIDI u awař n SIDI tuɣa ɛad war d as ittwassargeb.
\m 
\v 8 Iřaɣa-dd SIDI x Camwil ɛawed i twařa wiss třata u netta ikkar-dd, yuyur ɣar Ɛali, inna: “Necc aqa ayi da, cek třaɣid ayi-dd.” \add Xas uca\add* iḥekkar Ɛali, aqa SIDI tuɣa iřaɣa x uḥenjir,
\v 9 uca Ɛali inna i Camwil: “Ruḥ, ad tezzřed! Mařa Netta iřaɣa ac-dd \add ɛawed\add*, xenni arr xas: ‘Siweř, SIDI, maɣar amsexxar nnec ittesřa!’” Uca iɛqeb Camwil, izzeř deg wemcan nnes.
\m 
\v 10 \add Xenni\add* yusa-dd SIDI uca ibedd din uca iřaɣa am twařawin nneɣni: “Camwil, Camwil!” Inna Camwil: “Siweř, maɣar amsexxar nnec ittesřa!”
\v 11 SIDI inna i Camwil: “Xzar, Necc ad ggeɣ ca di Israil ařami marra wi xas i ɣa isřen, tnayen n imezzuɣen nnes ad ṭneṭnen. \x ◘ \xo 3:11 \xt 2 Ij. 21:12; Irm. 19:3. \x*
\v 12 Deg wass nni ad qefřeɣ marra i Ɛali, zeg umezwaru ař aneggaru min zi ssiwřeɣ x taddart nnes. \x ◘ \xo 3:12 \xt 1 Ṣm. 2:31. \x*
\v 13 \add Minzi\add* Necc ɛeřmeɣ as, aqa Necc ad ḥekmeɣ taddart nnes i řebda x řmuɛṣiyyet min xef issen, minzi řami ssiwḍen iḥenjiren nnes nneɛřet x yixef nsen, netta war ten iṭṭif ca.
\v 14 S uya Necc jjuǧeɣ i taddart n Ɛali: ‘War ittwagg weṣřaḥ i řebda i řmuɛṣiyyet n taddart n Ɛali s tɣarṣt uřa s tewhibt \add n řɣiǧet\add*!’”
\m 
\v 15 Camwil iqqim izzeř ař ṣṣbeḥ, \add xenni\add* yarzem tiwwura n Taddart n SIDI. \add Maca\add* Camwil iggʷed ad iḥaja řewḥiy i Ɛali.
\v 16 \add Xenni\add* iřaɣa Ɛali x Camwil, inna: “Camwil, mmi!” Netta yarra-dd xas: “Necc aqa ayi da!”
\v 17 \add Xenni\add* inna: “Man awař i d ac inna? Ttzawgeɣ cek, war xafi snuffar! Ejj ad ac igg AREBBI ammu, ɛad mahu, mařa cek tessnuffared xafi ijj n wawař \add waha\add* zi marra awař\add en\add* i kidek issiweř Netta.”
\v 18 \add Xenni\add* iḥaja as Camwil marra awařen u war xas ten iffar. Uca yarra-dd xas \add Ɛali\add*: “Aqa-t d SIDI, ejj i-t ad igg min iǧan nican di tiṭṭawin nnes!”
\m 
\v 19 Camwil tuɣa imeqqar u SIDI tuɣa-t akides u war ijji \add uřa d ijjen\add* zi marra awařen nnes ad iwḍa ɣar temmurt.
\v 20 Marra Israil, zi Dan ař Bi’r-Sebɛa, tuɣa ittwařa aqa Camwil tuɣa ittwařeqqem d anabi n SIDI.
\v 21 SIDI iqqim ad dd-iḍhar di Cilu, minzi SIDI issargeb Ixef nnes i Camwil di Cilu s wawař n SIDI.
\b
\b
\c 4
\s1 Ifilisṭiniyyen ṭṭfen Ttabut n SIDI
\m 
\v 1 Awař n Camwil yiweḍ ɣar marra Israil uca iffeɣ Israil ɣar umsagar ak-d Ifilisṭiniyyen i umenɣi \add akidsen\add*. Nitni wtin iqiḍan nsen ɣar Abin-Haɛizir, uca Ifilisṭiniyyen wtin iqiḍan nsen ɣar Afiq. \f ◼ \fr 4:1 \fk Abin-Haɛizir\ft - isem wanita ixs ad yini ‘aẓru n uɛawen’ niɣ ‘aẓru n twiza’.\f*
\v 2 Ifilisṭiniyyen sedden ixef nsen \add i umenɣi\add* ak-d Israil uca \add umi\add* imeyyeř umenɣi da d diha, ittwaɣelleb Israil zzat i wudem n Ifilisṭiniyyen uca nitni nɣin ɛřaḥař arebɛa-ařaf n yeryazen di řeṣfuf \add n řɛeskar nsen\add* deg wazzay \add n umenɣi\add*.
\v 3 \add Umi\add* iɛqeb řgens ɣar řmargeḥ n řɛeskar, nnan imɣaren n Israil: “Mayemmi d aneɣ iwta SIDI ass-a zzat i wudem n Ifilisṭiniyyen? Ejj aneɣ ad neksi Ttabut n Řɛahd n SIDI zi Cilu, ad dd-tas di řwest nneɣ, ḥima ad aneɣ tfekk zeg ufus n řɛedyan nneɣ.”
\v 4 Řgens issekk \add iryazen\add* ɣar Cilu, iwyen-dd ssenni Ttabut n Řɛahd n SIDI n řɛeskarat wenni ittɣiman \add x\add* ikiruben. Tuɣa dinni tnayen n iḥenjiren n Ɛali, Ḥufni d Finaḥas, ak-d Ttabut n Řɛahd n AREBBI. \f ◼ \fr 4:4 \fk ikiruben\ft - ict n marka n lmalakat.\f*  \x ◘ \xo 4:4 \xt 2 Ṣm. 6:2; Izhd. 80:2; 99:1. \x*
\v 5 \add Umi\add* dd-tusa Ttabut n Řɛahd n SIDI ɣar řmargeḥ n řɛeskar, imsar, aqa marra Israil isřiwřew s yijj n usřiwřew ijehden, ařami tarjiji temmurt.
\m 
\v 6 \add Umi\add* sřan Ifilisṭiniyyen i řḥess n usřiwřew, nnan: “Mana řḥess-a n usřiwřew ijehden di řmargeḥ n řɛeskar n Iɛibraniyyen?” Uca nitni fehmen, aqa Ttabut n SIDI tusa-dd di řmargeḥ n řɛeskar.
\v 7 Ggʷeden Ifilisṭiniyyen aṭṭas, maɣar nitni nnan: “AREBBI yusa-dd \add ɣarsen\add* ɣar řmargeḥ n řɛeskar!” Uca nnan: “Ayyaw xaneɣ, maɣar aya ammu ɛemmarṣ war imsar!
\v 8 Uct xaneɣ, man wen i d aneɣ ɣa ifekken zeg ufus n irebbiten ijehden? Ina d irebbiten i iwtin Imiṣriyyen s marra jjrayeḥ di řexřa!
\v 9 Iřim tmeḥḍem u iřim d iryazen, \add kenniw\add* Ifilisṭiniyyen, maḥend war tᵉttsexxarem i Iɛibraniyyen am mammec nitni ɣarwem sexxaren. Iřim d iryazen u menɣem!” \x ◘ \xo 4:9 \xt Řqḍ. 13:1. \x*
\v 10 Uca ffɣen Ifilisṭiniyyen ɣar umenɣi u ittwaɣřeb Israil. Arewřen nitni, kuř ijj ɣar uqiḍun nnes. Tuɣa d ict n txessart d tameqqrant aṭṭas, ařami wḍan třatin-ařef n yeryazen zi Israil i dd-iffɣen ɣar umenɣi x iḍaren.
\v 11 Ttabut n AREBBI tᵉttwaḥewwes u tnayen n iḥenjiren n Ɛali, Ḥufni d Finaḥas, mmuten. \x ◘ \xo 4:11 \xt 1 Ṣm. 2:34; Izhd. 78:61. \x*
\m 
\v 12 \add Xenni\add* yuzzeř ijjen zeg ayt n Binyamin zeg wazzay n umenɣi, yiweḍ ɣar Cilu deg wass nni simant nnes, s warruḍ icarreg uca \add a\add*cař tuɣa x uzeǧif nnes. \x ◘ \xo 4:12 \xt Yac. 7:6. \x*
\v 13 \add Řami\add* yiweḍ netta, iqqim Ɛali x řkursi nnes ɣar tma n webrid, iqceɛ, minzi uř nnes tuɣa ittarjiji zi ssibbet n Ttabut n AREBBI. \add Umi\add* dd-yusa weryaz nni maḥend ad t iḥaja di tendint, tesɣuy tendint marra.
\v 14 \add Umi\add* isřa Ɛali řḥess n usɣuyyi, inna: “Mana řḥess n řharaj-a n řɣaci nni?” \add Xenni\add* iqeǧeq weryaz, yusa-dd, iḥaja \add t\add* i Ɛali.
\v 15 Tuɣa ɣar Ɛali tmenya u-tesɛin n iseggʷusa. Tiṭṭawin nnes dewřent arxunt, ařami war ittwiři ɛad. \x ◘ \xo 4:15 \xt 1 Ṣm. 3:2\x*
\m 
\v 16 Aryaz inna i Ɛali: “Necc usiɣ-dd zeg wazzay n umenɣi. Ass-a arewřeɣ zi řeṣfuf \add n řɛeskar\add*.” Inna \add as Ɛali\add*: “Min imsaren, a mmi?”
\v 17 Areqqas yarra-dd xas, inna: “Israil yarweř zzat i wudem n Ifilisṭiniyyen u řgens igga ict n txessart tewɛar aṭṭas. Uřa d tnayen n iḥenjiren nnec, Ḥufni d Finaḥas, ttwanɣen u Ttabut n AREBBI tᵉttwaḥewwes.”
\v 18 Umi netta yidar Ttabut n AREBBI, imsar, aqa Ɛali iwḍa ɣar ḍeffar zi řkursi zzat i tewwart. Netta yarreẓ zeg yiri uca iffeɣ as buḥbeř, maɣar aryaz tuɣa iwsar u idqeř. Netta tuɣa d řqaḍi x Israil arebɛin n iseggʷusa.
\v 19 Tasřit nnes, tamɣart n \add mmis\add* Finaḥas, tuɣa teksi s ddeyset, tuɣa \add ɛřayen\add* ad dd-taruw. \add Umi\add* nettat tesřa aqa Ttabut n AREBBI tᵉttwaḥewwes, u ɛemmis immut uřa d aryaz nnes, \add xenni\add* tekmummec uca turuw-dd \add aḥenjir nnes\add*, minzi tuɣa iṭṭef i-tt řewjeɛ nnes n tarut.
\v 20 \add Umi\add* dd-tiweḍ řweqt n řmewt nnes, nnant temɣarin tinni ɣares ibedden: “War tteggʷed ca, cem turwed-dd ijj n uḥenjir.” Maca nettat war \add xasent\add* dd-tarri ca u uř nnes war tḥekkar.
\v 21 Nettat tegga as i uḥenjir ‘Ikabud’, tenna: “Ittwakkes uɛuǧi zi Israil!”, minzi tᵉmmeksi Ttabut n AREBBI, uca uřa di ssibbet \add n řmewt\add* n ɛemmis d weryaz nnes.
\v 22 Nettat tenna: “Ittwakkes uɛuǧi zi Israil, maɣar tᵉmmeksi Ttabut n AREBBI.”
\b
\b
\c 5
\s1 Ttabut di temmurt n Ifilisṭiniyyen
\m 
\v 1 Ifilisṭiniyyen ksin Ttabut n AREBBI uca iwyen tt zi Abin-Haɛizir ɣar Acdud.
\v 2 \add Xenni\add* ksin Ifilisṭiniyyen Ttabut n AREBBI uca ssiwḍen tt di taddart n Dajun uca ssarsen tt x uɣezdis n Dajun.
\v 3 Tiwecca nnes \add umi imezdaɣ\add* n Acdud kkaren zic, xzar, Dajun tuɣa iwḍa x uɣembub nnes x temmurt zzat i Ttabut n SIDI. Ksin nitni Dajun, ssbedden t ɛawed deg wemcan nnes.
\v 4 Tiwecca nnes umi dd-kkaren nitni zic \add ɛawed\add*, xzar, Dajun tuɣa iwḍa \add ɛawed\add* x uɣembub nnes x temmurt zzat i Ttabut n SIDI, maca azeǧif n Dajun d ifassen nnes s tnayen mmarsen qessen ɣar tnebdat. Mɣir \add arrimet n\add* Dajun tuɣa teqqim deg \add wemcan\add* nnes.
\v 5 X uya war ɛfisen ikehhanen n Dajun d marra inni i dd-ittasen ɣar taddart n Dajun x tnebdat n Dajun di Acdud ař ass-a.
\m 
\v 6 Afus n SIDI idqeř x \add imezdaɣ\add* n Acdud. Netta issarɛeb i-ten uca iwta ten s tḥebba, \add di tandint n\add* Acdud d jjwayeh nnes. \x ◘ \xo 5:6 \xt Izhd. 78:66. \x*
\v 7 \add Umi\add* iryazen n Acdud ẓrin, aqa ammu i imsar, nnan nitni: “Ttabut n AREBBI n Israil war tzemmar ad ɣarneɣ teqqim, maɣar afus nnes igga xaneɣ ddqeř uřa x arebbi nneɣ Dajun.”
\v 8 Nitni ssekken \add iryazen\add* uca ggin ad ssmunen marra řbacat \add n tneddam\add* n Ifilisṭiniyyen, nnan: “Min ɣa negg s Ttabut n AREBBI n Israil?” Nnan nitni: “Ttabut n AREBBI n Israil ad tᵉttwassmuṭṭiy ɣar Jat.” \add Xenni\add* ssmuṭṭiyen Ttabut n AREBBI n Israil \add ɣar Jat\add*.
\m 
\v 9 Maca awarni i umi tt ssmuṭṭiyen, issiweḍ ufus n SIDI ijj n uxarweḍ d ameqqran x tendint nni uca iwta iryazen n tendint, zeg umeẓyan ař ameqqran, s tḥebba \add innufaren\add*.
\v 10 \add Xenni\add* ssekken nitni Ttabut n AREBBI ɣar Ɛaqrun. Umi dd-tusa Ttabut n AREBBI ɣar Ɛaqrun, imsar, aqa \add imezdaɣ n\add* Ɛaqrun sɣuyen, nnan: “Nitni iwyen-dd Ttabut n AREBBI n Israil ɣarneɣ \add danita\add*, ḥima ad aneɣ nɣen uřa d řgens nneɣ.”
\v 11 Ssekken nitni \add ireqqasen\add* uca ggin ad ssmunen marra řbacat \add n tneddam\add* n Ifilisṭiniyyen, nnan: “Siggʷejem Ttabut n AREBBI n Israil, jjem tt ad dd-tedweř ɣar wemcan nnes, ḥima war d ayi ineqq uřa d řgens inu!”, minzi tuɣa din ijj n uqezzeb imɣar di marra tandint uca afus n AREBBI idqeř aṭṭas \add x Ɛaqrun\add*.
\v 12 Iwdan, inni war immuten, tuɣa ttwawten s tḥebba, ařami aɣuyyi n usɣati n tendint igeɛɛed ɣar ujenna sennej.
\b
\b
\c 6
\s1 Adweř n Ttabut ɣar Israil
\m 
\v 1 \add Umi\add* Ttabut n SIDI tekka sebɛa n iyuren di temmurt n Ifilisṭiniyyen,
\v 2 řaɣan Ifilisṭiniyyen x ikehhanen d igezzanen, nnan: “Min ɣa negg ak-d Ttabut n SIDI? Secnem aneɣ, mammec tt i ɣa nessekk ɣar wemcan nnes.”
\v 3 Nitni arrin-dd \add xasen\add*: “Mařa kenniw tessekkem Ttabut n AREBBI n Israil, xenni war tt tessekkem texwa, minzi ittxeṣṣa ad txeǧṣem ict n tewhibt n umarwas i weɛdař. Xenni ad teggenfam uca ad tessnem, mayemmi afus nnes war zzaywem ittekkes.”
\v 4 \add Xenni\add* nnan nitni: “Man tawhibt n umarwas i d as ɣa nqeddem i weɛdař?” Nitni arrin-dd \add xasen\add*: “Xemsa n tḥebba n wureɣ d xemsa n iɣardayen n wureɣ, x qedda n řbacat \add n tneddam\add* n Ifilisṭiniyyen, minzi kenniw marra \add teřqef\add* kenniw jjriḥect d icten uřa d řbacat nwem.
\v 5 Ggem řexyařat n tḥebba nwem d řexyařat n iɣardayen nwem nni yareddǧen tammurt, uca sɛuǧem AREBBI n Israil. Ad taɣ ad issefses afus nnes xawem, x irebbiten nwem u x temmurt nwem.
\v 6 Mayemmi ɣa tessqesḥem uř nwem am ssqesḥen Imiṣriyyen d firɛun uř nsen? \add Umi\add* xasen izeyyar Netta ař ṭṭarf, ma nitni war d arxun \add i ayt Israil\add* u ma nitni war dd-ffiɣen ca \add xenni\add*? \x ◘ \xo 6:6 \xt Uf. 12:31. \x*
\v 7 Xenni  řexxu, ksim ijj n ukarru n jdid, swejdem t s tnayen n tfunasin ssuṭṭuḍent, war xasent immars ɛad uzayřu, u qqnem tifunasin ɣar zzat i ukarru u kksem asent zi ḍeffar nsent imeẓyanen nsent u awyem ten ɣar taddart.
\v 8 \add Xenni\add* ksim Ttabut n SIDI, sarsem tt x ukarru u sarsem x uɣezdis nnes, deg ict n tsenduqt, řeqcuɛ n wureɣ i texsem ad as txeǧṣem \add am\add* tewhibt n umarwas i weɛdař. Sekkem tt, ad traḥ.
\v 9 Ḥḍam, mařa \add akarru\add* igeɛɛed-dd deg webrid ɣar weymir nnes, ɣar Bayt-Cams, \add xenni\add* d Netta i d aneɣ iwtin s tecti-ya tameqqrant, mařa lla, \add xenni\add* nessen neccin, aqa war iǧi d afus nnes i d aneɣ iřeqfen: aqa tusa-dd amenni waha.”
\m 
\v 10 Iryazen ggin \add tt\add* ammu. Nitni ksin tnayen n tfunasin ssuṭṭuḍent, qqnen tent ɣar zzat i ukarru uca qqnen imeẓyanen nsent deg uyennir n taddart.
\v 11 Nitni ssarsen Ttabut n SIDI x ukarru, uřa d tasenduqt ak-d iɣardayen n wureɣ d řexyařat n tḥebba nsen.
\v 12 Tifunasin uyurent nican ɣar webrid jjihet n Bayt-Cams, uyurent x webrid iseggmen nni. Nitenti qqiment ggurent, am ssmuhrutent, war ḥeyydent \add x webrid\add* \add ɣar\add* yefus uřa \add ɣar\add* uzeřmaḍ. Řbacat \add n tneddam\add* n Ifilisṭiniyyen areddfen tent ař aymir n Bayt-Cams.
\v 13 \add Imezdaɣ\add* n Bayt-Cams tuɣa mejjaren ṣṣabet n irden di řewḍa n teɣzurt. \add Umi\add* ssgeɛɛden nitni tamuɣři nsen, ẓrin Ttabut u farḥen aṭṭas umi tt ẓrin.
\v 14 Akarru tuɣa yiweḍ ař iyyar n Yacuwa, wenni zi Bayt-Cams, uca ibedd \add ukarru\add* dinni. Tuɣa dinni ijj n weẓru d ameqqran. Nitni zedmen tifeřwin n ukarru u ssgeɛɛden tifunasin d taɣarṣt n wecmaḍ i SIDI.
\v 15 Ilawiyyen ksin Ttabut n SIDI d tsenduqt \add immarsen\add* x uɣezdis nnes, i di tuɣa řeqcuɛ n wureɣ, u ssarsen aya x weẓru nni ameqqran. Deg wass nni simant nnes ssgeɛɛden yeryazen n Bayt-Cams tiɣarṣa n wecmaḍ i SIDI u qeddmen \add ɛawed\add* tiɣarṣa.
\v 16 \add Umi\add* ẓrin xemsa n řbacat \add n tneddam\add* n Ifilisṭiniyyen \add man aya\add*, dewřen-dd ɣar Ɛaqrun deg wass nni simant nnes.
\m 
\v 17 Tina d tiḥebba n wureɣ nni ixeǧṣen Ifilisṭiniyyen am tewhibt n umarwas i weɛdař i SIDI: ict i Acdud, ict i Ɣaza, ict i Acqilun, ict i Jat, ict i Ɛakrun.
\v 18 \add Uřa d\add* iɣardayen n wureɣ x qedda n marra tineddam n Ifilisṭiniyyen tinni iqqnen i xemsa n řbacat \add n tneddam\add*, zi tneddam ifaryen ař dcurat i d asent i-dd-innḍen. \add Yiweḍ ukarru\add* ař Abil, aẓru ameqqran i xef tuɣa ssarsen Ttabut n SIDI, \add aẓru\add* i din \add iqqimen\add* ař ass-a deg iyyar n Yacuwa zi Bayt-Cams.
\m 
\v 19 Netta maca iwta iryazen n Bayt-Cams, minzi nitni tuɣa xzaren Ttabut n SIDI. Zi řgens iwta Netta sebɛin n yeryazen \add zeg\add* xemsin-ařef n yeryazen. Uca icḍen řgens, minzi SIDI tuɣa igga i řgens ict n tecti d tameqqrant.
\v 20 \add Xenni\add* nnan iryazen n Bayt-Cams: “Wi izemmaren ad iqqim ibedd zzat i wudem n SIDI, AREBBI d amqeddes wa? D ɣar man wen zzayneɣ i ɣa tuyur Ttabut?”
\v 21 Nitni ssekken ireqqasen ɣar imezdaɣ n Qaryat-Yaɛarim, nnan: “Ifilisṭiniyyen arrin-dd Ttabut n SIDI. Hwam uca ssgeɛɛdem tt ɣarwem sennej!”
\b
\b
\c 7
\s1 Amenɣi ɣar Miṣfa
\m 
\v 1 \add Xenni\add* usin-dd yeryazen n Qaryat-Yaɛarim uca iwyen Ttabut n SIDI ɣarsen sennej. Nitni ssidfen tt di taddart n Abinadab, x tewrirt, uca ssqeddsen mmis Aliɛazar ḥima ad iḥḍa x Ttabut n SIDI. \x ◘ \xo 7:1 \xt 2 Ṣm. 6:4. \x*
\v 2 Zeg wass nni imsar aqa Ttabut teqqim di Qaryat-Yaɛarim. Tuɣa ɛdun aṭṭas n wussan ařami ɛdun ɛicrin n iseggʷusa. Marra taddart n Israil \add tuyur\add* awarni i SIDI, tᵉttcetca.
\v 3 \add Xenni\add* issiweř Camwil ɣar marra taddart n Israil, inna: “Mařa kenniw texsem ad dd-tdewřem ɣar SIDI s marra uř nwem, \add xenni\add* nḍarem xawem irebbiten iɣriben zi řwesṭ nwem, uřa d ‘Ɛactarutin’, u arrem uř nwem ɣar SIDI, xedmem as i Netta weḥḥdes, \add xenni\add* Netta ad kenniw ifekk zeg ufus n Ifilisṭiniyyen.” \x ◘ \xo 7:3 \xt Aɛwd. 6:13; 10:20; Mt. 4:10; Lk. 4:8\x*
\m 
\v 4 Uca nḍaren ayt n Israil ‘Ibaɛlen’ d ‘Ɛactarutin’ uca ɛebden i SIDI weḥḥdes.
\v 5 Inna Camwil: “Smunem marra Israil di Miṣfat, \add xenni\add* necc ad ẓẓaǧeɣ i SIDI i kenniw.”
\v 6 Munen di Miṣfa uca uymen aman, farrɣen ten zzat i wudem n SIDI. Deg wass nni ẓummen uca nnan din: “Aqa nexḍa ak-d SIDI!” Ammu i iḥkem Camwil ayt n Israil di Miṣfa.
\v 7 \add Umi\add* Ifilisṭiniyyen sřin, aqa ayt n Israil tuɣa munen di Miṣfat, ffɣen řbacat \add n tneddam\add* n Ifilisṭiniyyen ḍidd i Israil. \add Řami\add* sřin ayt n Israil i mana aya, ggʷeden nitni zeg Ifilisṭiniyyen.
\v 8 Nnan ayt n Israil i Camwil: “War sbeddi s uřaɣi di ṭṭweɛ nneɣ i SIDI, AREBBI nneɣ, \add maḥend\add* Netta ad aneɣ ifekk zeg ufus n Ifilisṭiniyyen.”
\v 9 \add Xenni\add* iksi Camwil ijj n izmar iṭṭeḍ u iqeddem i-t qaɛ d taɣarṣt n wecmaḍ i SIDI u Camwil iřaɣa ɣar SIDI di ṭṭweɛ n Israil u SIDI isřa as.
\m 
\v 10 Umi iqeddem Camwil taɣarṣt n wecmaḍ, imsar, aqa usin-dd Ifilisṭiniyyen i umenɣi ak-d Israil. Uca isshemhem SIDI aṭṭas deg wass nni x Ifilisṭiniyyen, issarjef i-ten \add ařami\add* ttwaɣeřben zzat i wudem n Israil. \x ◘ \xo 7:10 \xt Yac. 10:10. \x*
\v 11 Ffɣen yeryazen n Israil zi Miṣfa, ḍfaren Ifilisṭiniyyen uca wtin ten ař sadu Bayt-Kar.
\b
\m 
\v 12 Iksi Camwil ijj n weẓru, issbedd i-t jar Miṣfa d San. Netta igga as isem ‘Abin-Haɛizir’, inna: “Ař danita i d aneɣ iwca SIDI afus.” \f ◼ \fr 7:12 \fk Abin-Haɛizir\ft - isem wanita ixs ad yini ‘aẓru n uɛawen’ niɣ ‘aẓru n twiza’.\f*  \x ◘ \xo 7:12 \xt 1 Ṣm. 4:1. \x*
\v 13 \add Ammu\add* i ttwasseḥqaren Ifilisṭiniyyen uca war udifen ca ɛad daxeř i iymiren n Israil, \add minzi\add* tuɣa afus n SIDI ḍidd i Ifilisṭiniyyen marra ussan n Camwil.
\v 14 Tineddam zi Ɛaqrun ař Jat i tuɣa ṭṭfen Ifilisṭiyyen zeg ayt n Israil, dewřent-dd ɣar Israil uca jjwayeh i ɣarsen dd-iqqnen, iqřeɛ i-tent Israil zeg ufus n Ifilisṭiniyyen uca idweř din řehna jar Israil d Imuriyyen.
\m 
\v 15 Tuɣa Camwil d řqaḍi x Israil marra ussan n tudart nnes.
\v 16 Aseggʷas x useggʷas tuɣa netta itteffeɣ, iggur di Bayt-Il d Jiljal d Miṣfa. Di marra imucan nni tuɣa netta d řqaḍi x Israil.
\v 17 \add Awarni aya\add* idweř netta ɣar Rama, maɣar dinni i tuɣa taddart nnes u dinni tuɣa netta d řqaḍi x Israil uca ibna dinni ijj n uɛalṭar i SIDI. \x ◘ \xo 7:17 \xt 1 Ṣm. 8:4. \x*
\b
\b
\c 8
\s1 Řgens ittar ijj n ujeǧid
\m 
\v 1 \add Umi\add* idweř Camwil iwsar, imsar, aqa igga iḥenjiren nnes d řquḍat x Israil.
\v 2 Mmis amezwaru tuɣa qqaren as Yuwil u wenni wiss tnayen qqaren as Abiya. Nitni tuɣa aten d řquḍat di Bi’r-Sebɛa.
\v 3 Maca iḥenjiren nnes war aredfen ibriden nnes. Nitni arezzun x arbeḥ \add i yixef nsen\add*, ṭṭfen arriɣalut u ssfarrɣen řḥeqq. \x ◘ \xo 8:3 \xt Uf. 18:21; Aɛwd. 16:19. \x*
\v 4 \add Xenni\add* munen marra imɣaren n Israil, usin-dd ɣar Camwil di Rama.
\v 5 Nitni nnan as: “Xzar, cek tewsared u iḥenjiren nnec war gguren ca x tebridin nnec. S uya egg řexxu ijj n ujeǧid xaneɣ maḥend ad xaneɣ iḥkem, am mammec \add iǧa\add* ɣar marra řegnus nneɣni.” \x ◘ \xo 8:5 \xt Ḥuc. 13:10; Řex. 13:21. \x*
\m 
\v 6 Awař-a iǧa d aɛeffan di tiṭṭawin n Camwil, řami nnan: “Ewc aneɣ ijj n ujeǧid maḥend ad xaneɣ iḥkem!” Uca Camwil iẓẓuǧ i SIDI. \x ◘ \xo 8:6 \xt 1 Ṣm. 12:17. \x*
\v 7 Inna SIDI i Camwil: “Seř ɣar řgens di marra min i d ac ɣa inin, maɣar war iǧi d cek i nḍaren nitni, maca d Necc i nḍaren nitni, ḥima Necc war ttiřiɣ d ajeǧid xasen. \f ◼ \fr 8:7 \fk ɣar řgens\ft - s Tɛibranit ‘ɣar tmijja n řgens’.\f*
\v 8 Nitni tteggen \add ɛad\add* am mammec ggin s marra timegga nsen zeg wass i ten dd-ssgeɛɛdeɣ zi Miṣra ař ass-a. Nitni semḥen d ayi uca sexxaren i irebbiten nneɣni. Ammu i dayek tteggen nitni ɛawed.
\v 9 Seř řexxu ɣarsen, maca ɛřem asen nican uca sargeb i-ten s řḥeqq n ujeǧid wenni i xasen i ɣa iḥekmen.” \f ◼ \fr 8:9 \fk Seř řexxu ɣarsen\ft - s Tɛibranit ‘Seř řexxu ɣar tmijja nsen’.\f*
\m 
\v 10 Issiweř Camwil marra awařen n SIDI ak-d řgens nni zzayes ittaren ijj n ujeǧid.
\v 11 Netta inna: “Aya i ɣa yiři d řḥeqq n ujeǧid i xawem i ɣa iḥekmen: netta ad yawi iḥenjiren nwem, ad ten yarra i yixef nnes ɣar ikarruten nnes maḥend ad iřin d imnayen nnes, u ad zzřen ɣar zzat i ikarruten nnes.
\v 12 Netta ad ten igg i yixef nnes d imeqqranen x wařef uřa d imeqqranen x xemsin, u ad ten yarr ad carzen iyyaren nnes, ad mjaren ṣṣabet nnes u ad ggen dduzan n umenɣi nnes d dduzan n ikarruten nnes.
\v 13 Yessitwem ad tent-i-dd-yawi maḥend ad as ggent fumaḍat, ad ssnennant u ad ggʷent.
\v 14 Ad iksi mummu n iyyaren nwem, n imarjaɛen nwem n uḍiř u n iḥwicen n tazart nwem, uca ad \add t\add* iwc i imsexxaren nnes.
\v 15 Ad iksi řeɛcur n zzariɛet nwem, n imarjaɛen nwem n uḍiř uca ad ten iwc i imsexxaren nnes icennɛen u i imsexxaren nnes inneɣni.
\v 16 Ad iksi isemɣan d tiyya nwem d iḥudriyyen nwem iṣebḥen d iɣyař nwem, uca ad \add ten\add* yejj ad as xedmen.
\v 17 Ad iksi řeɛcur n tḥimriwin nwem u kenniw ad tiřim d imsexxaren nnes.
\v 18 Deg wass nni ad tesɣuyem zzat i wudem n ujeǧid nwem i texḍarem kenniw, \add maca\add* SIDI war d awem ittesři ca deg wass nni.”
\v 19 \add Maca\add* řgens war ixs ad iseř ɣar Camwil, nnan: “Lla, ittxeṣṣa ad xaneɣ yiři ijj n ujeǧid.”
\v 20 Uřa d neccin ad niři am řegnus \add nneɣni\add* marra, ajeǧid nneɣ ad xaneɣ iḥkem s řḥeqq. Netta ad yizwar zzat i wudem nneɣ uca ad issuyur imenɣan nneɣ.”
\v 21 \add Umi\add* isřa Camwil i marra awařen n řgens, inna ten deg imezzuɣen n SIDI.
\v 22 SIDI inna i Camwil: “Seř ɣarsen, egg xasen ijj n ujeǧid!” \add Xas uca\add* inna Camwil i yeryazen n Israil: “Ejj ad yuyur kuř ijj ɣar tendint nnes.” \f ◼ \fr 8:22 \fk Seř ɣarsen\ft - s Tɛibranit ‘Seř ɣar tmijja nsen’.\f*
\b
\b
\c 9
\s1 Cawul yarezzu x iɣyař uca imsagar ak-d Ṣamwil
\m 
\v 1 Tuɣa \add din\add* ijj n weryaz zi Binyamin, qqaren as Qis, mmis n Abiyil, mmis n Ṣarur, mmis n Bakurat, mmis n Afiyaḥ, ijj n weryaz zeg ayt n Binyamin, ijj n weryaz s wagřa aṭṭas. \x ◘ \xo 9:1 \xt 1 Ṣm. 14:51. \x*
\v 2 Netta tuɣa ɣares ijj n mmis, qqaren as Cawul. Tuɣa-t d ameẓyan u dayes aẓri. Uřa d ijj n weryaz jar ayt n Israil war dayes tuɣi aẓri am netta. Netta yujar marra řgens s tiddi n uzeǧif.
\v 3 Tuɣa tiɣyař n Qis, babas n Cawul, weddarent. \add Xenni\add* inna Qis i mmis Cawul: “Ksi ijjen zeg imsexxaren, awyi t akidek uca kkar, arzu x teɣyař.”
\v 4 Netta ikka x idurar n Ifrayim, ikka x temmurt n Calica, \add maca\add* nitni war tent ufin. \add Xas uca\add* kkin nitni x temmurt n Caɛalim, war \add tent\add* ufin \add dinni\add*. \add Xenni\add* kkin x temmurt n Binyamin, war \add tent\add* ufin dinni \add ɛawed\add*.
\v 5 \add Umi\add* iwḍen nitni ɣar temmurt n Ṣuf, inna Cawul i umsexxar nnes nni tuɣa akides: “As-dd, ad neɛqeb, niɣ baba war ikessi ɛad s wemnus di teɣyař, maca dayneɣ.”
\v 6 Wanita yarra-dd xas: “Xzar xenni, aqa ijj weryaz n AREBBI izeddeɣ di tendint-a. Aqa-t d ijj n weryaz d amcenneɛ. Marra min iqqar, itteffeɣ-dd nican. Ejj aneɣ ad ɣares nraḥ dinni, xenni ad taɣ ad aneɣ isscen abrid i ittxeṣṣa ad dayes nuyur.”
\v 7 \add Xenni\add* inna Cawul i umsexxar nnes: “\add Maca\add* xzar, mařa nraḥ, min ɣa nawi \add xenni\add* i weryaz nni? Maɣar aɣrum jar řeḥwayej nneɣ iruḥ. Neccin war ɣarneɣ aɣiralut i nzemmar ad newc i weryaz n AREBBI. Niɣ min ɣarneɣ \add nneɣni\add*?”
\v 8 Yarra-dd umsexxar ɛawed x Cawul, inna: “Xzar, necc ɣari da \add ɛad\add* ijj n arbeɛ n ijj n ciqlu n nnuqart. Ad t wceɣ i weryaz n AREBBI, \add maḥend\add* netta ad aneɣ isscen abrid.”
\v 9 Zic tuɣa iqqar weryaz di Israil, mařa tuɣa iffeɣ ḥima ad isseqsa AREBBI: “Asem-dd, ad nuyur ɣar umwařaw!”, maɣar anabi n wass-a, zic qqaren as ‘amwařaw’. \f ◼ \fr 9:9 \fk amwařaw\ft - ijj n bnadem wenni ittwařan di tmesřayin n Arebbi inuffaren.\f*  \x ◘ \xo 9:9 \xt Amz. 25:22. \x*
\v 10 Inna Cawul i umsexxar nnes: “Awař nnec iṣbeḥ! As-dd, ejj aneɣ ad nuyur!” Uca uyuren nitni ɣar tendint mani \add iǧa\add* aryaz n AREBBI.
\m 
\v 11 \add Umi\add* geɛɛden nitni tsawent n tendint msagaren ak-d tebřiɣin tinni dd-iffɣen maḥend ad ayment aman uca nnan asent: “Ma amwařaw da?”
\v 12 Nitenti arrint xasen, nnant: “Xzar, netta aqa-t diha ɣar zzat. Deɣyat, maɣar netta yusa-dd ass-a ɣar tendint, minzi řgens ass-a ad igg ict n tɣarṣt x řgeɛɛdet.
\v 13 Xmi ɣa tadfem ɣar tandint, ad t tafem qbeř ma ad igeɛɛed ɣar řgeɛɛdet ḥima ad imun i macca, maɣar řgens war ittett mařa war dd-yusi netta, minzi netta ad igg lbaraka di tɣarṣt, xenni ɛad ad ccen inewjiwen. Geɛɛdem řexxu, minzi ass-a aqa-t \add d lfurṣa\add* ad t tafem \add nican\add*!” \f ◼ \fr 9:13 \fk lfurṣa\ft - niɣ ‘ařaq’.\f*
\v 14 Nitni geɛɛden ɣar tendint uca \add umi\add* iwḍen ɣar řwesṭ n tendint, xzar, iffeɣ-dd ɣarsen Camwil, imsagar akidsen maḥend ad iggur ɣar řgeɛɛdet.
\m 
\v 15 \add Minzi\add* ijj n wass qbeř i dd-yusa Cawul, issargeb SIDI i Camwil deg umezzuɣ, inna: \x ◘ \xo 9:15 \xt 1 Ṣm. 15:1. \x*
\v 16 “Tiwecca ammu di řweqt-a, ad ɣarek ssekkeɣ ijj n weryaz zi temmurt n Binyamin. Ad t tdehned d řḥakem x řgens inu Israil. Netta ad ifekk řgens inu zeg ufus n Ifilisṭiniyyen, maɣar Necc ẓriɣ řgens inu Israil u tɣuyyit nsen i usɣati tiweḍ-dd ɣari.”
\m 
\v 17 \add Umi\add* Camwil iẓra Cawul \add ittas-dd\add*, yarra-dd xas SIDI: “Xzar, \add d wa\add* d aryaz i x i d ac nniɣ: ‘Wa ad iḥkem x řgens inu.’”
\v 18 Yuyur Cawul ɣar Camwil di řwesṭ n tewwart n tendint inna: “Scen ayi mani teǧa taddart n umwařaw.”
\v 19 Yarra-dd Camwil x Cawul, inna: “Necc d amwařaw. Uyur ɣar zzat i wudem inu x řgeɛɛdet, ḥima kenniw ad kidi teccem ass-a. Tiwecca zic ad cek jjeɣ ad teɛdud u necc ad cek ssargbeɣ x marra min \add iǧan\add* deg wuř nnec.
\v 20 X teɣyař i d ac iweddaren ass-a ɛad třata n wussan zeg wami, war dayek ittiři bu wemnus, maɣar ttwafent nitenti. \add Maca\add* wi ɣar ittraḥ marra meẓri n Israil? Ma war iǧi ɣarek u ɣar marra taddart n babac?”
\v 21 \add Xenni\add* yarra-dd Cawul, inna: “Ma war ǧiɣ necc zeg ayt n Binyamin, zi tmeẓyant qaɛ n tqebbař n Israil? Ma war teǧi řaǧ inu tamuqřiřt qaɛ zi marra řaǧat n teqbič n Binyamin? Mayemmi kidi tessawařed awařen am ina?”
\v 22 Camwil iksi Cawul d umsexxar nnes akides, issidef i-ten deg wexxam \add n arwa\add*, issɣim i-ten deg wemcan amezwaru jar inewjiwen. Tuɣa \add nnyarwen\add* amenni třatin n yeryazen.
\m 
\v 23 \add Xenni\add* inna Camwil i ugezzar: “Awi-dd \add řexxu\add* tasɣart i d ac wciɣ, tenni x d ac nniɣ: ‘Ejj i-tt ɣarek!’”
\v 24 D agezzar issgeɛɛed taɣruḍt ak-d marra min xas \add iǧan\add*, issars i-tt zzat i Cawul, inna: “Xzar, aya min iceṭṭen. Egg i-tt zzatek ad tecced, minzi ittwaḥḍa i tsaɛɛet-a, umi nniɣ: ‘Necc ɛarḍeɣ x řgens.’” Uca icca Cawul ak-d Camwil deg wass nni.
\v 25 \add Xenni\add* hwan-dd nitni zi řgeɛɛdet ɣar tendint u netta issiweř ak-d Cawul x tzeqqa.
\m 
\v 26 Kkaren zic, uca imsar, ɣar řefjar n wass, aqa iřaɣa-dd Camwil x Cawul \add i tuɣa iǧan\add* x tzeqqa, inna: “Kkar, necc xseɣ ad cek ssqebbḍeɣ!” \add Xenni\add* ikkar Cawul uca ffɣen s tnayen idsen ɣar barra, netta ak-d Camwil.
\v 27 Umi dd-hwan nitni ař ṭṭarf n tendint, inna Camwil i Cawul: “Ini i umsexxar ad ibeɛɛed zzat i wudem nneɣ!” \add Xenni\add* iggʷej netta. \add Inna Camwil\add*: “Qqim řexxu, bedd da u necc ad ac iniɣ awař n AREBBI.”
\b
\b
\c 10
\s1 Ittwadhen Cawul d ajeǧid
\m 
\v 1 \add Xas uca\add* iksi Camwil taziyyat n zzect, iseyyeb \add i-tt\add* x uzeǧif nnes, issudem i-t, inna: “Ma \add xenni\add* SIDI war cek idhin d řḥakem x řwart nnes? \x ◘ \xo 10:1 \xt Řex. 13:21. \x*
\v 2 Xmi xafi i ɣa tuyured ass-a, ad tafed tnayen n yeryazen ɣar wenḍeř n Raḥil di Ṣalṣaḥ di temmurt n Binyamin, nitni ad ac inin: ‘Tiɣyař i x tuɣa tarezzud, ttwafent uca babac ismeḥ di tmesřact n teɣyař, maca netta dayes \add řexxu\add* amnus xawem, iqqar: Min ɣa ggeɣ x mmi?’”
\v 3 Ssenni ad tarnid ad tuyured uca ad tawḍed ɣar tcejjart n yigg n Tabur. Dinni i ɣa temmeřqid ak-d třata n yeryazen nni ittgeɛɛaden ɣar SIDI ɣar Bayt-Il. Ijjen ad yarbu třata n iɣayḍen imeẓyanen, ijjen ad yarbu třata n tecnifin u ijjen ad yarbu ict n txancet n binu.
\v 4 Nitni ad sseqsan x umeddur nnec uca ad ac wcen tnayen n tecnifin i ɣa tᵉṭṭfed zeg ufus nsen. \x ◘ \xo 10:4 \xt Řqḍ. 18:15. \x*
\v 5 Awarni as ad dd-tased ɣar \add tendint n\add* Jibɛa n AREBBI mani beddent tecbarin n tɛessast n Ifilisṭiniyyen. Xmi dinni i ɣa tawḍed ɣar tendint, ad imsar ad temmeřqid ak-d ict n kula n inabiyyen, inni dd-ihwan zi řgeɛɛdet, uca zzatsen lharpa d ubendir d tẓamart d řgambri am ttnebban nitni. \x ◘ \xo 10:5 \xt 1 Im. 16:39; Řxř. 11:25\x*
\v 6 Ad xak dd-ihwa Arruḥ n SIDI u cek ad tnebbad akidsen uca ad tdewřed d ijj n bnadem nneɣni.
\v 7 Ad imsar xmi ɣarek i dd ɣa yasen řeɛřamat-a, aqa ad xak yiři ḥima ad tegged min ɣa yaf ufus nnec, minzi AREBBI aqa-t akidek.
\v 8 Ad ayi tizwared ad dd-tehwid ɣar Jiljal, u xzar, necc ad dd-hwiɣ ɣarek ḥima ad din ssgeɛɛdeɣ tiɣarṣa n wecmaḍ \add d\add* tɣarṣa n řehna. Sebɛa n wussan i din i ɣa trajid ař dd ɣarek i ɣa yaseɣ, ad ac dd-barrḥeɣ min ɣa tegged.” \x ◘ \xo 10:8 \xt 1 Ṣm. 13:8. \x*
\m 
\v 9 Umi issneqřeb aɛrur nnes ḥima ad yuyur x Camwil, imsar aqa AREBBI ibeddeř uř \add nnes\add* deg ijj n \add wuř\add* nneɣni. Marra řeɛřamat-a imsaren deg wass nni \add simant nnes\add*.
\v 10 \add Umi\add* iwḍen nitni ɣar Jibɛa, aqa iřqa i-t ijj n kula n inabiyyen uca Arruḥ n AREBBI ihwa-dd xas uca netta inebba di řwesṭ nsen. \x ◘ \xo 10:10 \xt 1 Ṣm. 19:19. \x*
\v 11 Uca imsar, aqa marra inni tuɣa t issnen iḍennaḍ d fariḍennaḍ, ẓrin mammec tuɣa ittnebba ak-d inabiyyen, uca řgens inna jar asen: “Min yuɣin mmis n Qic? Ma uřa d Cawul jar inabiyyen?”
\v 12 Ijj n weryaz ssenni yarra-dd, inna: “Man wen iǧan d babatsen?” Ammu i iqqim wawař-a ittwassnen: “Ma uřa d Cawul jar inabiyyen?” \x ◘ \xo 10:12 \xt Gal. 1:24; 1 Ṣm. 19:25\x*
\v 13 Umi issbedd ittnebba, yusa-dd ɣar řgeɛɛdet.
\v 14 Ɛemmis n Cawul inna as u i umsexxar nnes: “Mani tuɣa tᵉttrahem kenniw?” Netta yarra-dd xas: “Narezzu x teɣyař, \add maca umi\add* neẓra, aqa nitenti war dinni ǧint, niweḍ ɣar Camwil.”
\v 15 \add Xenni\add* inna ɛemmis n Cawul: “Ini ayi, ɛafak, min d awem inna Camwil?”
\v 16 Cawul yarra-dd x ɛemmis: “Netta inna aneɣ nican, aqa tiɣyař ttwafent.” Tamesřact n tgelda maca i x tuɣa issiweř Camwil, war d as tt iɛiwed ca.
\m 
\v 17 Camwil iřaɣa-dd i řgens ɣar SIDI di Miṣfa.
\v 18 Netta inna i ayt n Israil: “Ammu i iqqar SIDI, AREBBI n Israil: ‘Necc ssuffɣeɣ-dd Israil zi Miṣra u fekkeɣ kenniw zeg ufus n Imiṣriyyen u zeg ufus n marra tigeldiwin nni kenniw iḥṣaren.
\v 19 \add Maca\add* ass-a kenniw tenḍarem SIDI nwem, wenni tuɣa kenniw ifekken zi marra zzɛaf nwem u zi marra řeḥṣarat nwem. Kenniw tennam as: Egg ijj n ujeǧid xaneɣ! \add Xenni\add* řexxu, beddem zzat i wudem n SIDI, ɛlaḥsab tiqebbař nwem d řuřuf nwem!’” \x ◘ \xo 10:19 \xt 1 Ṣm. 8:7; 1 Ṣm. 8:19; 12:12. \x*
\v 20 Camwil ijja marra tiqebbař n Israil ad dd-qarrbent uca taqbič n Binyamin tᵉttwakkes \add zzaysent\add* \x ◘ \xo 10:20 \xt Yac. 7:14\x*
\v 21 \add Xas uca\add* ijja taqbič n Binyamin ad tqarreb, ɛlaḥsab řaǧat nnes, uca ittwakkes \add zzayes\add* řaǧ n Matri u xenni ittwakkes \add zzayes\add* Cawul, mmis n Qic. Arzun xas, \add maca\add* war zemmaren ad t afen.
\v 22 Nitni sseqsan SIDI ict n twařa nneɣnit: “Ma nican yusa-dd weryaz nni danita?” SIDI yarra-dd: “Xzar, netta iffar jar řeḥwayej.”
\v 23 Nitni uzzřen \add din\add*, iwyen t-i-dd ssenni. \add Umi\add* dd-yusa netta ibedd jar řgens, yujar netta marra řgens s tiddi n uzeǧif. \x ◘ \xo 10:23 \xt 1 Ṣm. 9:2\x*
\v 24 Inna Camwil i marra řgens: “Ma teẓrim \add řexxu\add* man wen ifarz SIDI? Uřa d ijjen zi řgens war dayes yarwis.” Uca isřiwřew marra řgens, nitni nnan: “Tudart i ujeǧid!”
\m 
\v 25 Camwil isscen i řgens řḥeqq n tgelda, yura i-t deg ijj n wedlis uca issars i-t zzat i wudem n SIDI. \add Xenni\add* yarxu Camwil i marra řgens, kuř ijj yuyur ɣar taddart nnes.
\v 26 Uřa d Cawul yuyur ɣar taddart nnes ɣar Jibɛa uca iruḥ akides \add wezyen n\add* řɛeskar nni tuɣa iḥada SIDI uř nsen. \x ◘ \xo 10:26 \xt 1 Ṣm. 13:2. \x*
\v 27 \add Maca\add* ayt i war isekkwin nnan: “Mammec i d aneɣ ɣa ifekk weryaz-a?” U nitni sseḥqaren t u war d as dd-iwyen ca tarzeft, \add maca\add* netta igga axmi war ittesři. \x ◘ \xo 10:27 \xt 1 Ṣm. 11:12; 2 Im. 17:5. \x*
\b
\b
\c 11
\s1 Cawul ifekk tandint n Yabic di Jilɛad
\m 
\v 1 \add Xenni\add* iffeɣ-dd Naḥac, Aɛammuni, uca inneḍ \add s řɛeskar nnes\add* i \add tendint n\add* Yabic di Jilɛad. Marra iryazen n Yabic nnan i Naḥac: “Egg ijj n řɛahd akidneɣ uca xenni ad ac nsexxar.” \f ◼ \fr 11:1 \fk Aɛammuni\ft - ijjen zi řgens n Ɛammun niɣ zi ayt n Ɛammun.\f*
\v 2 Inna asen Aɛammuni Naḥac: “X webrid-a necc akidwem ggeɣ řɛahd, necc ad awem dd-qeřɛeɣ marra tiṭṭ tafusect, ad tt ggeɣ d řefḍiḥet x marra Israil.”
\v 3 Imɣaren n Yabic nnan: “Ejj aneɣ sebɛa n wussan, ḥima ad dd-nessekk ireqqasen ɣar marra tammurt n Israil. Mařa war nufi uřa d ijj i d aneɣ ɣa issnejmen, \add xenni\add* ad ɣarek dd-neffeɣ.”
\m 
\v 4 \add Umi\add* dd-iwḍen ireqqasen ɣar Jibɛa n Cawul, ssiwḍen-dd nitni awařen-a ɣar imezzuɣen n řgens u marra řgens issgeɛɛed tmijja nnes, run.
\v 5 U xzar, Cawul yusa-dd awarni i ifunasen nnes zeg iyyar, inna: “Min yuɣin řgens ittru ammu?” Nitni ḥajan as awařen n yeryazen n Yabic.
\v 6 Ihwa-dd Arruḥ n AREBBI x Cawul umi isřa awařen-a uca yarɣa uxeyyeq nnes aṭṭas.
\v 7 Netta iksi ijj n uzayřu n ifunasen, iqeṭṭes i-ten d iceǧiqen, issekk iceǧiqen s ufus n ireqqasen ɣar marra tammurt n Israil. Ireqqasen nnan: “Wenni war iffiɣen awarni i Cawul u awarni Camwil \add ɣar umenɣi\add*, xzar, ammu i ɣa ittwagg ak-d ifunasen d tfunasin nnes.” \add Xenni\add* tewḍa-dd tiggʷudi n SIDI x marra řgens uca ffɣen munen am yijj n weryaz. \x ◘ \xo 11:7 \xt Řqḍ. 20:1. \x*
\v 8 Isedd i-ten Cawul di Bazaq. Tuɣa-ten di teřt-mya-ařef zeg ayt n Israil u třatin-ařef n yeryazen zi Yahuda.
\v 9 Nitni nnan i ireqqasen nni tuɣa dd-yusin: “Ammu i ɣa tinim i yeryazen n Yabic di Jilɛad: ‘Tiwecca, xmi ɣa tiři tfuct tařɣa, ad tᵉttwassnejmem.’” \add Umi\add* iwḍen ireqqasen, ɛawden tt i yeryazen n Yabic uca farḥen nitni.
\v 10 Nnan yeryazen n Yabic: “Tiwecca ad ɣarek dd-neffeɣ uca \add xenni\add* tzemmarem akidneɣ tᵉtteggem min tᵉttwařam kenniw mliḥ di tiṭṭawin nwem.”
\m 
\v 11 Tiwecca nnes imsar, aqa Cawul ibḍa řgens x třata n ibaṭayunen u ɣar tuffut n ṣṣbeḥ udfen nitni ɣar řmargeḥ n řɛeskar, uca wtin ayt n Ɛammun ɣar ṭṭḥa n uziř. Inni iqqimen iddaren ttwabezzɛen ařami war iqqim uřa d tyuya zzaysen ak-d wayawya.
\m 
\v 12 \add Xenni\add* inna řgens i Camwil: “Man wen i innan: ‘Ma Cawul ad xaneɣ yiři d ajeǧid?’ Awyi ten-dd danita, ḥima ad ten neneɣ.” \x ◘ \xo 11:12 \xt 1 Ṣm. 10:27. \x*
\v 13 \add Maca\add* Cawul inna: “Deg wass-a uřa d ijjen war ittwaneɣ, maɣar ass-a SIDI issiweḍ-dd asenjem ɣar Israil.”
\m 
\v 14 Inna Camwil i řgens: “Ejj aneɣ ad nuyur ɣar Jiljal, ad dinni nřeqqeḥ tagelda.”
\v 15 \add Xenni\add* yuyur marra řgens ɣar Jiljal u nitni ggin dinni di Jiljal Cawul d ajeǧid zzat i wudem n SIDI. Ɣarṣen tiɣarṣa n řehna zzat i wudem n SIDI uca ifarḥ Cawul aṭṭas ak-d marra iryazen n Israil.
\b
\b
\c 12
\s1 Awař aneggaru n Ṣamwil i řgens
\m 
\v 1 \add Xenni\add* inna Camwil i marra Israil: “Xzar, necc sřiɣ ɣarwem di marra min i d ayi tennam u necc ggiɣ ijj n ujeǧid xawem. \f ◼ \fr 12:1 \fk sřiɣ ɣarwem\ft - s Tɛibranit ‘sřiɣ ɣar tmijja nwem’.\f*
\v 2 Uca řexxu, xzar, ajeǧid iruḥ zzat i wudem nwem. Necc wsareɣ, dewřeɣ cabeɣ, u xzar, arraw inu aqa aten jar awem. Zi temẓi inu ař ass-a necc ggureɣ \add am ukehhan\add* zzat i wudem nwem.
\v 3 Aqa ayi necc \add da\add*. Cehdem xafi zzat i SIDI u zzat i lmasiḥ nnes. I umi iwyeɣ ca n ufunas? I umi iwyeɣ ijj n weɣyuř? Man wen i ḥṣareɣ u man wen i ɣezziɣ u zi man wen i ṭṭfeɣ ict n terzeft maḥend ad qqneɣ tiṭṭawin inu? Necc ad awem t arreɣ.”
\v 4 Nitni arrin-dd xas: “Cek war d aneɣ teḥṣared ca u war d aneɣ tɣezzid u war tᵉṭṭifed uřa d ict n řḥajjet zi ca n yijjen.”
\v 5 \add Xenni\add* inna asen: “SIDI d acehhad xawem u lmasiḥ nnes d acehhad ass-a, aqa kenniw war tufim uřa d ict n řḥajjet deg ufus inu!” Inna řgens: “Aqa-t d acehhad!”
\m 
\v 6 Inna Camwil i řgens: “D SIDI i tuɣa iggin Musa d Harun u Netta d wenni i dd-issuffɣen řejdud nwem zi Miṣra.
\v 7 Xenni řexxu, beddem-dd ɣari, maḥend ad awem ssecneɣ řḥeqq zzat i wudem n SIDI, marra timegga iseggden n SIDI tinni igga i kenniw u i řejdud nwem.
\v 8 Umi dd-yusa Yaɛqub ɣar Miṣra, sɣuyen řejdud nwem ɣar SIDI u SIDI issekk-dd Musa d Harun, uca nitni ssuffɣen-dd řejdud nwem zi Miṣra u sszedɣen ten deg wemcan-a. \x ◘ \xo 12:8 \xt Amz. 46:5; Uf. 2:23; Uf. 3:10. \x*
\v 9 \add Maca\add* nitni ttun SIDI, AREBBI nsen. \add Xenni\add* Netta izzenz i-ten i Sisara, akumandar n řɛeskar, di Ḥaṣur, u i Ifilisṭiniyyen u i ujeǧid n ayt n Mu’ab. Marra nitni tuɣa mmenɣen akidsen. \x ◘ \xo 12:9 \xt Řqḍ. 4:2; Řqḍ. 10:7; Řqḍ. 3:12. \x*
\v 10 Uca sɣuyen nitni ɣar SIDI, nnan: ‘Neccin nexḍa, maɣar neccin nesmeḥ di SIDI, nsexxar i ‘Ibaɛlen’ d ‘Ɛactarutin’. U řexxu, fekk aneɣ zeg ufus n řɛedyan nneɣ uca neccin ad Cek nsexxar.’
\m 
\v 11 \add Xas uca\add* issekk-dd SIDI Yarubbaɛl d Badan d Yaftaḥ d Camwil u Netta ifekk kenniw zeg ufus n řɛedyan nwem i d awem dd-innḍen, \add ařami\add* tzeddɣem kenniw di řaman. \x ◘ \xo 12:11 \xt Řqḍ. 6:14; 10:3; 11:15. \x*
\v 12 \add Umi\add* teẓrim kenniw aqa Naḥac, ajeǧid n ayt n Ɛammun, iffeɣ-dd ɣarwem, tennim ayi: ‘Lla, ittxeṣṣa ad xaneɣ yiři ijj n ujeǧid!’, waxxa SIDI, AREBBI nwem, d Ajeǧid nwem. \x ◘ \xo 12:12 \xt 1 Ṣm. 8:5, 19. \x*
\v 13 Řexxu, xzar, aqa ajeǧid nwem, wenni i tixḍarem, wenni tuɣa tᵉttrajam. Aqa SIDI igga i-t d ajeǧid xawem. \x ◘ \xo 12:13 \xt 1 Ṣm. 10:19. \x*
\v 14 Mařa kenniw tᵉtteggʷedem SIDI, ad as tsexxarem u ad tesřam i tmijja nnes, u war ttɣewwɣem x \add min dd-iffɣen\add* zeg uqemmum n SIDI, xenni kenniw, iwa kenniw d ujeǧid nwem wenni i xawem i ɣa iḥekmen, ad tiřim di řaman ɣar ḍeffar n SIDI, AREBBI nwem. \x ◘ \xo 12:14 \xt Aɛwd. 1:26. \x*
\v 15 \add Maca\add* mařa kenniw war tesřim ɣar tmijja n SIDI, ad tɣewwɣem x \add min dd-iffɣen zeg\add* uqemmum n SIDI, xenni afus n SIDI ad xawem yiři am t tuɣa x řejdud nwem.
\v 16 Xenni řexxu, beddem kenniw, xzarem \add řxedmet\add* tameqqrant i d ɣa igg SIDI zzat i tiṭṭawin nwem.
\v 17 Ma war iǧi ass-a ṣṣabet n irden? Necc ad řaɣiɣ ɣar SIDI u Netta ad iwc ajjajen d wenẓar ař ɣa tessnem u ad tẓarem mechař imɣar řɣar i teggim zzat i tiṭṭawin n SIDI maḥend ad as tᵉttarem ijj n ujeǧid i yixef nwem.”
\m 
\v 18 U Camwil iřaɣa ɣar SIDI, u SIDI issekk-dd deg wass nni ajjajjen d wenẓar, uca marra řgens teřqef i-t tiggʷudi d tameqqrant zi SIDI u zi Camwil.
\v 19 Marra řgens inna i Camwil: “Ẓaǧ i imsexxaren nnec ɣar SIDI, AREBBI nnec, maḥend war nettmetti ca, maɣar neccin narni-dd ɣar marra ddnub nneɣ ɛad tuɛeffna \add aya\add*, belli narzu ijj n ujeǧid i neccin.”
\m 
\v 20 \add Xenni\add* inna Camwil i řgens: “War tteggʷdem ca! Kenniw teggim marra tuɛeffna-ya, maca ḥḍam ařami war ttḥeyyadem \add ca ɛad\add* zi ɣar ḍeffar n SIDI, uca sexxarem i SIDI s marra uř nwem.
\v 21 War ttḥeyyadem ca, minzi \add xenni\add* ad taf tḍaffarem \add l’aṣnam\add* ixwan, \add timesřayin\add* nni war ineffɛen u war ittfekkin, minzi nitenti xwant.
\v 22 Minzi SIDI war isemmeḥ di řgens nnes di ṭṭweɛ n Yisem nnes ameqqran, maɣar SIDI igga ad kenniw igg d řgens i Yixef nnes.
\v 23 Min d ayi icqan, iggʷej xafi aqa ad xḍiɣ ak-d SIDI umi ssbeddeɣ tẓaǧit akidwem, \add maca\add* necc ad awem ssecneɣ abrid iṣebḥen iseggmen.
\v 24 Mɣir, ggʷedem SIDI, sexxarem xas s řmanet s wuř nwem marra, maɣar xzarem, ma war iggi Netta jar awem \add marra\add* timesřayin \add nni\add* imɣaren!
\v 25 \add Maca\add* mařa kenniw ad tarnim ad teggem tuɛeffna, xenni řa d kenniw uřa d ajeǧid nwem ad thellkem.”
\b
\b
\c 13
\s1 Řmuɛṣiyyet n Cawul
\m 
\v 1 Tuɣa ɣar Cawul ɛicrin n iseggʷusa umi idweř d ajeǧid. Netta iḥkem arebɛin n iseggʷusa x Israil.
\v 2 Cawul ifarz teřt-ařaf \add n yeryazen\add* zi Israil. Ařfayen \add zzaysen\add* tuɣa aten ɣar Cawul di Mixmas u x idurar n Bayt-Il, u ařef \add zzaysen\add* tuɣa aten ɣar Yunatan di Jibɛa di \add temmurt n\add* Binyamin. Min iqqimen zi řgens yarxu as ijj ijj ad yuyur ɣar uqiḍun nnes.
\m 
\v 3 Yunatan iɣřeb x tecbart n řɛeskar n Ifilisṭiniyyen di Jibɛa, uca sřan xas Ifilisṭiniyyen. \add Xenni\add* igga Cawul ad suḍen deg uyicc n icarri di marra tammurt, inna: “Ejj Iɛibraniyyen ad \add t\add* sřen!”
\v 4 Marra Israil isřa abarreḥ-a: “Cawul iɣřeb x ict n tecbart n řɛeskar n Ifilisṭiniyyen u s man aya issarzeg Israil ixef nnes ɣar Ifilisṭiniyyen.” Ittwařaɣa řgens \add maḥend ad uyuren\add* awarni i Cawul ɣar Jiljal.
\m 
\v 5 Ifilisṭiniyyen ssmunen i umenɣi ak-d Israil. \add Nitni tuɣa ɣarsen\add* teřt-ařaf n ikarruten d setta-ařaf n imnayen, uca řgens n řɛeskar tuɣa deg waṭṭas am yijdi ɣar tma n řebḥar. Nitni geɛɛden u wtin iqiḍan nsen ɣar Mixmas, ɣar ccarq n Bayt-Awin. \f ◼ \fr 13:5 \fk imnayen\ft - ‘inni inyin x iysan’.\f*
\v 6 \add Kuř\add* aryaz di Israil tuɣa ittwařa aqa nitni di řeḥṣaret, minzi uẓẓřen x řgens. Uca innufar řgens deg ifran u deg ifeǧaqen n teṣḍart u di tṣuḍar u deg imucan n tnuffra u deg wanuten.
\v 7 Ẓwan Iɛibraniyyen L’Urdun ɣar temmurt n Jad d Jilɛad. Tuɣa Cawul s yixef nnes ɛad di Jiljal u marra řgens tuɣa ittarjiji awarni as.
\v 8 Netta iraja di Jiljal sebɛa n wussan ař řweqt i igga Camwil. Maca umi Camwil war dd-yusi, aqa ibezzeɛ řgens ixef nnes, \add uyuren\add* xas.
\v 9 \add Řexdenni\add* inna Cawul: “Awyem ayi-dd da ict n tɣarṣt n wecmaḍ d tɣarṣa n řehna!” \add Xenni\add* issgeɛɛed taɣarṣt n wecmaḍ.
\v 10 Umi ikemmeř s tewhibt n tɣarṣt n wecmaḍ, imsar, aqa yusa-dd Camwil. Cawul iffeɣ ad t iřqa, ḥima ad as ibarek.
\v 11 \add Xenni\add* inna Camwil: “Min teggid cek?” Inna Cawul: “Minzi necc ẓriɣ, aqa řgens yuyur ayi u cek war dd-tusid ɛad deg wussan ittwaggen uca Ifilisṭiniyyen nnjarwen ɣar Mixmas,
\v 12 nniɣ necc: ‘Řexxu ad ɣari dd-hwan Ifilisṭiniyyen u necc war zawgeɣ \add ɛad\add* zzat i wudem n SIDI!’. \add X uya\add* uciɣ aqa din aɣiř xafi, ḥima ad ssgeɛɛdeɣ ict n tɣarṣt n wecmaḍ.”
\m 
\v 13 Camwil yarra-dd x Cawul: “Cek teggid tubbuheřya. War teḥḍid ca tawṣeyyet n SIDI, AREBBI nnec, tenni d ac yumur, minzi xenni iři aqa SIDI icedd řexxu tagelda nnec x Israil i řebda.
\v 14 Řexxu maca tagelda nnec war tᵉttɣimi ca. SIDI ifarz i Yixef nnes ijj n weryaz x wuř nnes u SIDI yumur as \add ad yiři\add* d řḥakem x řgens nnes, maɣar cek war teḥḍid ca min i d ac yumur SIDI.”
\m 
\v 15 Ikkar Camwil, igeɛɛed zi Jiljal ɣar Jibɛa di Binyamin uca Cawul isedd řgens i tuɣa ɣares iǧan, ca n setta-mya n yeryazen.
\v 16 Cawul, mmis Yunatan d řgens i ɣarsen iǧan, qqimen di Jibɛa di \add temmurt n\add* Binyamin. Uca Ifilisṭiniyyen wtin iqiḍan nsen di Mixmas.
\v 17 Uca iffeɣ \add ubarru n\add* iqṭaṭɛiyyen zi řmargeḥ n řɛeskar n Ifilisṭiniyyen di třata n bandiyyat Ict n bandiyya tarra azeǧif ɣar webrid n Ɛufra, ɣar temmurt n Cuɛal,
\v 18 u bandiyya \add nneɣni\add* tarra azeǧif ɣar webrid n Bayt-Ḥurun u bandiyya \add wiss třata\add* tarra azeǧif ɣar webrid n weymir nni ixezzaren di teɣzurt n Ṣabuɛim, ɣar řexřa.
\m 
\v 19 Di marra Israil war ittwif uřa d ijj n wemziř, minzi Ifilisṭiniyyen tuɣa nnan: “Ḥima Iɛibraniyyen war tteggen ssif niɣ lansa.” \x ◘ \xo 13:19 \xt Řqḍ. 5:8. \x*
\v 20 \add X uya\add* marra Israil iqqim ihekkwa ɣar Ifilisṭiniyyen, ḥima ad isseqḍeɛ \add kuř\add* aryaz uzzař n wesɣar nnes, dduzan nnes, wuzzař n uzeddam nnes d wuzzař n tsiřit nnes.
\v 21 Tuɣa ɣarsen izeynaten war iqḍiɛen ɣar wuzzař n isuɣar u ɣar dduzan u ɣar tazzarin \add s třata n icukḍan\add* u ɣar isennanen ibedden \add n řmacam n iyenduzen\add*.
\v 22 Umi dd-yiweḍ wass n umenɣi war ittwif uřa d ijj n ssif uřa d ijj n uḥric di marra řgens nni tuɣa iǧan ɣar Cawul d Yunatan, aqa ttwafen mɣir ɣar Cawul d Yunatan.
\v 23 Ict n terbiɛt n iɛessasen n řeskar n Ifilisṭiniyyen iffeɣ ɣar webrid n uẓekkwu x idurar n Mixmas.
\b
\b
\c 14
\s1 Adef n Yunatan ɣar tecbart n Ifilisṭiniyyen
\m 
\v 1 Ijj n wass imsar, aqa Yunatan, mmis n Cawul, inna i umsexxar wenni d as yarebbun řesnaḥ: “As-dd, ejj aneɣ ad neẓwa ɣar terbiɛt n iɛessasen n řɛeskar n Ifilisṭiniyyen nni din \add iǧan\add* x ujemmaḍ!”, \add maca\add* netta war t inni i babas.
\m 
\v 2 Tuɣa Cawul iqqim ɣar tma n Jibɛa sadu ict n tcejjart n aremmam nni \add ibedden\add* di Miɣrun, uca řgens i tuɣa akides iǧan, dayes ɛřaḥař setta-mya n yeryazen. \x ◘ \xo 14:2 \xt 1 Ṣm. 13:15\x*
\v 3 Axiya, mmis n Axiṭub, umas n Ixabud, mmis n Finaḥas, mmis n Ɛali, akehhan n SIDI di Cilu, tuɣa yarḍ apalṭu \add n ukehhan\add*. Řgens war issin aqa Yunatan tuɣa yuyur.
\m 
\v 4 Jar imucan n uẓekkʷu \add x idurar\add* i x tuɣa Yunatan yarezzu ad iẓwa ɣar terbiɛt n iɛessasen n řeskar n Ifilisṭiniyyen, tuɣa din ɣar uɣezdis-a ict n teṣḍart iqeḍɛen i dd-iffɣen uřa d ict teṣḍart iqeḍɛen i dd-iffɣen ɣar uɣezdis nneɣni. Ict ttřaɣan as Buṣayṣ d ict nneɣnit \add ttřaɣan as\add* Sana.
\v 5 Ict n teṣdart iqeḍɛen tuɣa ɣar ccamal arendad n Mixmas d \add ict n tesḍart iqeḍɛen\add* nneɣni tuɣa ɣar ljanub arendad n Jibaɛ.
\m 
\v 6 Inna Yunatan i umsexxar wenni d as yarebbun řesnaḥ: “As-dd, ejj aneɣ ad neẓwa ɣar terbiɛt n iɛessasen n řeskar n yinni war ittwaxetnen, ad taɣ ad igg SIDI ca di ṭṭweɛ nneɣ, minzi war iwɛar i SIDI, ḥima ad ifekk s ufus n waṭṭas niɣ s ufus n drus.”
\v 7 Aḥemmař n řesnaḥ nnes yarra-dd xas: “Egg marra min ɣarek deg wuř nnec. Uyur, xzar, necc akidek am wuř nnec.”
\v 8 Yunatan inna: “Xzar, neccin ad neẓwa ɣar yeryazen nni, ad asen nesscen ixef nneɣ.
\v 9 Mařa nitni \add xenni\add* ad aneɣ inin: ‘Beddem ař ɣarwem dd ɣa nas!’, \add xenni\add* ad neqqim nbedd deg wemcan nneɣ, war ɣarsen nettgeɛɛid ca.
\v 10 \add Maca\add* mařa nitni ad inin: ‘Geɛɛdem-dd ɣarneɣ!’, \add xenni\add* ad ɣarsen ngeɛɛed, minzi SIDI igga aneɣ ten deg ufus nneɣ. Aya ad aneɣ yiři d řeɛřamet.”
\m 
\v 11 \add Řami\add* dd seccnen nitni ixef nsen s tnayen idsen ɣar terbiɛt n iɛessasen n řeskar n Ifilisṭiniyyen, nnan Ifilisṭiniyyen: “Xzarem, Iɛibraniyyen ffɣen-dd zeg ixubac nsen i di tuɣa nnuffaren.”
\v 12 Iryazen n terbiɛt n řɛeskar nnan i Yunatan u i wenni d as yarebbun řesnaḥ: “Geɛɛdem-dd ɣarneɣ, neccin ad awem dd-nessiweḍ řexbar!” Uca inna Yunatan i uḥemmař n řesnaḥ nnes: “Geɛɛed awarni ayi, maɣar SIDI igga i-ten deg ufus n Israil.”
\v 13 \add Xenni\add* igeɛɛed Yunatan x ifassen d iḍaren ɣar sennej, u aḥemmař n řesnaḥ nnes iḍfar i-t uca wḍan \add iɛessasen nni\add* zzat i wudem n Yunatan u awarni as inɣa i-ten uḥemmař n řesnaḥ nnes.
\v 14 Ticti-ya tamezwarut i zi iwta Yunatan d uḥemmař n řesnaḥ nnes ɛřaḥař ɛicrin n yeryazen, tuɣa teǧa x ijj n yeyyar i tuɣa anect n ijj n wezyen n yeyyar \add i izemmar\add* ijj n uzayřu \add n iyenduzen\add* ad t icarz \add deg ijj n wass\add*.
\v 15 Amenni tudef tarjijet di řmargeḥ n řɛeskar x yeyyar, di marra řgens u deg yinni n terbiɛt n řɛeskar. Uřa d abarru n ikeccaḍen ttarjijen s yixef nsen, \add wah,\add* uřa d tammurt tenhezz. Tuɣa-tt d ict n řɛurret temɣar n AREBBI.
\m 
\v 16 Iɛessasen n Cawul di Jibɛa di Binyamin ẓrin, aqa ittwabezzeɛ řɣaci, dewřen nitni ttmenɣan ak-d wayawya.
\v 17 \add Xenni\add* inna Cawul i řgens i tuɣa ɣares iǧan: “Arzum xenni u xzarem man wen i zzayneɣ iffɣen.” Nitni arzun u xzar, aqa Yunatan d uḥemmař n řesnaḥ nnes war din ǧin.
\v 18 \add Xenni\add* inna Cawul i Axiya: “Awi-dd Ttabut n AREBBI danita!” Maɣar Ttabut tuɣa-tt deg wussan nni ɣar ayt n Israil .
\v 19 Umi tuɣa Cawul issawař ɛad ak-d ukehhan, imsar, aqa řɣaci di řmargeḥ n řɛeskar n Ifilisṭiniyyen idweř innehweř aṭṭas. \add Xenni\add* inna Cawul i ukehhan: “Fekk afus nnec!”
\v 20 Cawul d marra řgens nni tuɣa ɣares, aqa ttwařaɣan-dd maḥend ad munen, uca usin-dd ɣar wazzay n umenɣi, u xzar, ssif n ijjen tuɣa x wenneɣni. Aqa ikkar ijj n uxarweḍ d ameqqran.
\v 21 Tuɣa din ɛawed Iɛibraniyyen inni aṭṭas zeg wami tuɣa ibedden x uɣezdis n Ifilisṭiniyyen, tuɣa tteffɣen-dd akidsen mmṭarrcen jar řɛeskar. Uřa d nitni munen ɣar Israiliyyen nni iǧan ak-d Cawul d Yunatan.
\v 22 \add Umi\add* marra iryazen n Israil, inni tuɣa innuffaren x idurar n Ifrayim, sřan, aqa Ifilisṭiniyyen tuɣa arewřen, munen uřa d nitni ɣarsen i umenɣi maḥend ad ḍfaren \add Ifilisṭiniyyen\add*.
\v 23 Deg wass nni ifekk SIDI Israil uca amenɣi iffeɣ uřa ɣar Bayt-Awin.
\m 
\v 24 Ttwaɛarrnen iryazen n Israil deg wass nni \add ar ṭṭarf\add*, minzi Cawul ijjuǧ i řgens, inna: “Wenni i ɣa iccen macca qbeř tameddit u qbeř i ɣa ntaqmeɣ necc x řɛedyan inu, ad yiři ittwanɛeř!” \add X uya\add* war icci marra řgens.
\v 25 Marra \add řgens n\add* temmurt yudef ɣar wezɣar uca tuɣa \add din\add* tamment \add tewseɛ\add* deg iyyar. \f ◼ \fr 14:25 \fk azɣar\ft - niɣ ‘řɣabet’ niɣ ‘tazgant’.\f*
\v 26 \add Umi\add* dd-yudef řgens ɣar wezɣar, \add aqa din\add* tamment s ufeyyeḍ, \add maca\add* uřa d ijj war ɣares isswiẓẓeḍ s ufus maḥend ad zzayes iksi ɣar uqemmum nnes, maɣar řgens iggʷed tajaǧit \add n Cawul\add*.
\m 
\v 27 \add Maca\add* Yunatan tuɣa war isři řami issjuǧ babas řgens. Netta isswiẓẓeḍ s uneggar n uzeǧaḍ nnes nni \add iǧan\add* deg ufus nnes uca issisen i-t deg ict n teɣraṣt n tamment. \add Řami\add* yiwi afus nnes ɣar uqemmum nnes, aqa dewřent tiṭṭawin nnes izdigent aṭṭas.
\v 28 \add Xenni\add* yarra-dd ijj n weryaz zi řgens, inna: “Babac issjuǧ řgens s ict n tjaǧit, inna: ‘Aryaz i ɣa iccen ass-a aɣrum, ad yiři ittwanɛeř!’ \add S uyenni\add* ifna řgens.”
\v 29 \add Xas uca\add* inna Yunatan: “Baba iɣḍeř tammurt di arrẓiyyet. Xzarem waha, tiṭṭawin inu ttceɛɛřent, minzi necc qqaseɣ drust zi tamment-a.
\v 30 Iḥřa asen mři icca řgens mliḥ ass-a zi tkeccaḍt i iṭṭef zi řɛedyan nnes, minzi řexxu ticti \add i zi wtin nitni\add* Ifilisṭiniyyen war teǧi d tameqqrant \add ɛad\add*.”
\m 
\v 31 Deg wass nni wtin nitni Ifilisṭiniyyen zi Mixmas ař Ayalun, u řgens tuɣa ifna aṭṭas.
\v 32 Řgens iɛemmed x tkeccaḍt u nitni ksin uǧi d ifunasen d tfunasin, uca ɣarṣen asen x temmurt, u řgens icca \add aysum\add* s idammen.
\v 33 Ssargben man aya i Cawul, nnan: “Aqa řgens ixḍa ak-d SIDI umi nitni ccin \add aysum\add* ak-d idammen.” Netta inna: “Kenniw tɣeddarem. Seqnunniyem-dd kenniw ass-a ict n teṣḍart ɣari.”
\v 34 Inna Cawul \add ɛawed\add*: “Bezzɛem ixef nwem jar řgens, tinim asen: ‘Ejj \add kuř\add* aryaz ad ayi dd-yawi afunas nnes, u \add ejj kuř\add* aryaz \add ad ayi dd-yawi ɛawed\add* ijjen zeg wuǧi nnes. Ɣarṣem asen da, ccem zzaysen, \add maca\add* war ttxeṭṭim ak-d SIDI umi ɣa teccem s idammen.” Uca \add kuř\add* aryaz zi marra řgens yiwi-dd afunas nnes s ufus di ǧiřet uca ɣarṣen as dinni.
\v 35 Uca Cawul ibna ijj n uɛalṭar i SIDI. Tuɣa-t d aɛalṭar amezwaru i issbedd i SIDI.
\m 
\v 36 \add Xenni\add* inna Cawul: “Ejj aneɣ ad nehwa ǧiřet-a, ad neḍfar Ifilisṭiniyyen u ad ten nkecceḍ ař tuffut n ṣṣbeḥ, war zzaysen nᵉttejji uřa d ijjen \add ad iddar ɛad\add*.” Nnan nitni “Egg marra min tᵉttwařid nican di tiṭṭawin nnec.” Maca akehhan inna: “Jjem aneɣ ad dd-nqarreb ɣar AREBBI.”
\v 37 \add Xenni\add* isseqsa Cawul AREBBI “Ma ad hwiɣ, ad ḍfareɣ Ifilisṭiniyyen? Ma ad ten tegged deg ufus n Israil?” \add Maca\add* SIDI war xas dd-yarri deg wass nni.
\v 38 \add Xas uca\add* inna Cawul: “Asem-dd da, marra imḍebbaren n řgens, snem u xzarem, min di iǧa ddnub-a i ittwaggen ass-a. \x ◘ \xo 14:38 \xt Řqḍ. 20:2\x*
\v 39 Minzi s tidett am iddar SIDI wenni ifekken Israil, waxxa tuɣa-t d mmi Yunatan, netta ad immet nican.” Maca uřa d ijj zi řgens war dd-yarri ca.
\m 
\v 40 Inna \add ɛawed\add* i marra ayt n Israil: “Ittxeṣṣa ad tbeddem ɣar ijj n uɣezdis, necc d mmi Yunatan ad nbedd ɣar uɣezdis nneɣni.” Řgens yarra-dd x Cawul: “Egg min tᵉttwařid cek mliḥ di tiṭṭawin nnec.”
\v 41 \add Xas uca\add* issiweř Cawul ak-d SIDI, AREBBI n Israil “Arr-dd xaneɣ maḥend ad t nessen nican!” \add Xenni\add* ittwaṭṭef Yunatan d Cawul uca řgens iffeɣ \add d amezdag\add*.
\v 42 Cawul inna: “Nḍarem taqedduḥt jar ayi necc d mmi Yunatan!” \add Xenni\add* ittwaṭṭef Yunatan.
\v 43 Inna Cawul i Yunatan: “Ini ayi, min teggid cek!” Yunatan iḥaja as t, inna: “Necc qqaseɣ mɣir cwayt n tamment s uneggaru n uẓeǧaḍ nni \add iǧan\add* deg ufus inu. Aqa ayi da, ma ittxeṣṣa ayi ad mmteɣ?”
\v 44 \add Xenni\add* inna Cawul: “Ejj ad ayi igg AREBBI ta d ta u ad dayes yarni ɛad, \add mařa war cek neqqeɣ\add* minzi \add cek\add*, Yunatan, ittxeṣṣa ac ad temmted nican.”
\v 45 \add Maca\add* řgens inna i Cawul: “Ma ittxeṣṣa ad immet Yunatan, wenni iwyen asenjem-a ameqqran i Israil? War xas nessiweř! S tidett am iddar SIDI, aya war ittiři, war zzayes iweṭṭa uřa d ict n uẓeṭṭu n ucuwwaf n uzeǧif nnes ɣar temmurt, minzi netta igga i-t ass-a ak-d AREBBI.” \add Ammu\add* i ifekk řgens i Yunatan uca tuɣa war ittxeṣṣi ad immut.
\m 
\v 46 Cawul ismeḥ deg weḍfar n Ifilisṭiniyyen uca Ifilisṭiniyyen ɛeqben ɣar imucan \add n tzeddiɣt\add* nsen.
\b
\m 
\v 47 Uca Cawul iṭṭef tagelda x Israil, immneɣ ak-d marra řɛedyan nnes i d as dd-innḍen: ak-d Mu’ab, ak-d ayt n Ɛammun, ak-d Idum, ak-d ijeǧiden n Ṣuba u ak-d Ifilisṭiniyyen. Mani ma yarra s uzeǧif, yiwi-dd aɣelleb.
\v 48 Netta igga s teryast, iɣřeb x ayt n Ɛamaliq u ifekk Israil zeg ufus n yinni t ikeccḍen.
\m 
\v 49 Arrawen n Cawul \add tuɣa aten d\add* Yunatan d Yicwi d Malkicuɛa. Ismawen n tnayen n yessis d Mirab, tenni d tamenzut, u isem n tmaẓuẓt \add aqa\add* d Mixal.
\v 50 Tamɣart n Cawul qqaren as Axinuɛam, yeǧis n Aximaɛaṣ. Uca isem n ukumandar n řɛeskar nnes, \add aqa\add* d Abnir, mmis n Nir, ɛemmis n Cawul.
\v 51 Qic, wenni d babas n Cawul, u Nir, wenni d babas n Abnir, \add tuɣa aten d\add* iḥenjiren n Abiyil.
\m 
\v 52 Tuɣa \add din\add* ijj n umenɣi iwɛar ak-d Ifilisṭiniyyen marra ussan min ikka iddar Cawul. Kuř ijj n weryaz bu-teɣruḍt d kuř ijj n mmis n umenɣi i iẓra Cawul, iksi i-t ɣares.
\b
\b
\c 15
\s1 Cawul ittwammenḍar zi Arebbi am ujeǧid x Israil
\m 
\v 1 Camwil inna i Cawul: “SIDI tuɣa issekk ayi-dd ḥima ad cek dehneɣ d ajeǧid x řgens nnes, x Israil. Seř xenni ɣar wawařen n SIDI.
\v 2 Ammu i iqqar SIDI n řɛeskarat: ‘Necc ad xeǧṣeɣ min igga Ɛamaliq i Israil, aqa ibedd as deg webrid umi dd-igeɛɛed Israil zi Miṣra. \x ◘ \xo 15:2 \xt Uf. 17:8, 14; Aɛwd. 25:17\x*
\v 3 Kkar řexxu u wwet Ɛamaliq. Ḥarrem marra min ɣares i uteḥḥi u war xas ttḥiwiř ca, maca neɣ \add marra\add*, zeg weryaz ař temɣart, zeg uḥenjir ař aseymi, zeg ufunas ař uǧi, zeg weřɣem ař aɣyuř!’”
\m 
\v 4 Iřaɣa-dd Cawul x řgens. Isedd i-ten di Ṭalayim. Tuɣa-ten di mitayen-ařef n yeryazen x iḍaren d tenɛac ařef n yeryazen n Yahuda.
\v 5 \add Umi\add* yiweḍ Cawul ɣar tendint n Ɛamaliq, igga ijj n řfex di teɣzurt,
\v 6 uca Cawul ijja ad inin i ayt n Iqiniyyen: “Ffɣem, beɛɛdem, semḥem di řwesṭ n Ɛamaliq, ḥima necc war kenniw tteḥḥiɣ akidsen, maɣar kenniw teggim s tmexsiwt icewwaren ak-d ayt n Israil umi dd-ffɣen zi Miṣra.” \add Xas uca\add* ffɣen Iqiniyyen zi řwesṭ n ayt n Ɛamaliq. \x ◘ \xo 15:6 \xt Uf. 18:10, 19; Řxř. 10:29; Řqḍ. 1:16\x*
\v 7 \add Xenni\add* iɣřeb Cawul x ayt n Ɛamaliq zi Ḥawila ař Cur \add i iǧan\add* arendad n Miṣra.
\v 8 Ajaj, ajeǧid n Ɛamaliq, iṭṭef i-t iddar, maca marra řgens iḥarrem i-ten i uteḥḥi s řeqḍeɛ n ssif. \x ◘ \xo 15:8 \xt Řxř. 24:7\x*
\v 9 \add Maca\add* Cawul d řgens ḥawřen x Ajaj uřa x řemxeyyer n wuǧi d ifunasen d tfunasin u x min \add iǧan\add* iṣebḥen awarni as u x marra izmaren daysen tadunt u x marra min tuɣa d aṣebḥan qaɛ. War xsen ad ten ḥarrmen i uteḥḥi, \add maca\add* marra min \add iǧan\add* drus d min iḍeɛfen, ḥarrmen t i uteḥḥi.
\m 
\v 10 \add Xenni\add* yusa-dd wawař n SIDI ɣar Camwil, inna:
\v 11 “Necc nedmeɣ, aqa ggiɣ Cawul d ajeǧid, maɣar netta iḥeyyed zi ḍeffar inu u war isseqfeř awařen inu.” Innehweř Camwil, isɣuy tameddit tmun ɣar SIDI.
\v 12 Tiwecca nnes zic ikkar Camwil, yuyur ad iřqa Cawul. Ittwanna as i Camwil, nnan: “Cawul yusa-dd ɣar Karmil u issbedd \add dinni\add* ijj n uqellij n řidaret i yixef nnes, xenni inneqřeb, iɛdu, ihwa ɣar Jiljal.”
\m 
\v 13 Yusa-dd Camwil ɣar Cawul u Cawul inna as: “Aqa cek tᵉttwabarked zi SIDI! Necc ssqefřeɣ awař n SIDI.”
\v 14 \add Xenni\add* yarra-dd xas Camwil: “D min \add ixs ad yini\add* řḥess-a n wuǧi \add i d ayi ittadfen\add* deg imezzuɣen inu, d řḥess n ifunasen d tfunasin i ttesřiɣ?”
\v 15 Cawul inna: “Nitni iwyen ten-dd akidsen zi Ɛamaliq, minzi řgens iḥaweř x mummu n wuǧi d ifunasen d tfunasin, ḥima ad ten qeddmen d taɣarṣt i SIDI, AREBBI nnec. Min iqqimen nḥarrem i-t i uteḥḥi.”
\v 16 \add Xenni\add* inna Camwil i Cawul: “Cfa! Necc ad cek iniɣ min i d ayi inna SIDI di ǧiřet-a.” Inna as Cawul: “Siweř!”
\m 
\v 17 Inna Camwil: “Umi teǧid \add ɛad\add* d ameẓyan di tiṭṭawin nnec, ma war tdewřed ca d azeǧif n tqebbař n Israil, u ma war cek idhen SIDI d ajeǧid x Israil?
\v 18 SIDI issekk i cek ɣar webrid, inna: “Uyur, ḥarrem imednab nni, ayt n Ɛamaliq, i uteḥḥi u mneɣ akidsen ař ten ɣa teqḍid qaɛ.
\v 19 Mayemmi war tesřid ca ɣar tmijja n SIDI uca tewḍiḍ cek x tkeccaḍt u teggid \add min iǧan\add* d řɣar di tiṭṭawin n SIDI?”
\m 
\v 20 \add Xenni\add* inna Cawul i Camwil: “Necc sřiɣ ɣar tmijja n SIDI u necc kkeɣ abrid i x i d ayi dd-issekk SIDI. Necc iwyeɣ-dd danita Ajaj, ajeǧid n Ɛamaliq uca ayt n Ɛamaliq ḥarrmeɣ ten i uteḥḥi.
\v 21 Řgens iksi uǧi d ifunasen d tfunasin zi tkeccaḍt, mummu n min ittwaḥarrmen, ḥima ad qeddmen aya i SIDI, AREBBI nnec, di Jiljal.”
\v 22 \add Maca\add* Camwil inna: “Ma teɛjeb as i SIDI tiɣarṣa n wecmaḍ d tiɣarṣa nneɣni am mammec i d as iɛjeb useǧi i tmijja n SIDI? Xzar aseǧi ḥsen zi tɣarṣt u asḥessi s taynit \add ḥsen zi\add* tadunt n icarriyyen. \x ◘ \xo 15:22 \xt Amb. 4:17; Ḥuc. 6:6; Mt. 9:13; 12:7\x*
\v 23 Minzi aɣewweɣ am ddenb n uɛezzem, u taɣennant am weɛbad n ṣṣanam d řexyařat timeẓyanin n l’aṣnam. Minzi cek tenḍared awař n SIDI, inḍar Netta i cek \add am\add* ujeǧid.”
\m 
\v 24 \add Xenni\add* inna Cawul i Camwil: “Necc xḍiɣ, maɣar necc ttɛeddiɣ x \add řumur i dd-iffɣen zeg\add* uqemmum n SIDI u x wawařen nnec, minzi necc ggʷedeɣ zi řgens u sřiɣ ɣarsen. \f ◼ \fr 15:24 \fk sřiɣ ɣarsen\ft - s Tɛibranit ‘sřiɣ ɣar tmijja nsen’.\f*
\v 25 S uyenni, ɣfar ayi ddenb inu u dweř akidi, \add xenni\add* ad sejdeɣ i SIDI.”
\v 26 \add Maca\add* Camwil yarra-dd x Cawul: “Necc war kidek dikkʷiřeɣ ca, maɣar cek tenḍared awař n SIDI. S uya SIDI inḍar i cek \add am\add* ujeǧid x Israil.”
\m 
\v 27 \add Umi\add* Camwil inneqřeb ḥima ad yuyur, icebbar as \add Cawul\add* di tma n useřham nnes, \add maca\add* wanita icarreg.
\v 28 \add Xenni\add* inna as Camwil: “Deg wass-a icarreg ac SIDI tagelda n Israil u iwca i-tt i jjar nnec wenni iǧan ḥsen zzayek.\f ◼ \fr 15:28 \fk tagelda\ft - awař-a ixs ad yini ‘řeḥkam x ict n tgeldit’.\f*
\v 29 Uřa Lɛaḍim n Israil i ittduman i řebda war issxarriq ca u war indim, maɣar Netta war iǧi d bnadem ařami i ɣa indem.” \x ◘ \xo 15:29 \xt Řxř. 23:19; Yaɛ. 1:17\x*
\v 30 \add Xas uca\add* inna as: “Necc xḍiɣ. Ewc ayi maca aweqqar zzat i imɣaren n řgens u zzat i Israil. Dweř akidi, \add xenni\add* ad sejdeɣ i SIDI, AREBBI nnec.”
\v 31 Uca idweř Camwil, yareddef Cawul u Cawul ibendeq zzat i SIDI.
\m 
\v 32 \add Xas uca\add* inna Camwil: “Awi-dd ɣari Ajaj, ajeǧid n Ɛamaliq. Ajaj yuyur ɣares s arratuḥ. Inna Ajaj \add ak-d ixef nnes\add*: “S tidett, tarzugi n řmewt tᵉttwaḥeyyed \add xafi\add*.”
\v 33 \add Maca\add* Camwil inna: “Am mammec issḥarrem ssif nnec timɣarin x iḥenjiren nsent, ammu i ɣa tᵉttwaḥarrem yemmac jar timɣarin x tarwa nnes.” U Camwil iqeṭṭes Ajaj d iceǧiqen zzat i wudem n SIDI di Jiljal.
\v 34 \add Xenni\add* yuyur Camwil ɣar Rama u Cawul igeɛɛed ɣar taddart nnes di Jibɛa n Cawul.
\v 35 Camwil war iẓri ɛad Cawul ař ass n řmewt nnes, maca Camwil icḍen x Cawul. Uca indem SIDI řami igga Cawul d ajeǧid x Israil.
\b
\b
\c 16
\s1 Dawud ittwadhen am ujeǧid
\m 
\v 1 \add Xenni\add* inna SIDI i Camwil: “Mecḥař d acḍan \add i yeǧan ɛad\add* ɣarek x Cawul, wenni ggiɣ Necc d ajeǧid x Israil? Ɛemmar icc nnec s zzect, uca tuyured. Necc ad cek ssekkeɣ ɣar Yassa zi Bayt-Laḥm, minzi jar arraw nnes aqa ẓriɣ ijj n ujeǧid i Necc.”
\v 2 \add Maca\add* Camwil inna: “Mammec i ɣa ggeɣ ad \add din\add* raḥeɣ? Mařa iseř x man aya Cawul, ad ayi ineɣ.” Yarra-dd SIDI: “Ksi ict n tɛejmit zeg ifunasen akidek, ad tinid: ‘Necc usiɣ-dd ḥima ad qeddmeɣ ict n tɣarṣt d tawhibt i SIDI.’
\v 3 Ittxeṣṣa ad tɛarḍed x Yassa ɣar tewhibt u Necc ad cek ssargbeɣ x min i ittxeṣṣan ad tegged. Cek ad tdehned wenni i d ac ɣa iniɣ.”
\v 4 Camwil igga min tuɣa d as inna SIDI. Umi dd-yusa ɣar Bayt-Laḥm, ffɣen-dd ɣares imɣaren n tendint ttarjijin, nnan: “Ma tawasit nnec s řehna?”
\v 5 Netta inna: “S řehna. Necc usiɣ-dd ḥima ad qeddmeɣ ict n tɣarṣt d ṣṣedqet i SIDI. Qeddsem ixef nwem u asem-dd akidi ɣar ṣṣedqet. Netta iqeddes Yassa d iḥenjiren nnes uca iɛarḍ i-ten ɣar tewhibt n tɣarṣt.
\m 
\v 6 Uca imsar umi dd-usin nitni, iẓra netta Iliyab uca ixarreṣ: “D wa s tidett ɣar SIDI d amedhun nnes.”
\v 7 SIDI \add maca\add* inna i Camwil: “War xezzar ca ɣar waddud nnes uřa ɣar řuɛřa nnes n tiddi, minzi Necc nḍareɣ t, maɣar war itthimmi ca min ɣar ixezzar bnadem, minzi bnadem ittwařa min iǧan zzat i tiṭṭawin \add nnes\add*, \add maca\add* SIDI ittwařa uř.” \x ◘ \xo 16:7 \xt 1 Im. 28:9; Izhd. 7:10; Irm. 11:20; 17:10; 20:12\x*
\m 
\v 8 \add Xenni\add* iřaɣa Yassa x Abinadab, ijja i-t ad iɛdu x Camwil, \add maca\add* netta inna: “Wanita ɛawed war t yixḍar SIDI.”
\v 9 \add Xas uca\add* ijja Yassa ad \add xas\add* iɛdu Camma, maca netta inna: “Wanita ɛawed war t yixḍar SIDI.”
\v 10 Ammu i ijja Yassa ad ɛdun sebɛa n iḥenjiren nnes x Camwil, \add maca\add* Camwil inna i Yassa: “Ina war ten ixḍar ca SIDI.”
\v 11 \add Xenni\add* inna Camwil i Yassa: “Ma d ina marra iḥudriyyen \add nnec\add*?” Netta yarra-dd xas: “Amaẓuẓ iqqim ɛad, aqa yarekkwes uǧi.” Inna Camwil i Yassa: “Sekk \add ijj\add* maḥend ad t-i-dd-yawi, minzi neccin war nettquwwir ca \add i ṭṭabřa\add* qbeř i dd ɣa yas netta.” \x ◘ \xo 16:11 \xt 2 Ṣm. 7:8; Izhd. 78:70\x*
\v 12 Netta issekk \add ijj\add* maḥend ad t-i-dd yawi. Netta tuɣa d arrubyu u tuɣa ɣares tiṭṭawin cnant u tuɣa d muṣbiḥ i řxezrat. \add Xenni\add* inna SIDI: “Kkar, dehn i-t, maɣar aqa d wa.”
\v 13 Uca iksi Camwil icc s zzect, idehn i-t di řwest n aytmas. Uca Arruḥ n SIDI ihwa x Dawud zeg wass nni d tsawent. Camwil ikkar, yareggʷeḥ ɣar Rama. \x ◘ \xo 16:13 \xt Izhd. 89:21; Řex. 7:46; 13:22\x*
\b
\s1 Dawud ittirar x řgambri i Cawul
\m 
\v 14 Arruḥ n SIDI tuɣa iḥeyyed x Cawul u ijj n řaryah d aɛeffan zi ɣar SIDI issiggʷed i-t.
\v 15 Nnan as imsexxaren n Cawul: “Xzar, ijj n řaryah d aɛeffan n AREBBI issiggʷed i cek.
\v 16 Ejj ad yini siditneɣ i imsexxaren nnec inni ibedden zzat i wudem nnec, maḥend ad arzun x ijj n weryaz ittḥakan di řgambri. Mařa iṭṭef i cek řaryaḥ aɛeffan n AREBBI, ejj i-t \add xenni\add* ad yirar netta s ufus nnes \add di řgambri,\add* \add ḥima\add* ad tiřid mliḥ.”
\v 17 \add Xenni\add* inna Cawul i imsexxaren nnes: “Arzum ayi-dd x ijj n weryaz nni ittiraren mliḥ \add x řgambri\add* u awyem t-i-dd da ɣari!”
\v 18 Ijjen zeg imsexxaren yarra-dd xas, inna: “Aqa ẓriɣ ijj n mmis n Yassa zi Bayt-Laḥm wenni izemmaren ad yirar \add mliḥ\add*. Netta d ijj n bu-teɣruḍt imeḥḍen d ijj n weryaz aɛeskari, issen ad ixḍar awařen nnes. Aqa-t d ijj n weryaz d aṣebḥan n waddud u SIDI akides.”
\m 
\v 19 Issekk Cawul ireqqasen ɣar Yassa, inna: “Sekk ayi-dd mmic Dawud wenni iǧan ak-d wuǧi.”
\v 20 Yassa iksi ijj n weɣyuř ak-d weɣrum d ict n tecyart n binu d ijj n iɣayḍ d ameẓyan zeg iɣayḍen uca issekk aya s ufus n mmis Dawud ɣar Cawul.
\v 21 Ammu dd-yusa Dawud ɣar Cawul uca ibedd zzat i wudem nnes u netta ittexs i-t aṭṭas. Netta idweř d aḥemmař n řesnaḥ nnes.
\v 22 S uyenni issekk Cawul ɣar Yassa maḥend ad as yini: “Ttzawgeɣ cek, ejj Dawud ad iqqim ibedd zzat i wudem inu, maɣar netta yufa arḍa di tiṭṭawin inu.”
\v 23 Meřmi ma dd-yusa řaryaḥ d aɛeffan n AREBBI ɣar Cawul, iksi Dawud řgambri uca ibda ittirar dayes s ufus nnes. D man aya dd-yarrin nnefs ɣar Cawul ařami idweř mliḥ, uca \add xenni\add* iḥeyyed xas buḥbeř aɛeffan.
\b
\b
\c 17
\s1 Dawud d Juliyat
\m 
\v 1 Ifilisṭiniyyen ssmunen řɛeskarat nsen i umenɣi u nitni nnyarwen ɣar Suku di \add temmurt n\add* Yahuda. Wtin iqiḍan nsen jar Suku d Ɛaziqqa ɣar Afas-Dammim.
\v 2 \add Uřa d\add* Cawul d yeryazen n Israil nnyarwen uca wtin iqiḍan nsen di Teɣzurt n Ila. Nitni sedden ixef nsen i umenɣi qibač i Ifilisṭiniyyen.
\v 3 Ifilisṭiniyyen bedden x wedrar ɣar uɣezdis-a u Israiliyyen bedden x wedrar ɣar uɣezdis nni u taɣzurt tuɣa jar asen.
\v 4 \add Xenni\add* iffeɣ-dd ijj n uɛeskari d azeɛɛam zi řmargeḥ n řɛeskar n Ifilisṭiniyyen, qqaren as Juliyat. Tuɣa-t zi Jat. Řuɛřa nnes setta n iɣaǧen d ijj n wezyen n uɣiř.
\v 5 X uzeǧif nnes tuɣa ijj n lkask n nnḥas, u netta yarḍ arruḍ n wuzzař n uɛeskari s teqcurin. Tuɣa řewzen n warruḍ n wuzzař xemsa-ařaf ciqlu n nnḥas.
\v 6 Netta tuɣa ɣares iseřqan n ifadden n nnḥas i uḥeṭṭu n iḍaren u jar tɣarḍin nnes \add yarbu\add* ijj n uḥric n nnḥas.
\v 7 Aɛmud n lansa nnes tuɣa t am yijj n ukeccuḍ n uxeyyeḍ u tixeft \add n wuzzař\add* n lansa nnes tewzen setta-mya ciqlu n wuzzař u wenni d as yarebbun taseddart nnes tameqqrant n uɛeskari izwar as.
\m 
\v 8 Netta tuɣa ibedd \add din\add*, iřaɣa i iseddiyyen n řɛeskar n Israil, inna asen: “Mayemmi i dd-teffɣem u tseddem ixef nwem i umenɣi? War iǧi necc d Afilisṭini u kenniw d imsexxaren n Cawul? Farzem ijj n weryaz i kenniw wenni ɣari dd ɣa ihwan.
\v 9 Mři xafi izemmar deg umenɣi, ad ayi iwwet, \add xenni\add* neccin ad niři d imsexxaren nwem, \add maca\add* mařa necc arebḥeɣ uca ad xas ɣeřbeɣ, \add xenni\add* kenniw ad tiřim d imsexxaren nneɣ, ad aneɣ tsexxarem.”
\v 10 Inna Ufilisṭini \add ɛawed\add*: “Deg wass-a stehziɣ zeg iseddiyyen n řɛeskar n Israil, ad \add awem\add* iniɣ: ‘Ewc ayi ijj n weryaz maḥend ad nemmneɣ ak-d wayawya!’”
\v 11 Cawul d marra Israil sřan awařen-a n Ufilisṭini uca nnxeřɛen u ggʷeden aṭṭas.
\m 
\v 12 Dawud tuɣa d mmis n ijj n weryaz zi Ifrata, zi Bayt-Laḥm di \add temmurt n\add* Yahuda, qqaren as Yassa. Netta tuɣa ɣares tmenya n iḥenjiren u deg wussan n Cawul \add tuɣa ḥessben t\add* d awessar umi dd-yusa jar yeryazen.
\v 13 Třata n iḥenjiren imeqqranen n Yassa ḍfaren Cawul ɣar umenɣi. Ismawen n třata n iḥenjiren nnes, inni dd-iffɣen ɣar umenɣi, aqa aten Iliyab, amenzu, u wenni wiss tnayen d Abinadab u wenni wiss třata d Camma.
\v 14 Tuɣa Dawud d amaẓuẓ uca třata n \add iḥenjiren\add* imeqqranen tuɣa ḍfaren Cawul.
\v 15 Dawud tuɣa \add innum\add* ittraḥ \add dinni\add* u \add xenni\add* ittareggʷeḥ-dd zi Cawul, ḥima ad yarwes uǧi n babas di Bayt-Laḥm. \x ◘ \xo 17:15 \xt 1 Ṣm. 16:19\x*
\m 
\v 16 Afilisṭini tuɣa ittas-dd ɣar tuffut u ɣar tmeddit, isscan ixef nnes \add din\add*, arebɛin n wussan.
\m 
\v 17 Inna Yassa i mmis Dawud: “Ksi ɛafak i aytmac ijj n ifa n teɣwawin-a d ɛecra n tecnifin, awyi tent deɣya ɣar řmargeḥ n řɛeskar ɣar aytmac.
\v 18 U ɛecra n trussi n uɣi-ya awyi tent ɣar umeqqran x wařef. Arzu x yaytmac, ma mliḥ i iǧan u awyi zzaysen ict n weḍman \add d jjurret n tudart\add*!”
\v 19 Cawul d aytmas d marra iryaz\add en\add* n Israil, tuɣa ttmenɣan ak-d Ifilisṭiniyyen di Teɣzurt n Ila.
\m 
\v 20 Ikkar Dawud zic ɣar tuffut, ijja tḥimart n wuǧi ɣar ijj n uɛessas u yiwi \add marra aya\add* akides uca yuyur am mammec tuɣa i d as t yumur Yassa. Umi dd-yiweḍ ɣar řmargeḥ n ikarruten, řexdenni i iffeɣ řɛeskar ɣar useddi n umenɣi, \add bdan\add* ad sɣuyen s iɣuyyan n umenɣi. \x ◘ \xo 17:20 \xt 1 Ṣm. 26:5\x*
\v 21 Israil d Ifilisṭiniyyen sedden ixef nsen \add i umenɣi\add*, aɣembub n ijj n useddi deg uɣembub n ijj n useddi nneɣni.
\v 22 Dawud ijja řeḥwayej nni ɣares deg ifassen n ijj n uɛessas n řeḥwayej uca yuzzeř ɣar useddi n řɛeskar. Umi \add din\add* yiweḍ, isseqsa x yaytmas mammec ǧan nitni.
\v 23 \add Řami\add* tuɣa akidsen issawař, xzar, iffeɣ-dd umjahed azeɛɛam nni, qqaren as Julyat zi Jat, zi řɛeskar n Ifilisṭiniyyen. Netta issiweř s wawařen d ijjen u Dawud isřa \add xas\add*.
\v 24 Umi ẓrin marra iryazen n Israil aryaz \add nni\add*, arewřen. Nitni ggʷeden aṭṭas.
\v 25 Nnan yeryazen n Israil: “Ma teẓrim kenniw mammec i dd-igeɛɛed weryaz nni? Netta igeɛɛed-dd ḥima ad istehza zi Israil. Aryaz wenni t i ɣa iɣeřben, ad t yarr ujeǧid d bu-wagřa ameqqran. Netta ad as iwc yeǧis u ad ikkes x \add řaǧ n\add* taddart n babas ḍḍariba di Israil.”
\v 26 \add Xenni\add* issiweř Dawud ak-d yeryazen inni ɣares dd-ibedden, inna: “Min ɣa ittwagg i weryaz nni i ɣa iwten Afilisṭini-aya, wenni i ɣa ikkes astehzi x Israil? Min iɛna Afilisṭini-aya i war ittwaxetnen, aqa istehza x iseddiyyen n řɛeskar n AREBBI iddaren?”
\v 27 Yarra-dd xas řgens s wawař d ijjen, nnan: “D man aya i ɣa ittwagg i weryaz nni t i ɣa iɣeřben.”
\m 
\v 28 Umas ameqqran Iliyab isřa as issawař ak-d yeryazen. Yarɣa uxeyyeq n Iliyab x Dawud, inna: “Mayemmi i dd-tehwid cek \add danita\add* u man wen i umi tejjid taḥimart tameẓyant n wuǧi di řexřa? Necc ssneɣ aɛeffar nnec d tuɛeffna n wuř nnec, minzi cek tehwid-dd \add danita\add* ḥima ad texzared ɣar umenɣi.”
\v 29 Dawud inna: “Min ggiɣ řexxu ɛawed? Ma war \add iǧi\add* mɣir ijj n wawař \add i sseqsiɣ\add*?”
\v 30 Netta iḥeyyed xas, iruḥ ɣar ijjen nneɣni, isseqsa aseqsi d ijjen uca yarra-dd xas řgens s wawař d ijjen am mammec dd-arrin nitni twařa tamezwarut.
\m 
\v 31 Nitni sřan i wawařen i tuɣa issawař Dawud uca ssiwřen x man aya zzat i wudem n Cawul u netta ijja ad t-i-dd-awyen.
\v 32 Inna Dawud i Cawul: “Uřa d ijj n bnadem war ittefciř wuř nnes zeg Ufilisṭini. Amsexxar nnec ad yuyur ad immneɣ ak-d Ufilisṭini.”
\v 33 Cawul inna i Dawud: “Cek war tzemmared ad traḥed ɣar Ufilisṭini-aya ḥima akides tᵉmmenɣed, maɣar cek d aḥudri \add ɛad\add*, \add maca\add* netta d aryaz aɛeskari zi temẓi nnes.”
\v 34 \add Xas uca\add* inna Dawud i Cawul: “Amsexxar nnec tuɣa yarekkwes taḥimart n wuǧi n babas. \add Mařa\add* yusa-dd ijj n weyrad niɣ ijj n ddub, uca iṭṭef ijjen zeg wuǧi n tḥimart,
\v 35 \add xenni\add* ḍfareɣ t, wtiɣ t u fekkeɣ-dd \add izmar\add* zeg uqemmum nnes. \add Řami\add* dd-ikkar akidi, cebbareɣ as di tmart, wtiɣ t uca nɣiɣ t.
\v 36 Amsexxar nnec inɣa ayrad uřa d ddub. Ammu i ɣa yiři ak-d Ufilisṭini-aya i war ittwaxetnen, ad as temsar am i yijj n zzaysen, minzi netta istehza zeg iseddiyyen n řɛeskar n AREBBI iddaren.”
\v 37 Inna Dawud \add ɛawed\add*: “SIDI wenni d ayi ifekken zeg iceqřaḍen n wayrad u zeg iceqřaḍen n ddub, ad ayi ifekk zeg ufus n Afilisṭini-aya.” \add Xenni\add* inna Cawul i Dawud: “Uyur, ad kidek yiři SIDI!”
\v 38 Cawul issyarḍ i Dawud arruḍ nnes \add n umenɣi\add*, igga as ijj n lkask n nnḥas x uzeǧif nnes u iḥezzem as s yijj n warruḍ n wuzzař.
\v 39 Icedd Dawud ssif nnes tiwa i warruḍ nnes, inwa ad yuyur \add cwayt\add*, minzi war t iqeǧeb ɛemmarṣ. \add Xenni\add* inna Dawud i Cawul: “Necc war zemmareɣ ad uyureɣ di řeḥwayej-a, war tt qeǧbeɣ ɛemmarṣ!” Uca Dawud issars i-tent ɛawed.
\v 40 Iksi aɛekkaz deg ufus nnes, ixḍar xemsa n iẓra iḥnunnyen zi teɣzart uca igga i-ten di tecyart nnes n tarewsa i ɣares tuɣa, \add maca\add* mani ten i ɣa yaweḍ deɣya, u tuɣa iǧiy deg ufus nnes. \add Ammu i\add* iffeɣ ɣar umsagar ak-d Ufilisṭini.
\v 41 Afilisṭini yuyur, iqarreb-dd ɣar Dawud u wenni d as yarebbun taseddart tameqqrant izwar as.
\v 42 \add Umi\add* dd issgeɛɛed Ufilisṭini tamuɣři nnes, iẓra Dawud, isseḥqar i-t, maɣar Dawud tuɣa d aḥudri ɛad, netta tuɣa arrubyu d muṣbiḥ i řxezrat.
\v 43 Afilisṭini inna i Dawud: “Ma necc d ijj n weqzin, aqa cek tusid-dd ɣari s ikecwaḍ?” Uca Afilisṭini tuɣa ineɛɛeř x Dawud ɣar irebbiten nnes.
\v 44 Inna Ufilisṭini \add ɛawed\add* i Dawud: “As-dd ɣari, \add xenni\add* necc ad wceɣ aysum nnec, \add maḥend ad t ṣarḍen\add* ijḍaḍ n ujenna d řmař n řexřa.”
\m 
\v 45 \add Xenni\add* inna Dawud i Ufilisṭini: “Cek tusid-dd ɣari s ssif d lansa d uḥric, maca necc usiɣ-dd ɣarek deg Yisem n SIDI n řɛeskarat, AREBBI n iseddiyyen n řɛeskar n Israil nni zi testᵉhezzid.”
\v 46 Ass-a ad cek igg SIDI deg ufus inu. Necc ad cek ɣeřbeɣ. Ad ac kkseɣ azeǧif u deg wass-a ad wceɣ řxecbat n řɛeskar n Ifilisṭiniyyen, \add maḥend ad tent ṣarḍen\add* ijḍaḍ n ujenna d řmař n řexřa. Marra ddunect ad tessen aqa Israil ɣares ijj n AREBBI.
\v 47 Uřa d marra agraw-a \add n řgens\add* ad issen aqa SIDI war ittfekki s ssif uřa s lansa, maɣar amenɣi n SIDI u Netta ad cek igg deg ifassen nneɣ.” \f ◼ \fr 17:47 \fk deg ifassen nneɣ\ft - s Tɛibranit ‘deg ufus nneɣ’.\f*
\v 48 Uca imsar, umi Afilisṭini ikkar, iqarreb-dd ɣar Dawud, Dawud igga s tazřa uca yuzzeř ɣar useddi n řɛeskar \add n řeɛdu\add* i umsagar ak-d Ufilisṭini.
\v 49 Iwta Dawud ɣar tecyart nnes n tarewsa, ikkes-dd ijj n weẓru, iḥejjar \add i-t\add* s iǧiy uca iřqef Afilisṭini di tenyart nnes. Aẓru indef i tenyart nnes ařami iwḍa netta x uɣembub nnes ɣar temmurt.
\v 50 Ammu i iɣřeb Dawud x Ufilisṭini s ijj n yiǧiy d ijj n weẓru. Netta iřqef Afilisṭini, inɣa i-t. War ɣares tuɣi i Dawud qaɛ ssif deg ufus nnes.
\v 51 \add Xenni\add* yuzzeř Dawud \add din\add* ɣar Ufilisṭini u \add umi\add* dd-ibedd \add zzates\add*, iṭṭef ssif nnes, ijbed i-t-i-dd zeg weɣraf, inɣa i-t, uca iqess as azeǧif s ssif nnes. \add Umi\add* ẓrin Ifilisṭiniyyen, aqa bu-teɣruḍt nsen immut, arewřen nitni.
\v 52 Iryazen n Israil d Yahuda kkaren, sɣuyen ařaɣi n umenɣi uca ḍfaren Ifilisṭiniyyen ař Jat u ař tiwwura n Ɛaqrun. Inni ittwanɣen zeg Ifilisṭiniyyen wḍan deg webrid zi Caɛarayim ař Jat d Ɛaqrun.
\v 53 \add Awarni aya\add* ɛeqben-dd ayt n Israil zeg weḍfar s wecnaq n Ifilisṭiniyyen uca keccḍen řemrageḥ n řɛeskar nsen.
\v 54 Iksi Dawud azeǧif n Ufilisṭini, yiwyi t ɣar Urcalim, \add maca\add* řesnaḥ nnes igga i-ten deg uqiḍun nnes. \f ◼ \fr 17:54 \fk řesnaḥ nnes\ft - ixs ad yini ‘řesnaḥ n Julyat’.\f*
\m 
\v 55 \add Umi\add* iẓra Cawul aqa Dawud iggur ɣar umsagar ak-d Ufilisṭini, inna netta i Abnir, akumandar n řɛeskar: “Umi igga mmis uḥudri-ya?” Abnir yarra-dd xas: “S tidett am iddar řeɛmar nnec, \add a\add* ajeǧid, necc war t ssineɣ.”
\v 56 Ajeǧid inna: “Seqsa \add xenni\add* umi igga mmis uḥuḍri-ya!”
\v 57 \add Umi\add* dd-iɛqeb Dawud awarni i umi tuɣa iɣřeb x Ufilisṭini, yiwyi t akides Abnir, indeh i-t ɣar Cawul. Dawud tuɣa ɣares ɛad azeǧif n Ufilisṭini deg ufus nnes.
\v 58 Cawul isseqsa t: “Umi teggid mmis cek, \add a\add* aḥudri?” Dawud yarra-dd xas: “Mmis n umsexxar nnec, \add n\add* Yassa zi Bayt-Laḥm.”
\b
\b
\c 18
\s1 Řeɛdawat n Cawul ḍidd i Dawud
\m 
\v 1 Umi ikemmeř \add Dawud\add* řhard ak-d Cawul, imsar, aqa řeɛmar n Yunatan iqqen ɣar Dawud, u Yunatan ittexs Dawud am řeɛmar nnes.
\v 2 Cawul iksi ɣares Dawud deg wass nni u war t ijji ɛad ad iɛqeb ɣar taddart n babas.
\v 3 Yunatan igga ijj n řɛahd ak-d Dawud, minzi netta ittexs i-t am yixef nnes.
\v 4 Yunatan ikkes aseřham nnes i tuɣa yarḍ, iwca i-t i Dawud, uřa d arruḍ nnes, \add uca\add* ɛawed ssif nnes d řqews nnes d webyas nnes \add i řesnaḥ\add*.
\v 5 Dawud iffeɣ \add ɣar umenɣi\add* mani ma issekk i-t Cawul. Tuɣa abrid nnes mliḥ ařami t yarra Cawul x iɛeskariyyen nnes. Tuɣa \add Dawud\add* d lemliḥ di tiṭṭawin n marra řgens uřa di tiṭṭawin n imsexxaren n Cawul.
\v 6 \add Xmi\add* dd-usin umi yareggʷeḥ Dawud awarni i řeɣřeb x Ifilisṭiniyyen, imsar, aqa ffɣent-i-dd temɣarin zi marra tineddam n Israil i umsagar ak-d Cawul uca ɣennjent u ceḍḥent s ibendiren, s řefraḥet u s řgambriyat s třata n ifiřan.
\v 7 Timɣarin arrint meẓri nsent, ɣennjent s nnubtat, nnant: “Cawul iɣřeb x řuřuf nnes, maca Dawud x ɛecra n řuřuf nnes!” \x ◘ \xo 18:7 \xt Uf. 15:21; 1 Ṣm. 21:11; 29:5\x*
\v 8 Cawul iffugem aṭṭas. Tuɣa d man aya d řɛib di tiṭṭawin nnes, inna: “Wcint i Dawud ɛecra n řuřuf, maca wcint ayi mɣir řuřuf. \add Maca\add* teqqim as mɣir tgelda \add waha\add*?”
\v 9 Zeg wass nni sennej ibda Cawul iḥeṭṭa Dawud.
\m 
\v 10 Tiwecca nnes imsar, aqa iwḍa-dd ɛawed řaryaḥ d aɛeffan n AREBBI x Cawul, u idweř ittekk x uzeǧif di taddart nnes, am tuɣa ittirar Dawud am wussan nneɣni s ufus nnes \add x řgambri\add*. Cawul tuɣa ɣares lansa deg ufus.
\v 11 Cawul inḍar lansa, inna: “Necc ad řeqfeɣ Dawud u \add ad t semmareɣ\add* ɣar řḥiḍ.” Izemmar Dawud ad as ixnes tnayen n twařawin.
\v 12 Tuɣa Cawul itteggʷed zi Dawud, minzi SIDI tuɣa-t ak-d Dawud, maca tuɣa ismeḥ di Cawul.
\v 13 S uyenni issiggʷej Cawul \add Dawud\add* x yixef nnes, igga i-t d ameqqran x wařef. Netta itteffeɣ u ittareggʷaḥ zzat i wudem n řgens.
\v 14 Tuɣa Dawud ifřeḥ di marra ibriden nnes u SIDI tuɣa-t akides.
\m 
\v 15 \add Umi\add* iẓra Cawul, aqa Dawud ifřeḥ, tuɣa netta itteggʷed zzat i wudem nnes.
\v 16 \add Maca\add* marra Israil d Yahuda ttexsen Dawud, minzi netta itteffeɣ u ittareggʷaḥ zzat i wudem nsen.
\m 
\v 17 Cawul inna i Dawud: “Xzar, necc ad ac wceɣ Mirab, yeǧi tameqqrant qaɛ, d tamɣart. Mɣir iři d ijj n uḍeggʷař imḥeḍ \add deg umenɣi\add* i necc u mneɣ imenɣan n SIDI.” Inna Cawul \add ak-d yixef nnes\add*: “Ḥima war ittiři ufus inu ḍidd nnes, maca afus n Ifilisṭiniyyen ad yiři ḍidd nnes.”
\v 18 Inna Dawud i Cawul: “Min ɛniɣ necc d min teɛna tudart inu d min teɛna řaǧ n baba di Israil, aqa necc ad dewřeɣ d aḍeggʷař n ujeǧid?”
\v 19 Umi dd-tiweḍ řweqt i di i ɣa temmewc Mirab, yeǧis n Cawul, d tamɣart i Dawud, imsar, aqa temmewc nettat d tamɣart i Ɛadriyil zi Maḥula.
\v 20 Mixal, yeǧis n Cawul, tuɣa tᵉttexs Dawud. Xebbaren as t i Cawul u tuɣa aya d ict n tmesřact tecna di tiṭṭawin nnes.
\v 21 Inna Cawul: “Necc ad as tt wceɣ, ḥima ad as idweř d řfex u ḥima ad yiři ufus n Ifilisṭiniyyen ḍidd nnes.” Inna Cawul i Dawud: “Ass-a tzemmared ad tdewřed d aḍeggʷař inu s tenni d wiss tnayen.” \f ◼ \fr 18:21 \fk aḍeggʷař\ft - ixs ad yini aqa Cawul iwaɛd i Dawud belli wanita ad idweř d ‘mmis nnes’ s řemrac ak-d yessis.\f*
\v 22 Yumur Cawul i imsexxaren nnes: “Siweř ak-d Dawud di tnuffra, ini: ‘Aqa cek tusid-dd i ujeǧid x řxaḍar u marra imsexxaren ttexsen cek. \add Xenni\add* dweř řexxu d aḍeggʷař n ujeǧid.’”
\v 23 Ssiwřen imsexxaren n Cawul awařen-a deg imezzuɣen n Dawud. \add Xenni\add* inna Dawud: “Ma d tamesřact tehwen di tiṭṭawin nwem ad idweř ijj d aḍeggʷař n ujeǧid? Ma war ǧiɣ d ijj n weryaz d amezřuḍ d amuqřiř?”
\v 24 Imsexxaren n Cawul ḥajan as t, nnan: “Issiweř Dawud awařen-a.”
\v 25 \add Xenni\add* inna Cawul: “Ammu i ɣa tinim i Dawud: ‘Ajeǧid war d as teɛjib ṣṣadaq, maca \add iɛjeb as\add* mya n řeɛdařeyyat n Ifilisṭiniyyen, ḥima ad intaqem zi řɛedyan n ujeǧid.” Tuɣa Cawul ittxarraṣ ad ineɣ Dawud s ufus n Ifilisṭiniyyen.
\m 
\v 26 Ixeddamen nnes ɛawden awařen-a i Dawud. \add Xenni\add* tuɣa aya d ict n tmesřact tecna di tiṭṭawin n Dawud, ḥima ad idweř d aḍeggʷar n ujeǧid. Řmijař n wussan \add ittwaggen\add* tuɣa ɛad war ɛdun.
\v 27 \add Xenni\add* ikkar Dawud. Netta d yeryazen nnes ṭṭfen abrid, uca iwta netta mitayen n yeryazen n Ifilisṭiniyyen. Yiwi-dd Dawud řeɛdařeyyat nsen u s uya sedden nitni qaɛ \add řqedd-a\add* i ujeǧid, ḥima ad idweř d aḍeggʷař n ujeǧid. \add Xenni\add* iwca as Cawul yeǧis Mixal d tamɣart. \x ◘ \xo 18:27 \xt 2 Ṣm. 3:14\x*
\v 28 Cawul iẓra u issen, aqa SIDI tuɣa-t ak-d Dawud, u Mixal, yeǧis n Cawul, tuɣa tᵉttexs i-t.
\v 29 Idweř Cawul iggʷed ɛad ktar zi Dawud uca Cawul idweř d řeɛdu n Dawud marra ussan \add n tudart nnes\add*.
\m 
\v 30 Umi dd-ffɣen řḥukkam n Ifilisṭiniyyen, imsar, meřmi ma ffɣen tuɣa Dawud yarenni mahu di wefřaḥ nnes x marra imsexxaren n Cawul, ařami idweř isem nnes icennɛen ař ṭṭarf.
\b
\b
\c 19
\s1 Dawud yarweř zi Cawul
\m 
\v 1 Issiweř Cawul ak-d mmis Yunatan u ak-d imsexxaren nnes belli ittxeṣṣa ad nɣen Dawud. \add Maca\add* Yunatan, mmis n Cawul, tuɣa issɛizz xas Dawud aṭṭas.
\v 2 Iḥaja Yunatan x uya i Dawud, inna: “Baba Cawul yarezzu ad cek ineɣ. Xenni řexxu, raja ař tiwecca. Adef ɣar wemcan n usneffar u xemmeř ixef nnec.
\v 3 Necc ad ffɣeɣ, ad beddeɣ ak-d baba deg weḥwic mani ɣa tiřid cek. Ad xak ssiwřeɣ ak-d baba, ad xzareɣ mammec ggurent tmesřayin. \add Xenni\add* ad cek ssargbeɣ.”
\m 
\v 4 Yunatan issiweř s tizi n Dawud ak-d babas, inna as: “Ittxeṣṣa ujeǧid war ittegg ca ddenb deg umsexxar nnes Dawud, maɣar uřa d netta war dayek iggi ca ddenb, u timegga nnes aqa atent d řefḍeř i cek aṭṭas.
\v 5 Netta isebbeř tudart nnes, iɣřeb x Ufilisṭini u SIDI yiwiḍ ijj n usenjem d ameqqran i marra Israil. Cek teẓrid t simant nnec u tfarḥed. Mayemmi texsed ad texḍid x idammen imezdagen ařami ɣa tenɣed Dawud břa ssibbet?”
\v 6 Cawul isřa ɣar Yunatan u Cawul ijjuǧ: “S tidett am iddar SIDI, netta war ittwaneqq ca!” \f ◼ \fr 19:6 \fk ɣar Yunatan\ft - s Tɛibranit ‘ɣar tmijja n Yunatan’.\f*
\v 7 Uca iřaɣa Yunatan x Dawud, iḥaja as Yunatan marra awařen-a. \add Xenni\add* indeh Yunatan Dawud ɣar Cawul u netta tuɣa-t zzat i wudem nnes am iḍennaḍ d fariḍennaḍ.
\m 
\v 8 Yiweḍ-dd umenɣi ɛawed uca iffeɣ Dawud, immneɣ ak-d Ifilisṭiniyyen. Netta ihettek i-ten s ict n tecti d tameqqrant u nitni ṭṭfen tarewřa zzat i wudem nnes.
\m 
\v 9 Maca řaryaḥ d aɛeffan n SIDI iwḍa-dd \add ɛawed\add* x Cawul. Umi netta iqqim di taddart nnes, imneɛ lansa deg ufus nnes umi tuɣa Dawud ittirar s ufus nnes \add x řgambri\add*. \x ◘ \xo 19:9 \xt 1 Ṣm. 16:14; 18:10\x*
\v 10 Cawul tuɣa yarezzu ad isemmar Dawud di řḥiḍ s lansa nnes, maca netta ixnes as i Cawul u netta iřqef řḥiḍ s lansa. Dawud yarweř, issenjem ixef nnes ǧiřet nni.
\m 
\v 11 Issekk Cawul ireqqasen ɣar taddart n Dawud, ḥima ad t ḥḍan u ad t nɣen ɣar tuffut. \add Maca\add* Mixal, tamɣart n Dawud, tḥaja \add xas\add* i Dawud, tenna: “Mařa cek war tessnejmed ixef nnec di ǧiřet-a, ad tᵉttwanɣed tiwecca.”
\v 12 Mixal tessehwa Dawud zi řkazi. \add Xenni\add* yuyur, yarweř uca issenjem ixef nnes.
\v 13 \add Xenni\add* teksi Mixal ijj n řexyař n ṣṣanam, tessars \add i-t\add* di qama uca tegga ict n thiḍurt n cɛar n iɣayḍ ɣar mani iǧa uzeǧif u tedřa \add i-t\add* s yijj n warruḍ.
\m 
\v 14 Cawul issekk ireqqasen maḥend ad dd-awyen Dawud, \add maca\add* nettat tenna: “Netta ihřec.”
\v 15 \add Xenni\add* issekk Cawul ireqqasen maḥend ad ssijjen x Dawud, inna: “Awyem t-i-dd di tassut ɣari da, ḥima ad t nɣeɣ.”
\v 16 Umi dd-usin ireqqasen, xzar, aqa din ijj n řexyař n ṣṣanam di qama d ict n thiḍurt n cɛar n iɣayḍ ɣar mani iǧa uzeǧif nnes.
\v 17 Uca inna Cawul i Mixal: “Mayemmi d ayi teɣdared ammu, tejjid řeɛdu inu ad yarweř, ařami issenjem ixef nnes?” Mixal tarra-dd x Cawul: “Netta inna ayi: ‘Ejj ayi ad uyureɣ, mayemmi i cem i ɣa nɣeɣ?’”
\m 
\v 18 Ammu yarweř Dawud, issenjem ixef nnes uca yusa-dd ɣar Camwil di Rama, iḥaja as marra min tuɣa i d as igga Cawul. Xenni yuyur netta \add jmiɛ\add* ak-d Camwil, qqimen di Nayut.
\v 19 Uca ḥajan aya i Cawul, nnan: “Dawud aqa-t di Nayut ɣar Rama.”
\v 20 \add Xenni\add* issekk Cawul ireqqasen, ḥima ad awyen Dawud. Nitni ẓrin tarbiɛt n inabiyyen nni ittnebban. Tuɣa Camwil ibedd ɣarsen d ameḥḍay, uca ihwa-dd Arruḥ n AREBBI x ireqqasen n Cawul ařami uřa d nitni bdan ad nebban.
\v 21 \add Umi\add* ittwanna \add aya\add* i Cawul, issekk netta ireqqasen nneɣni, maca uřa d nitni bdan ad nebban. Yarni Cawul deg usekki n ireqqasen i twařa wiss třata, uca uřa d nitni bdan ad nebban.
\v 22 \add Xas uca\add* yuyur netta simant nnes ɣar Rama. Yiweḍ netta ɣar wanu ameqqran di Sixu, isseqsa, inna: “Mani \add ǧan\add* Camwil d Dawud?” Nnan as: “Xzar, \add aqa aten\add* di Nayut ɣar Rama.”
\v 23 \add Xenni\add* yuyur din ɣar Nayut ɣar Rama, u ihwa-dd xas Arruḥ n AREBBI. Netta tuɣa iggur am ittnebba ař dd-yiweḍ ɣar Nayut ɣar Rama.
\v 24 Uřa d netta ikkes arruḍ nnes uca uřa d netta ittnebba zzat i wudem n Camwil. Ass nni d ǧiřet tmun izzeř din d aqeddid. X uya qqaren: “Ma uřa d Cawul jar inabiyyen?”
\b
\b
\c 20
\s1 Řɛahd jar Dawud d Yunatan
\m 
\v 1 Dawud yarweř zi Nayut tenni ɣar Rama uca yusa-dd ɣar Yunatan, inna: “Min ggiɣ necc? Man ljarima inu d ddenb i d as ggiɣ i babac, aqa netta ixs ad zzayi ikkes tudart?”
\v 2 Inna as Yunatan: “War xas nessiweř! Cek war tᵉttmettid ca. Xzar baba war ittegg walu, uřa d ict n řḥajjet d tameqqrant niɣ tameẓyant, břa ma i d ayi tt ɣa issargeb. Mayemmi baba zzayi i ɣa issnuffar tamesřact-a? Aya war izemmar.”
\v 3 \add Xenni\add* ijjuǧ as Dawud twařa nneɣnit, inna: “Babac issen nican, aqa ufiɣ řxaḍar di tiṭṭawin nnec. \add X uya\add* inna: ‘War ttejji ad issen Yunatan man aya, ḥima war ikessi s wemnus!’ \add X uya\add*, s tidett am iddar SIDI u am ddareɣ necc, aqa din jar ayi d řmewt mɣir ijj n uṣurif waha!”
\m 
\v 4 Yunatan inna i Dawud: “Min \add iǧan\add* deg wuř nnec, necc ad ac t ggeɣ.”
\v 5 Dawud yarra-dd x Yunatan: “Xzar, tiwecca ad ibedd uyur uca ittxeṣṣa ayi ad qqimeɣ \add ɣar ṭṭabřa\add* ak-d ujeǧid ad cceɣ. Ewc ayi ttesřiḥ ḥima ad uyureɣ maḥend ad nuffareɣ deg iyyar ař tameddit wiss třata.
\v 6 Mařa yarzu xafi babac, ifqed ayi, xenni ini: ‘Dawud iḥeccem ayi s waṭṭas ḥima izemmar ad iraḥ ɣar tendint nnes deɣya, ɣar Bayt-Laḥm, minzi dinni i ɣa tiři tɣarṣt n useggʷas i marra řaǧ.’
\v 7 Mařa netta xenni inna: ‘Mliḥ!’, ad yiři řehna i umsexxar nnec, maca mařa yarɣa ufugem nnes, xenni ad tessned, aqa netta igga di řbař nnes ad \add d ayi\add* igg řɣar.
\v 8 Egg s tmexsiwt icewwaren ak-d umsexxar nnec, minzi tessidfed amsexxar nnec akidek deg ijj n řɛahd n SIDI. \add Maca\add* mařa ggiɣ ict n ljarima, neɣ ayi cek. Mayemmi texsed ad ayi tawyed ɣar babac?” \x ◘ \xo 20:8 \xt 1 Ṣm. 18:3\x*
\v 9 Inna Yunatan: “Aqa man aya iggʷej xak! Minzi waxxa aregbeɣ xas, aqa baba igga di řbař nnes ad dayek igg řɣar, ma xenni necc war d ac t qqareɣ?”
\v 10 Inna Dawud i Yunatan: “Man wen i d ayi dd ɣa yawyen areqqas, mařa iwca ac babac ict n temwarrit teqseḥ?”
\v 11 \add Xenni\add* inna Yunatan i Dawud: “As-dd, ejj aneɣ ad neffeɣ barra ɣar yeyyar.” Uca ffɣen nitni s tnayen idsen, ɣar yeyyar barra.
\m 
\v 12 Inna Yunatan i Dawud: “\add Jjuǧeɣ ɣar\add* SIDI, AREBBI n Israil, mařa necc tiwecca niɣ farwicca ɣar řweqt-a, aqa wtiɣ řeḥsab ammu d wammu \add zi jjihet\add* n baba, ufiɣ aqa mliḥ i Dawud uca xenni necc war ssekkiɣ \add ḥed\add* ad ac \add t\add* yini,
\v 13 xenni ad igg SIDI ta d ta s Yunatan u ad dayes yarni ɛad. \add Maca\add* mařa ittɣiř as mliḥ i baba ad dayek igg řɣar, xenni necc ad ac t iniɣ, ad cek jjeɣ ad teffɣed ḥima \add tzemmared\add* ad tuyured di řehna. SIDI ad yiři akidek am mammec i tuɣa ak-d baba.
\v 14 \add Uca xak,\add* war ittiři \add waha\add* am ddareɣ, war ittiři \add xenni waha\add* ad ayi tessecned tamexsiwt icewwaren n SIDI ḥima war ttmettiɣ ca,
\v 15 \add maca ɛad\add* war tqeṭṭɛed tamexsiwt nnec icewwaren i řebda x taddart inu, uřa xmi ɣa iqḍeɛ SIDI marra řɛedyan n Dawud zeg wudem n temmurt!”
\v 16 Uca igga Yunatan ijj n řɛahd ak-d taddart n Dawud uca SIDI ittar i-t zeg ufus n řɛedyan n Dawud.
\v 17 Yunatan ijja Dawud ad ijjaǧ twařa nneɣnit, minzi netta tuɣa ittexs i-t, aqa ittexs i-t am mammec tuɣa ittexs ixef nnes.
\m 
\v 18 \add Xas uca\add* inna as Yunatan: “Tiwecca d ayur amaynu u nitni war cek ttifen, maɣar řkursi nnec ad iqqim ixwa.
\v 19 Awarni ɛdun třata n wussan ittxeṣṣa ad tehwid qaɛ, ad truḥed ɣar wemcan mani tuɣa tennuffared deg wass nni di yarzu netta ad cek ineɣ, u qqim ɣar uɣezdis n weẓru n Ha’izil.
\v 20 Necc ad wteɣ třata n fřitcat zzates axmi xseɣ ad řeqfeɣ tandayt.
\v 21 Xzar, necc ad ssekkeɣ aḥudri \add awarni asent\add*, ad as iniɣ: ‘Uyur, arzu x fřitcat!’ Mařa necc ad iniɣ nican i uḥudri: ‘Ḥḍa, fřitcat aqa \add udsent\add* ɣar uɣezdis-a zi ɣarek!’, \add xenni\add* awyi tent-i-dd, as-dd, maɣar aqa din řehna i cek u war din walu, \add s tidett am\add* iddar SIDI!
\v 22 \add Maca\add* mařa necc nniɣ i uḥudri: ‘Xẓar, fřitcat aqa aggʷejent xak \add ɛad\add* ktar!’, xenni aggʷej, maɣar SIDI issekka cek ɣar řaggʷaj.
\v 23 Uca \add x\add* wawař i nekkes, necc d cek, aqa SIDI ad yiři \add d acehhad\add* jar ayi d cek i řebda!”
\m 
\v 24 Issnuffar Dawud ixef nnes barra deg iyyar. Řami dd-yusa uyur amaynu iqqim ujeǧid \add ɣar ṭṭabřa\add* ḥima ad icc.
\v 25 Tuɣa ajeǧid iqqim ɣar umensi-ya deg wemcan nnes am mammec \add tuɣa iqqim\add* ɣar imensiyyen inneɣni, di řkursi \add i iǧan\add* ɣar řḥiḍ. Yunatan ikkar u Abnir iqqim ɣar uɣezdis n Cawul u řkursi n Dawud iban-dd ixwa.
\v 26 Deg wass nni Cawul war ini walu, maɣar netta inna \add deg ixef nnes\add*: “Imsar as ca ařami netta war iǧi d amezdag. Aqa nican netta war iǧi d amezdag.”
\m 
\v 27 Tiwecca nnes, deg wass wiss tnayen awarni i uyur amaynu, umi iqqim řkursi n Dawud ixwa \add ɛawed\add*, imsar, aqa inna Cawul i mmis Yunatan: “Mayemmi mmis n Yassa war dd-yusi iḍennaḍ d wass-a ɣar umensi?”
\v 28 Yunatan yarra-dd x Cawul: “Dawud iḥeccem ayi aṭṭas \add maḥend izemmar ad iraḥ\add* ɣar Bayt-Laḥm.
\v 29 Netta inna: ‘Ejj ayi ad uyureɣ, maɣar neccin ad negg ict n tɣarṣt n řaǧ nneɣ di tendint. Uma igga xafi \add ad ḥḍareɣ\add*. Mařa \add xenni\add* ufiɣ řexxu arḍa di tiṭṭawin nnec, ttzawageɣ, ejj ayi ad uyureɣ ḥima ad ẓareɣ aytma.’ X uya war dd-yusi Dawud ɣar ṭṭabřa n ujeǧid.”
\m 
\v 30 \add Xenni\add* yareɣ uxeyyeq n Cawul x Yunatan, inna as: “Cek, mmis n \add temɣart\add* iɣennan ifarɣen, necc ssneɣ mliḥ, aqa cek tixḍared aɣezdis n mmis n Yassa. D man aya d řefḍiḥet i cek d řefḍiḥet i tuɛɛaryent n yemmac!
\v 31 Minzi marra ussan min ɣa yekk mmis n Yassa iddar x temmurt, war tbeddid cek uřa d tageldit nnec. Xenni řexxu, sekk \add ijjen\add*, awyi t-i-dd ɣari, maɣar netta d mmis n řmewt.”
\m 
\v 32 Yarra-dd Yunatan x babas Cawul, inna as: “Mayemmi ittxeṣṣa ad ittwaneɣ netta? Min igga?”
\v 33 \add Xenni\add* iḥejjar i-t Cawul s lansa nnes, ḥima ad t iřqef. Ammu i issen Yunatan, aqa babas tuɣa igga di řbař nnes ad ineɣ Dawud.
\v 34 Ikkar Yunatan x ṭṭabřa umi yarɣa uxeyyeq \add nnes\add*, war icci aɣrum deg wass wiss tnayen n uyur amaynu, maɣar netta tuɣa ikessi s wemnus i Dawud, minzi babas tuɣa issbehdeř i-t ammu.
\m 
\v 35 Tiwecca nnes ɣar tuffut, imsar aqa Yunatan yuyur barra deg iyyar, di řweqt i igga amsagar ak-d Dawud u tuɣa akides ijj n uḥudri d ameẓyan.
\v 36 Netta inna i uḥudri: “Uyur, arzu x fřitcat nni ɣa wteɣ.” Aḥudri yuzzeř u netta iwta ict n fřitca tekka sennej nnes.
\v 37 \add Umi\add* dd-yiweḍ uḥudri ɣar wemcan mani teǧa fřitca, iřaɣa-dd Yunatan awarni i uḥudri, inna: “Ma war tewḍi fřitca zzayek aɣirin ɛad?”
\v 38 Iřaɣa Yunatan \add ɛawed\add* i uḥudri “Deɣya, azzeř, war ttbeddi!” Aḥudri \add i iǧan\add* ak-d Yunatan issmun fřitca uca iɛqeb ɣar bab nnes.
\v 39 Aḥudri war issin walu. Mɣir Yunatan d Dawud ssnen x tmesřact \add jar asen\add*.
\v 40 \add Xenni\add* iwca Yunatan řeqcuɛ \add n řesnaḥ nnes\add* i uḥudri i tuɣa ɣares iǧan, inna as: “Uyur, arr i-ten ɣar tendint!”
\v 41 \add Umi\add* yuyur uḥudri, ikkar Dawud zeg uɣezdis n ljanub, iwḍa s uɣembub nnes ɣar temmurt uca yuḍar třata n twařawin. Nitni ssudmen ayawya, run s tnayen idsen ařami Dawud yarni dayes.
\v 42 U Yunatan inna i Dawud: “Uyur di řehna. Aqa nejjuǧ s tnayen idneɣ s Yisem n SIDI, nenna: ‘Ad yiři SIDI d acehhad jar ayi d cek, jar zzariɛet inu d zzariɛet nnec i řebda!’”
\b
\b
\c 21
\s1 Dawud di Nub
\m 
\v 1 Xenni ikkar \add Dawud\add*, yuyur, uca yudef Yunatan ɣar tendint.
\v 2 \add Xenni\add* yiweḍ Dawud ɣar Nub ɣar ukehhan Aximalik. Aximalik iffeɣ-dd ɣar Dawud yarjef, inna as: “Mayemmi cek weḥḥdek, war kidek uřa d ijj?”
\v 3 Dawud inna i ukehhan Aximalik: “Ajeǧid iwca ayi ijj n wareqqas, inna ayi: ‘Uřa d ijj war ittriggib x tmesřact i d ac dd-ssekkeɣ u xak ggiɣ!’ Sargbeɣ i imsexxaren aqa \add ad ruḥen\add* ɣar wemcan-a d wemcan-in.
\v 4 Xenni řexxu, min ɣarek? Ewc ayi xemsa n tecnifin deg ufus niɣ min ma tzemmared ad tafed.”
\m 
\v 5 Akehhan yarra-dd x Dawud, inna: “War din aɣrum i macca ɣar ufus, mɣir aɣrum amqeddes waha i da. Meɛlik imsexxaren tuɣa ttaggʷejen waha x temɣarin!”
\v 6 Dawud yarra-dd x ukehhan, inna as: “S tidett, timɣarin ttwaḥeyydent xaneɣ am mammec teǧa lqaɛida zeg wami ffɣeɣ, u řeqcuɛ n imsexxaren ttwaqeddsen. Waxxa amenni manawya d ijj n wuffuɣ am řebda, aqa uffuɣ-a ittwaqeddes ass-a s řeqcuɛ.”
\m 
\v 7 \add Xenni\add* iwca as ukehhan \add aɣrum\add* iqeddsen, maɣar war tuɣi dinni aɣrum mɣir aɣrum n wescan nni ittwakkes zi zzat i wudem n SIDI, ḥima ad ssarsen deg wemcan nnes aɣrum iḥma deg wass nni ittwakkes. \x ◘ \xo 21:7 \xt Mt. 12:3; Mk. 2:25; Lk. 6:3\x*
\v 8 Deg wass nni tuɣa dinni ijj zeg imsexxaren n Cawul. Netta tuɣa ittwaḥṣar dinni zzat i wudem n SIDI. Qqaren as Duwaɛ, zi Idum. Netta tuɣa ɣares ṣṣulṭa aṭṭas jar imeksawen inni \add iǧan\add* ɣar Cawul.
\v 9 Uca inna Dawud i Aximalik: “Ma war da ɣarek ict n lansa niɣ ijj n ssif ɣar ufus? Maɣar war kidi ksiɣ ssif d řesnaḥ inu deg ufus inu, minzi tamesřact n ujeǧid tuɣa tᵉttqeǧiq.”
\m 
\v 10 Inna ukehhan: “Ssif n Julyat, Afilisṭini wenni x tɣeřbed di Řewḍa n Teɣzurt n Ila, aqa-t \add da\add*, ittwanneḍ deg ijj n warruḍ awarni i upalṭu n ikehhanen. Mařa texsed ad t teksid, ksi t, minzi war da walu mɣir wanita.” Inna Dawud: “War iǧi ijj am netta! Ewc ayi t!”
\b
\s1 Dawud di Jat
\m 
\v 11 Ikkar Dawud, yarweř deg wass nni zzat i wudem n Cawul uca netta yusa-dd ɣar Axic, ajeǧid n Jat.
\v 12 Imsexxaren n Axic nnan as: “Ma wanita war iǧi d Dawud, ajeǧid n temmurt? Ma war iǧi d wenni zi ɣennjent, ceḍḥent temɣarin s nnubtat, qqarent: ‘Cawul iɣřeb x řuřuf nnes, maca Dawud x ɛecra n řuřuf nnes?’”\x ◘ \xo 21:12 \xt 1 Ṣm. 18:7\x*
\v 13 Dawud yarra awařen-a ɣar wuř nnes u tuɣa itteggʷed aṭṭas zzat i wudem n Axic, ajeǧid n Jat.
\v 14 \add Xenni\add* igga ixef nnes axmi iweddar řeɛqeř nnes zzat i tiṭṭawin nsen, igga axmi ijjen dayes aṭemmes umi xas ssarsen ifassen, uca ibda ixebbec di tewwura n tewwart \add n tendint\add*, ijja ikuffan nnes hekkwan-dd x tmart nnes.
\v 15 \add Xenni\add* inna Axic i imsexxaren nnes: “Xzarem, kenniw tᵉttwařam aqa aryaz ibbuhři. Mayemmi i-t-i-dd-tiwyem ɣari?”
\v 16 Ma ttxeṣṣan ayi ibuhařiyyen, aqa tiwyem-dd ɣari wanita maḥend ad ɣari igg tubbuheřya? Ma d wanita i dd ɣa yadfen ɣar taddart inu?”
\b
\b
\c 22
\s1 Dawud deg ifri n Adullam
\m 
\v 1 \add Xenni\add* yuyur Dawud ssenni, issenjem ixef nnes ɣar ifri n Adullam. Aytmas d marra taddart n babas sřan aya uca hwan ɣares dinni.
\v 2 Uca \add kuř\add* aryaz nni tuɣa di ca n řeḥṣaret u \add kuř\add* aryaz i di tuɣa iǧa umarwas u \add kuř\add* aryaz s řbař d amerzag, aqa \add marra\add* nitni ffɣen ɣares uca netta idweř d amgewwed nsen. Tuɣa ɣares řqedd n arebɛa-mya n yeryazen.
\v 3 Ssenni iffeɣ Dawud ɣar Miṣfat di Mu’ab. Inna netta i ujeǧid n Mu’ab: “Ejj baba d yemma ad ɣarwem dd-asen, ař ɣa ssneɣ min kidi i ɣa yegg SIDI.”
\m 
\v 4 Netta yiwyi ten zzat i wudem n ujeǧid n Mu’ab uca nitni qqimen ɣares marra ussan i di ikka Dawud di lburj \add deg idurar\add*.
\v 5 \add Maca\add* anabi Jat inna i Dawud: “War ttɣimi di lburj \add deg idurar\add*, maca aggʷej, ad tadfed ɣar temmurt n Yahuda!” \add Xenni\add* yuyur Dawud, yiweḍ ɣar wezɣar n Ḥarit. \f ◼ \fr 22:5 \fk azɣar\ft - niɣ ‘řɣabet’ niɣ ‘tazgant’.\f*
\b
\s1 Tamenɣiwt n ikehhanen n Nub
\m 
\v 6 Cawul isřa belli Dawud d iryazen, inni tuɣa ɣares \add iǧan\add*, ttwafen. Tuɣa Cawul iqqim di Jibɛa sadu ict n tcejjart n tmarist ɣar Rama. Tuɣa ɣares ict n lansa deg ufus nnes u marra imsexxaren nnes bedden ɣares. \f ◼ \fr 22:6 \fk tacejjart n tmarist\ft - s tlatinit ‘Tamarix’.\f*
\v 7 Inna Cawul i imsexxaren nnes i ɣares ibedden: “Ttzawgeɣ, sřem, kenniw ayt n Binyamin! Ma ad iwc mmis n Yassa iyyaren d imarjaɛen n uḍiř i kenniw marra? Ma ad yarr kenniw marra d imeqqranen x wařef d imeqqranen x mya?
\v 8 Aqa kenniw marra teggim xafi tameɛmuč uca uřa d ijjen war d ayi issargeb belli mmi igga ijj n řɛahd ak-d mmis n Yassa uca uřa d ijj zzaywem war d as cqiɣ, war d ayi tessargbem aqa mmi issamar amsexxar inu xafi maḥend ad xafi izeyyar s tḥraymect am mammec \add iǧa\add* ass-a.”
\m 
\v 9 \add Xenni\add* yarra-dd Duwaɛ, wenni iǧan zi Idum, wenni d ameḥḍay x imsexxaren n Cawul, inna: “Necc ẓriɣ mmis n Yassa řami dd-yusa di Nub ɣar Aximalik, mmis n Axiṭub.
\v 10 Netta ittar SIDI di ṭṭweɛ nnes, iwca as macca uřa d ssif n Julyat, Afilisṭini.”
\v 11 \add Xas uca\add* issekk ujeǧid \add ijj\add* maḥend ad dd-iřaɣa x ukehhan Aximalik, mmis n Axiṭub, \add jmiɛ\add* ak-d marra taddart n babas, ikehhanen, inni \add iǧan\add* di Nub. Uca marra usin-dd ɣar ujeǧid.
\m 
\v 12 Inna Cawul: “Seř, cek, mmis n Axiṭub!” Netta yarra-dd: “Xzar, aqa ayi da, a sidi inu!”
\v 13 Cawul inna as: “Mayemmi xafi teggim tameɛmuč, cek d mmis n Yassa, aqa cek tewcid as macca d ssif u tᵉttared AREBBI di ṭṭweɛ nnes ḥima ad xafi iɣewweɣ u ad xafi izeyyar, am mammec \add iǧa\add* ass-a.”
\v 14 Yarra-dd Aximalik x ujeǧid, inna: “Man wen zi marra imsexxaren nnec d amtiqqi am Dawud, aḍeggʷař n ujeǧid, u \add man wen\add* i ɣa yawḍen \add amenni\add* ɣar imtiqqan nnec u wi ɣar iǧa ccan \add ammu\add* di taddart nnec?
\v 15 Ma ass-a waha i kkareɣ ad ttareɣ SIDI di ṭṭweɛ nnes? Aqa man aya iggʷej xafi. Ejj ajeǧid war ineṭṭar řbaṭeř x umsexxar nnes niɣ x marra taddart n baba di ssibbet n ca n řḥajjet, minzi amsexxar nnec war issin walu x marra aya, ma \add d tamesřact\add* d tameẓyant niɣ d tameqqrant \add i teǧa\add*.”
\v 16 \add Maca\add* ajeǧid inna: “Cek s tidett ad temmted, \add a\add* Aximalik, cek d marra taddart n babac.”
\v 17 Ajeǧid inna i iřeqqasen n tazřa nni ɣares-dd ibedden: “Nqeřbem u nɣem ikehhanen n SIDI, maɣar uřa d nitni wcin afus i Dawud, minzi nitni ssnen aqa netta tuɣa ittrakkwař u nitni war d ayi xas ssargben ca.” \add Maca\add* imsexxaren n ujeǧid war xsen ad sswiẓẓḍen afus nsen, ḥima ad zzayes wten ikehhanen n SIDI.
\v 18 \add Xenni\add* inna ujeǧid i Duwaɛ: “Neqřeb, wwet ikehhanen!” \add Xenni\add* inneqřeb Duwaɛ, wenni iǧan zi Idum, iwta ikehhanen. Deg wass nni inɣa netta xemsa u-tmanyin n yeryazen nni yarḍen apalṭu \add n ukehhan\add*.
\v 19 Netta iwta uřa d Nub, tandint n ikehhanen, s řeqḍeɛ n ssif, iryazen d temɣarin, iḥenjiren d iseyman. Iwta ɛawed ifunasen d yeɣyař d wuǧi s řeqḍeɛ n ssif.
\v 20 Ijj zeg warraw n Aximalik, mmis n Axiṭub, issenjem ixef nnes. \add Tuɣa\add* isem nnes Abyatar u netta iqeǧeq \add ixef nnes\add* awarni i Dawud.
\m 
\v 21 Abyatar iḥaja i Dawud, aqa Cawul tuɣa inɣa ikehhanen n SIDI.
\v 22 \add Xenni\add* inna Dawud i Abyatar: “Deg wass nni, umi tuɣa Duwaɛ zi Idum dinni, ssneɣ aqa netta ad iḥaja aya i Cawul. Necc d wenni x \add iǧan\add* marra řeɛmur n taddart n babac.
\v 23 Qim ɣari, war tteggʷed ca, maɣar wenni yarezzun \add ad ineɣ\add* řeɛmar inu, yarezzu \add ad ineɣ\add* uřa d řeɛmar nnec. Aqa cek \add ɛawed\add* ɣari di řaman.”
\b
\b
\c 23
\s1 Dawud di Qaɛila
\m 
\v 1 Ḥajan i Dawud, nnan: “Aqa Ifilisṭiniyyen ttmenɣan ak-d Qaɛila uca ttkeccaḍen inedrar.”
\v 2 Isseqsa Dawud SIDI, inna: “Ma ad ffɣeɣ din, ad wteɣ Ifilisṭiniyyen?” SIDI yarra-dd x Dawud: “Ffeɣ, wwet Ifilisṭiniyyen uca fekk Qaɛila!”
\v 3 Nnan as yeryazen n Dawud: “Xzar, neccin nᵉtteggʷed \add deɣya\add* da di Yahuda, mammec ɛad mařa neccin neffeɣ ɣar Qaɛila ɣar iseddiyyen n řɛeskar n Ifilisṭiniyyen.”
\v 4 Uca Dawud isseqsa SIDI twařa nneɣnit u SIDI yarra-dd xas, inna: “Kkar, hwa ɣar Qaɛila, minzi Necc ad ac wceɣ Ifilisṭiniyyen deg ifassen \add nnec\add*.”
\v 5 \add Xas uca\add* iffeɣ Dawud ak-d yeryazen nnes ɣar Qaɛila, immneɣ ak-d Ifilisṭiniyyen. Netta yuẓẓeř x tḥimarin nsen uca iwta ten s ict n tecti d tameqqrant. \add Ammu i\add* ifekk Dawud imezdaɣ n Qaɛila.
\m 
\v 6 Umi Abyatar, mmis n Aximalik, yarweř ɣar Dawud ɣar Qaɛila, imsar, netta aqa ihwa ak-d upalṭu \add n ukehhan\add* deg ifassen nnes. \x ◘ \xo 23:6 \xt 1 Ṣm. 22:20\x*
\m 
\v 7 Ḥajan as i Cawul, aqa Dawud yiweḍ ɣar Qaɛila. \add Xenni\add* inna Cawul: “AREBBI igga ayi i-t deg ufus inu, minzi netta ittwaḥebbes ařami yudef ɣar ict n tendint s tewwura d iɛumad i ubelleɛ.”
\v 8 Ijja Cawul ad řaɣan x marra řgens ɣar umenɣi, ḥima ad hwan ɣar Qaɛila maḥend ad nnḍen i Dawud d yeryazen nnes.
\m 
\v 9 \add Řami\add* yargeb Dawud belli Cawul issewjed as tuɛeffna-ya s tnuffra, inna netta i ukehhan Abyatar: “Awi-dd apalṭu \add n ukehhan\add* da!”
\v 10 Inna Dawud: “\add A\add* SIDI, AREBBI n Israil, amsexxar nnec isřa nican, aqa Cawul iɛemmed ad dd-yas ɣar Qaɛila, ḥima ad ixarreb tandint di ssibbet inu.
\v 11 Ma ad ayi sseɛdun imezdaɣ n Qaɛila deg ufus nnes? Ma ad ihwa Cawul am mammec isřa umsexxar nnec? \add A\add* SIDI, AREBBI n Israil, ini t i umsexxar nnec!” SIDI yarra-dd: “Netta ad ihwa.”
\v 12 \add Xas uca\add* inna Dawud: “Ma imezdaɣ n Qaɛila ad sseɛdun necc d yeryazen inu i Cawul?” Inna SIDI “Nitni ad \add cek\add* sseɛdun.”
\v 13 \add Xas uca\add* ikkar Dawud ak-d yeryazen nnes, amenni setta mya n yeryazen, uca ffɣen nitni zi Qaɛila, dewřen gguren mani ma zemmaren ad uyuren. \add Umi\add* ittwanna i Cawul, aqa injem-dd Dawud zi Qaɛila, ijja \add zeg webrid nnes\add*, war iffiɣ ca.
\b
\s1 Dawud di řexřa n Zif
\m 
\v 14 Dawud iqqim di řexřa di lqelɛat n idurar uca iqqim x idurar di řexřa n Zif. Cawul yarzu xas marra ussan, \add maca\add* AREBBI war t iggi deg ufus nnes.
\v 15 \add Umi\add* iẓra Dawud, aqa Cawul tuɣa iffeɣ ḥima ad xas yarzu, \add tuɣa\add* Dawud di řexřa n Zif di Xurisa. \f ◼ \fr 23:15 \fk ḥima ad xas yarzu\ft - s Tɛibranit ‘ḥima ad yarzu x řeɛmar nnes’.\f*
\v 16 \add Xenni\add* ikkar Yunatan, mmis n Cawul, uca yuyur ɣar Dawud di Xurisa, issejhed afus nnes di AREBBI.
\v 17 Netta inna as: “War tteggʷed ca, minzi afus n baba Cawul war cek dd-ittikkʷiḍ u cek ad tdewřed d ajeǧid x Israil u necc ad dewřeɣ d wiss tnayen ɣarek. Uřa d baba Cawul issen aya.”
\v 18 U nitni s tnayen idsen ggin ijj n řɛahd zzat i wudem n SIDI. Dawud iqqim di Xurisa u Yunatan yareggʷeḥ ɣar taddart nnes.
\m 
\v 19 \add Xas\add* uca geɛɛden yeryazen zi Zif ɣar Cawul di Jibɛa, nnan: “Ma war innuffar Dawud ɣarneɣ di lqelɛat \add deg idurar\add* di Xurisa, x tewrirt n Ḥaxila, ɣar ljanub n tnezruft? \f ◼ \fr 23:19 \fk ɣar ljanub n tnezruft\ft - niɣ ‘ɣar yefusi n tnezruft’.\f*
\v 20 \add Xenni\add* řexxu, \add a\add* ajeǧid, hwa-dd ɛlaḥsab marra meẓri n wuř nnec. Ad tiři \add xenni\add* tmesřact nneɣ, ḥima ad t nesseɛdu ɣar ufus n ujeǧid.”
\v 21 Cawul inna: “Ad tᵉttwabarkem zi SIDI, minzi cqiɣ awem \add ammu\add*.
\v 22 Uyurem, wejdem ɛad ktar u ḥḍam u snem u xzarem amcan mani iǧa uḍar nnes u man wen i t dinni iẓrin, maɣar qqaren ayi, aqa netta d aḥraymi aṭṭas.
\v 23 Ḥḍam u ssnem marra imucan n tnuffra mani issnuffar ixef nnes u ɛeqbem mařa tkemmřem. \add Xenni\add* ad kidwem uyureɣ u mařa netta di temmurt, necc ad xas arzuɣ jar marra řuřuf n Yahuda.”
\v 24 Kkaren nitni, izzaren zzat i wudem n Cawul ɣar Zif. Dawud d yeryazen nnes tuɣa aten di řexřa n Maɛun, di Řewḍa ɣar ljanub n tnezruft.
\m 
\v 25 Cawul d yeryazen nnes ffɣen ḥima ad xas arzun. Nnan aya i Dawud u netta ihwa-dd zi řejruf di řexřa n Maɛun. \add Umi\add* t isřa Cawul, \add řexdenni\add* iḍfar netta Dawud di řexřa n Maɛun.
\v 26 Cawul ikka x ijj n uɣezdis n wedrar u Dawud d yeryazen nnes kken x uɣezdis nneɣni n wedrar. Řami iqeǧeq Dawud maḥend ad yaggʷej x wudem n Cawul, imsar, aqa Cawul d yeryazen nnes nnḍen-dd i Dawud d yeryazen nnes ḥima ad ten ṭṭfen.
\v 27 \add Maca\add* yusa-dd ijj n ureqqas ɣar Cawul inna: “Deɣya, as-dd, minzi Ifilisṭiniyyen hejmen x temmurt!”
\v 28 \add Xenni\add* iɛqeb-dd Cawul zeg weḍfar n Dawud uca iffeɣ ɣar umsagar ak-d Ifilisṭiniyyen. X uya qqaren as i wemcan nni Salaɛ-ha-Maxlikut. \f ◼ \fr 23:28 \fk Salaɛ-ha-Maxlikut\ft - isem wanita ixs ad yini ‘aseǧaḥ n ubeṭṭu’ niɣ ‘aseǧaḥ n warweř’.\f*
\b
\b
\c 24
\s1 Dawud issɛizz x tudart n Cawul
\m 
\v 1 Yuyur Dawud ssenni uca iqqim di lqelɛat \add deg idurar\add* n Ɛayn-Jadi.
\v 2 Uca imsar, umi dd-iɛqeb Cawul zeg weḍfar n Ifilisṭiniyyen, ɛawden as, nnan: “Dawud aqa-t di řexřa n Ɛayn-Jadi.”
\v 3 \add Xenni\add* iksi Cawul teřt-ařaf n yeryazen ittwafarzen zi marra Israil, iffeɣ ḥima ad yarzu x Dawud d yeryazen nnes arendad n tṣuḍar n Iɣayḍen n Řejruf.
\v 4 Netta yusa-dd ɣar řkuriyyat n wuǧi i \add iǧan\add* ɣar webrid mani tuɣa iǧa ijj n yefri. Cawul yudef ɣares, ḥima ad ideř iḍaren nnes. Tuɣa Dawud d yeryazen nnes qqimen ɣar ḍeffar deg ifri. \f ◼ \fr 24:4 \fk ḥima ad ideř iḍaren nnes\ft - awař-a ixs ad yini ‘ḥima ad ibarḍ’.\f*
\v 5 \add Xenni\add* nnan as yeryazen n Dawud: “Xzar, wa d ass i x d ac inna SIDI: ‘Xzar, Necc ad ac ggeɣ řeɛdu nnec deg ufus nnec u cek tzemmared akides tegged min tᵉttwařid nican di tiṭṭawin nnec.” Uca ikkar Dawud, iqess s tnuffra ijj n ṭṭarf zeg useřham n Cawul.
\v 6 Awarni as \add maca\add* issdewdiw uř n Dawud dayes, minzi netta tuɣa icarreg ijj n ṭṭarf \add zeg useřham\add* n Cawul.
\v 7 Netta inna i yeryazen nnes: “SIDI ad ayi iḥḍa aqa necc ad ggeɣ aya i sidi inu, i umedhun n SIDI, aqa ad sswiẓẓḍeɣ afus inu ḍidd nnes, maɣar netta d amedhun n SIDI!” \f ◼ \fr 24:7 \fk amedhun n SIDI\ft - awař-a ixs ad yini ‘wenni ittwafarzen zi SIDI umi t dehnen s zzect’.\f*
\v 8 Issiweř Dawud ak-d yeryazen nnes s wawařen iqesḥen u war ten ijji ad hejmen x Cawul. U Cawul ikkar, iffeɣ-dd zeg ifri, iṭṭef abrid.
\m 
\v 9 \add Xas uca\add* ikkar uřa d Dawud, iffeɣ-dd zeg ifri, iřaɣa-dd x Cawul, inna: “Sidi inu, ajeǧid!” U Cawul ixzar ɣar ḍeffar uca yuḍar Dawud s uɣembub \add nnes\add* ɣar temmurt, ibendeq. \f ◼ \fr 24:9 \fk s uɣembub \bdit ‘nnes’\bdit*\ft - s Tɛibranit ‘s tinzar nnes’.\f*
\v 10 Inna Dawud i Cawul: “Mayemmi tesřid ɣar wawařen n iwdan, inni iqqaren: ‘Xẓar, Dawud ixs ad ac igg řɣar?’
\v 11 Xzar ass-a teẓrid s tiṭṭawin nnec, aqa SIDI igga cek ass-a deg ifri deg ufus inu. Nnan ayi ḥima ad cek nɣeɣ, maca necc ḥawřeɣ xak, minzi nniɣ \add ak-d yixef inu\add*: ‘Necc war sswiẓẓaḍeɣ afus inu ḍidd i sidi inu, maɣar netta d amedhun n SIDI.’
\v 12 Xzar baba, ṭṭarf n useřham nnec aqa-t deg ufus inu. Umi necc carrgeɣ ijj n ṭṭarf n upartessu nnec, war cek nɣiɣ. \add Xenni\add* ssen u xzar, aqa war ɣari deg ufus inu řa d tuɛeffna uřa d axeṭṭu u necc war kik xḍiɣ ca. \add Maca\add* cek tarezzud ḥima ad ayi tekksed tudart inu. \f ◼ \fr 24:12 \fk tudart inu\ft - s Tɛibranit ‘řeɛmar inu’.\f*
\v 13 SIDI ad iḥkem jar ayi d cek uca SIDI ad intaqem i necc zzayek, \add maca\add* afus inu war ittiři xak.
\v 14 Am mammec iqqar wawař iweznen n řejdud: ‘Zeg iɛeffanen ittas-dd tuɛeffna!’, maca afus inu war ittiři ḍidd i cek.
\v 15 Awarni man wen iḍeffar ujeǧid n Israil? Man wen i tyemmared? Awarni yijj n weqzin immuten, awarni i yijj n uyenni n ucurdu!
\v 16 SIDI ad yiři d řqaḍi nneɣ u netta ad iḥkem jar ayi d cek. Netta ad ixzar \add di man aya\add* uca ad iḥkem x ddeɛwet inu u Netta ad ayi yaɣ tasɣart zeg ufus nnec.” \f ◼ \fr 24:16 \fk řqaḍi\ft - niɣ ‘amezruf’.\f*
\m 
\v 17 Umi ikemmeř Dawud x řhard n wawařen-a i Cawul, imsar, aqa Cawul inna: “Ma ta d tmijja nnec, mmi Dawud?” \add Xenni\add* issgeɛɛed Cawul tmijja nnes, iru.
\v 18 Inna netta i Dawud: “Cek d amsegged xafi necc, maɣar cek teggid akidi mliḥ, maca necc ggiɣ akidek tuɛeffna.
\v 19 Cek, \add wah\add* cek tessecned ayi ass-a, mammec d ayi teggid mliḥ, maɣar SIDI tuɣa igga ayi deg ufus nnec u cek war d ayi tenɣid ca.
\v 20 Maɣar \add mařa\add* ijj n weryaz yufa řeɛdu nnes, ma \add xenni\add* ad t yejj ad yuyur abrid \add nnes\add* di řxar? SIDI ad cek ixeǧeṣ s řxar di ssibbet n min d ayi teggid ass-a.
\v 21 Řexxu ssneɣ, aqa cek ad tdewřed d ajeǧid u tageldit n Israil ad temten s ufus nnec.
\v 22 \add X uyenni\add* jjaǧ ayi řexxu ɣar SIDI, aqa cek war tqeṭṭɛeḍ zzariɛet inu awarni ayi u war tᵉttekksed isem inu zi taddart n baba!”
\v 23 Dawud ijjuǧ i Cawul u Cawul yareggʷeḥ ɣar taddart nnes u Dawud d yeryazen nnes geɛɛden ɣar lburj \add deg idurar\add*.
\b
\b
\c 25
\s1 Dawud d Nabal ak-d Abijayil
\m 
\v 1 Camwil immut u marra Israil imun. Nitni wtin xas agejdur u neḍřen t di taddart nnes di Rama. \add Xas uca\add* ikkar Dawud, ihwa ɣar řexřa n Faran. \x ◘ \xo 25:1 \xt 1 Ṣm. 28:3\x*
\v 2 Tuɣa di Maɛun ijj n weryaz wenni tuɣa ɣar iǧa wagřa di Karmil. Aryaz tuɣa d bu-wagřa ař ṭṭarf, iǧa ɣares teřt-ařaf n wuǧi d ařef n iɣayḍen. Netta tuɣa iǧas uǧi nnes di Karmil.
\v 3 Aryaz ttřaɣan as Nabal u tamɣart nnes ttřaɣan as Abijayil. Tamɣart tuɣa ɣares řeɛqeř mliḥ u tuɣa-tt d muṣbiḥ i řxezrat, maca aryaz tuɣa iqseḥ u timegga nnes d tiɛeffanin \add i ǧant\add*. Netta tuɣa-t am wuř nnes. \f ◼ \fr 25:3 \fk Nabal\ft - isem wanita ixs ad yini ‘abuhaři’. \fk Abijayil\ft - isem wanita ixs ad yini ‘baba d řefraḥet inu’.\f*
\m 
\v 4 \add Umi\add* isřa Dawud di řexřa, aqa Nabal tuɣa iǧas uǧi nnes,
\v 5 issekk Dawud ɛecra n imsexxaren din. Inna Dawud i iḥudriyyen: “Gaɛɛdem ɣar Karmil u xmi ɣa tawḍem ɣar Nabal, ittxeṣṣa awem ad tesseqsam x umeddur nnes deg yisem inu.
\v 6 Ittxeṣṣa ad tinim ammu: ‘Iři ad xak yiři řehna uca ad yiři řehna x taddart nnec d řehna \add ɣar\add* marra min iǧan nnec!
\v 7 Aqa necc sřiɣ belli cek ɣarek irewwan. Iwa xenni, imeksawen nni ɣarek tuɣa aten akidneɣ uca neccin war ten nxewwej ca uca war ten inqiṣ walu zi min ɣarsen marra ussan i ikkin nitni \add akidneɣ\add* di Karmil.
\v 8 Seqsa imsexxaren nnec u nitni ad ac inin. Ejj ad afen imsexxaren arḍa di tiṭṭawin nnec, maɣar nusa-dd ɣar ijj n wass n wurar. Ttzawgeɣ, ewc i imsexxaren nnec u i mmic Dawud min ɣa yaf ufus nnec.’”
\m 
\v 9 \add Umi\add* iwḍen imsexxaren n Dawud \add din\add*, ssiwřen ak-d Nabal marra awařen-a deg yisem n Dawud, uca qqimen ttrajan.
\v 10 \add Maca\add* Nabal yarra-dd x imsexxaren n Dawud, inna: “Man wen i iǧan Dawud u man wen i iǧan d mmis n Yassa? Ass-a \add aqa din\add* aṭṭas n imsexxaren nni yarewřen. Kuř ijj \add yarweř\add* zi zzat n wudem n bab nnes.
\v 11 Ma ad ksiɣ xenni aɣrum inu d waman inu d tɣarṣt i ɣarṣeɣ i irewwan inu uca ad t wceɣ i yeryazen x yinni war ssineɣ uřa d manis dd-usin nitni?”
\v 12 \add Xenni\add* nnqeřben imsexxaren n Dawud ɣar webrid i zi dd-usin, ɛeqben uca usin-dd \add ɣar Dawud\add* u ḥajan as marra awařen-a. \f ◼ \fr 25:12 \fk ɣar webrid i zi dd-usin\ft - s Tɛibranit ‘ɣar webrid nsen’.\f*
\v 13 \add Xas uca\add* inna Dawud i yeryazen nnes: “Kur aryaz ad ibyes ssif nnes!” Uca \add kuř\add* aryaz ibyes ssif nnes, uřa d Dawud ibyes ssif nnes. Nitni geɛɛden awarni i Dawud, amenni arebɛa-mya n yeryazen, u qqimen mitayen ɣar řeḥwayej.
\b
\m 
\v 14 Ijjen zeg imsexxaren tuɣa iḥaja aya i Abijayil, tamɣart n Nabal, inna \add as\add*: “Xzar, Dawud issekk-dd ireqqasen zi řexřa ḥima ad ssiwḍen lbaraka i siditneɣ, maca wanita iqřeɛ xasen s tzawart.
\v 15 Iryazen tuɣa aten cnan i neccin u nitni war d aneɣ seddɛen ca. War nefqid walu marra ussan i dinni nesseɛdu akidsen deg iyyar n tarewsa.
\v 16 Nitni tuɣa aten am yijj n řḥiḍ i neccin, ǧiřet d wass, di marra ussan i kidsen neǧa u tuɣa neccin narwes uǧi.
\v 17 Řexxu aqa tessned tt. Xzar mliḥ, min ittxeṣṣa ad t tegged, maɣar řɣar x siditneɣ d marra taddart nnes imten. Netta d ijj n weryaz war isekkwi wawař akides.”
\v 18 Tqeǧeq Abijayil, teksi mitayen n tecnifin d tnayen n txuncay n yiřem i binu d xemsa n texsiwin wejdent d xemsa n řeqyas n teɣwawin d mya n tɣayiṭatin n zzbib d mitayen n iɣrumen n tazart, u nettat tessars manawenni marra x yeɣyař. \f ◼ \fr 25:18 \fk řeqyas\ft - ɛřayen 7-8 litru.\f*
\v 19 Tenna i imsexxaren nnes: “Uyurem zzat i wudem inu. Xzar necc ad kenniw aredfeɣ.” \add Maca\add* nettat war d as tenni aya i weryaz nnes Nabal. \f ◼ \fr 25:19 \fk Uyurum\ft - s Tɛibranit ‘Ẓwam’.\f*
\m 
\v 20 Umi tenya nettat x weɣyuř, tehwa x udurri n wedrar, xzar, imsar aqa Dawud d yeryazen nnes hwan-dd i umsagar akides u nettat temmeřqa akidsen.
\v 21 Dawud tuɣa inna: “S tidett, baṭeř i ḥḍiɣ x marra min ɣares iǧan di řexřa, ařami war iweddar walu zi min ɣares. Netta ixeǧeṣ ayi min iṣebḥen s min war iḥřin.
\v 22 Ejj ad igg AREBBI ta d ta ak-d řɛedyan n Dawud u ad dayes yarni ɛad, mařa necc ad jjeɣ ař tiwecca uřa d ijj wenni t itteggen x řḥiḍ zi marra min ɣares!”
\m 
\v 23 Umi teẓra Abijayil Dawud, teḍra deɣya x weɣyuř nnes, tewḍa \add x temmurt\add* zzat i Dawud, tuḍar \add as\add* s uɣembub nnes ɣar temmurt.
\v 24 Nettat tewḍa as ɣar iḍaren, tenna: “Necc, waha, i di iǧa řɛib, \add a\add* Sidi inu. Ejj ad tessiweř tayya nnec akidek u seř i wawařen n tayya nnec.
\v 25 Ejj sidi inu war ixezzar ɣar weryaz-a i war isekkwin, ɣar Nabal, maɣar am mammec d as qqaren, ammu \add i yeǧa\add* netta. Nabal d isem nnes u tubbuheřya aqa-tt dayes. \bd Necc\bd*, tayya nnec, war ẓriɣ ca imsexxaren n sidi inu i dd-tessekked.
\v 26 Xenni řexxu, a sidi, \add s tidett\add* am iddar SIDI u iddar řeɛmar nnec, aqa SIDI d wenni cek immenɛen maḥend ad tessizzřed idammen u ad tfekked ixef nnec s ufus nnec. Ad dewřen řexxu řɛedyan nnec d yinni yarezzun ad ggen řɣar di sidi inu am Nabal.
\v 27 Iwa řexxu, man aya d lbaraka i dd-tiwi tayya nnec i sidi inu, maḥend ad tt wcen i imsexxaren nni yuyuren deg iṣuraf n sidi inu.
\v 28 Ttzawgeɣ, ɣfar axeṭṭu i tayya nnec, maɣar SIDI \add Arebbi\add* ad issbedd i sidi inu ict n taddart temten, minzi sidi inu ittegg garrat n SIDI u war dayek ittwaff řɣar zeg wussan \add imezwura\add* nnec.
\v 29 \add Mařa\add* ijj n bnadem ikkar xak ḥima ad cek iḍfar, ḥima ad yarzu x řeɛmar nnec, xenni ad yiři řeɛmar n sidi inu \add di řaman,\add* iqqen di tecyart n yinni iddaren ɣar SIDI AREBBI nnec, \add maca\add* řeɛmar n řɛedyan nnec ad zzayes iḥejjar netta ɣar řaggʷaj zeg ukemmic n iǧiy.
\v 30 Ad imsar, mařa SIDI ad igg ak-d sidi inu ɛlaḥsab marra taṣebḥant i xak issiweř u ad cek yegg d řḥakem x Israil,
\v 31 xenni war ittiři aya i cek, \add a\add* sidi inu, d ssibbet i zi ɣa tenqarḍed uřa d taɛenkrift i wuř, aqa cek tessizzřed idammen baṭeř u aqa sidi inu igga ad ifekk ixef nnes. Mařa SIDI \add AREBBI\add* ad igg řxar di sidi inu, ɛqeř \add xenni\add* x tayya nnec.”
\m 
\v 32 \add Xenni\add* inna Dawud i Abijayil: “Ad ittwabarek SIDI, AREBBI n Israil, wenni cem dd-issekken ass-a i umsagar akidi!
\v 33 Aqa tᵉttwabarek řefhamet nnem uca tᵉttwabarked uřa d cem, řami d ayi tessbedded ass-a zeg usizzeř n idammen u zi nneqmet i yixef inu s ifassen inu!
\v 34 \add Maɣar\add* s tidett, am iddar SIDI, AREBBI n Israil, wenni d ayi issbedden ad am ggeɣ řɣar, mařa cem war ɣari dd-teffiɣed deɣya, xenni war ittɣimi ɣar tfawt n tuffut uřa d ijjen \add zeg iwdan\add* n Nabal, wenni t itteggen x řḥiḍ!”
\v 35 Uca iksi Dawud zeg ufus nnes min tuɣa i d as dd-tiwi, inna as: “Uyur di řehna ɣar taddart nnem! Xzar, necc sřiɣ-dd ɣarem u ad ssgeɛɛdeɣ udem nnem \add iḥeznen\add*.” \f ◼ \fr 25:35 \fk sřiɣ-dd ɣarem\ft - s Tɛibranit ‘sřiɣ i tmijja nnem’.\f*
\b
\m 
\v 36 \add Umi\add* dd-tusa Abijayil ɣar Nabal, ittegg netta ict n zzardet n tissit di taddart nnes am yict n zzardet n ujeǧid. Uř n Nabal tuɣa-t x řxaḍar nnes, iscar ař ṭṭarf. S uyenni nettat war d as tenni uřa d ijj n wawař, ameẓyan niɣ ameqqran, x min imsaren ař tafawt n tuffut.
\v 37 Ɣar tuffut, řami iffeɣ binu x Nabal, imsar, aqa tamɣart nnes tenna as man aya. Uca ijmed wuř nnes, idweř am yijj n weẓru.
\v 38 Awarni ɛecra n wussan, imsar, aqa SIDI iwta Nabal ařami immut.
\m 
\v 39 Umi isřa Dawud belli Nabal immut, inna netta: “Ad ittwabarek SIDI wenni iggin řḥukm x řḥegra i d ayi ittwaggen, ittar i-t zeg ufus n Nabal, uca issbedd amsexxar nnes ḥima ad igg řɣar. SIDI yarra řɣar n Nabal ad dd-idweř x uzeǧif nnes!” Uca Dawud issekk \add ijj\add* u wanita issiweř ak-d Abijayil, ḥima ad tt yawi d tamɣart i netta.
\b
\m 
\v 40 \add Umi\add* dd-usin imsexxaren n Dawud ɣar Abijayil ɣar Karmil, ssiwřen akides, nnan: “Dawud issekk aneɣ-dd ɣarem, ḥima ad cem nawi d tamɣart i netta.”
\v 41 \add Řexdenni\add* tekkar, tbendeq s uɣembub nnes ɣar temmurt, tenna: “Xzar, tamsexxart nnec am yict n tayya, ḥima ad tessird iḍaren i imsexxaren n sidi inu.”
\v 42 Tqeǧeq Abijayil, tekkar. Nettat tenya x weɣyuř nnes ak-d xemsa n temsexxarin nnes timeẓaynin tinni tt yareddfen x iḍaren. Nettat teḍfar ireqqasen n Dawud uca tedweř d tamɣart nnes.
\m 
\v 43 Yiwi Dawud ɛawed Axinuɛam zi Yazraɛil \add d tamɣart\add*. Nitenti s tnayen idsent dewřent d tamɣart i netta.
\v 44 Cawul maca tuɣa iwca yeǧis Mixal, tamɣart n Dawud, i Palti, mmis n Layic wenni \add iǧan\add* zi Jallim. \x ◘ \xo 25:44 \xt 2 Ṣm. 3:15\x*
\b
\b
\c 26
\s1 Dawud issɛizz x tudart n Cawul i twařa wiss tnayen
\m 
\v 1 Iryazen n Zif usin-dd ɣar Cawul ɣar Jibɛa, nnan: “Ma war issnuffar Dawud ixef nnes x tewrirt n Ḥaxila arendad n tnezruft?”
\v 2 \add Xenni\add* ikkar Cawul uca ihwa ɣar řexřa n Zif, akides teřt-ařaf n yeryazen ittwafarzen zi Israil, ḥima ad yarzu x Dawud di řexřa n Zif.
\v 3 Iwta Cawul iqiḍan nnes ɣar webrid x tewrirt n Ḥaxila tenni arendad n tnezruft. Dawud iqqim di řexřa, iẓra Cawul iḍfar i-t-i-dd ɣar řexřa.
\v 4 \add Maɣar\add* Dawud tuɣa issekk ixbarjiyyen u netta tuɣa issen aqa Cawul igga ad dd-yas.
\v 5 Dawud ikkar u yusa-dd mani tuɣa iwta Cawul iqiḍan nnes. Dawud tuɣa ittwařa mani tuɣa izzeř Cawul ak-d ukumandar n řɛeskar nnes, Abnir, mmis n Nir. Cawul iṭṭeṣ di řmargeḥ n ikarruten u řgens tuɣa inneḍ as-dd \add s iqiḍan nsen\add*.
\v 6 \add Xenni\add* iṭṭef Dawud deg wawař. Issiweř ak-d Aximalik, Aḥitti, u ak-d Abicay, mmis n Ṣiruya, umas n Yuwab, inna: “Man wen akidi i ɣa ihwan ɣar Cawul di řmargeḥ n řɛeskar?” Abicay inna: “Necc ad kidek hwiɣ.”
\m 
\v 7 Yusa-dd Dawud ak-d Abicay di ǧiřet ɣar řgens, u xzar, Cawul tuɣa iṭṭeṣ di řmargeḥ n ikarruten u lansa nnes tejju zzat i uzeǧif nnes di temmurt. Innḍen as-dd Abnir d řgens.
\v 8 \add Xenni\add* inna Abicay i Dawud: “Ass-a iqqen SIDI řeɛdu nnec deg ufus nnec. Ejj ayi řexxu ad t ssnuqqbeɣ ak-d temmurt s ict n tecti n lansa. War tteḥdijiɣ ad tt ggeɣ ict n twařa nneɣnit.”
\v 9 Dawud inna i Abicay: “War t ttareddeǧ ca, maɣar man wen izemmaren ad yarr afus nnes ɣar umedhun n SIDI uca ad iqqim d afurri?”
\v 10 \add Xenni\add* inna Dawud: “\add S tidett am\add* iddar SIDI, SIDI ad t iwwet: niɣ ad dd-yas wass nnes i di i ɣa immet niɣ ad dd-ihwa ɣar umenɣi uca ad ittwaneɣ.
\v 11 SIDI ad ayi iḥḍa aqa necc ad wteɣ s ufus inu amedhun n SIDI. Ttzawgeɣ cek, ksi lansa i \add iǧan\add* zzat i uzeǧif nnes d tebriqt n waman uca ejj aneɣ ad nuyur!”
\v 12 Iksi Dawud lansa d tebriqt n waman \add i tuɣa din iǧan\add* zzat i uzeǧif n Cawul uca ffɣen nitni. Uřa d ijj war \add t\add* iẓri, řa d ijj war \add t\add* yuci u uřa d ijj war ifiq, maɣar marra ṭṭṣen, minzi SIDI tuɣa isseɣḍes i-ten deg ijj n yiḍeṣ yuǧeɣ.
\v 13 Dawud iɛdu ɣar uɣezdis nneɣni uca ibedd ɣar řaggʷaj x tqiccat n wedrar. Tuɣa iǧa ttasiɛ d ameqqran jar asen.
\v 14 Iřaɣa-dd Dawud i řgens u i Abnir, mmis n Nir, inna: “Ma war dd-tarrid ca, Abnir?” \add Xenni\add* yarra-dd Abnir, inna: “Min teɛnid cek wenni d ittřaɣan x ujeǧid?”
\v 15 \add Xenni\add* inna Dawud i Abnir: “Ma cek war teǧid d aryaz? Man wen di Israil i iǧan am cek? Mayemmi \add xenni\add* war teḥḍid x sidi nnec, ajeǧid? Aqa ijjen zi řgens yudef-dd ḥima ad yareddeǧ ajeǧid, sidi nnec.
\v 16 Min teggid war iǧi ca mliḥ. \add S tidett am\add* iddar SIDI, kenniw d tarwa n řmewt, minzi kenniw war tɛessem x sidi nwem, amedhun n SIDI! Xzar mani ǧant řexxu lansa n ujeǧid d tebriqt n waman tinni tuɣa zzat i uzeǧif nnes!”
\m 
\v 17 Cawul iɛqeř tmijja n Dawud, inna: “Ma ta d tmijja nnec, a mmi Dawud?” Dawud inna: “Aqa-tt d tmijja inu, sidi inu, ajeǧid!”
\v 18 \add Xenni\add* inna: “Mayemmi iḍeffar sidi inu amsexxar nnes ammu? Minzi min ggiɣ u man \add t\add* řɛib i \add yumsen\add* ɣar ufus inu?
\v 19 Xenni řexxu, ejj ad iseř sidi inu, ajeǧid, i wawařen n umsexxar nnes. Mařa SIDI issehweř i cek xafi, iři ad icemm Netta tawhibt \add n řɣiǧet\add*, maca mařa d iwdan \add i iǧan\add*, \add xenni\add* ad ttwaneɛřen nitni zzat i wudem n SIDI, maɣar nitni uẓẓřen xafi ass-a ařami war zemmareɣ ad qqimeɣ qqneɣ \add ɛad\add* i řwart n SIDI, u \add maɣar\add* nitni qqaren: ‘Ruh, sexxar i irebbiten inneɣni!’
\v 20 \add Xenni\add* řexxu, ejj idammen inu war ttizzřen deg ict n temmurt iggʷejen x SIDI. Minzi ajeǧid n Israil iffeɣ, ḥima ad yarzu x ijj n uyenni n ucurdu waha, am mammec yemmaren tasekkurt deg idurar.” \x ◘ \xo 26:20 \xt 1 Ṣm. 24:15\x*
\m 
\v 21 \add Xas\add* uca inna Cawul: “Necc xḍiɣ, ɛqeb-dd, \add a\add* mmi Dawud, maɣar necc war d ac tteggeɣ ɛad řɣar, minzi tudart inu tuɣa ass-a tsekkwa ɣarek di tiṭṭawin nnec. Xzar, necc ggiɣ tubbuheřya u weddareɣ s waṭṭas.” \f ◼ \fr 26:21 \fk tudart inu\ft - s Tɛibranit ‘řeɛmar inu’.\f*
\v 22 Dawud yarra-dd, inna: “Xzar, aqa da lansa n ujeǧid. Ejj ijj zeg imsexxaren nnec ad iẓwa, ad tt-i-dd yawi.
\v 23 Ad ixeǧeṣ SIDI kuř ijj x tsegda nnes d ttiqqet nnes, minzi SIDI tuɣa isellem i cek ass-a deg ufus inu, maca war xseɣ ca ad ggeɣ afus inu deg umedhun n SIDI.
\v 24 Xzar, am mammec tuɣa tudart nnec ass-a tiɣřa di tiṭṭawin inu, ammu i ɣa tiři tudart inu di tiṭṭawin n SIDI tiɣřa. Netta ad ayi ifekk zi marra řeḥṣaret.” \f ◼ \fr 26:24 \fk tudart\ft - s Tɛibranit ‘řeɛmar’.\f*
\v 25 Cawul inna i Dawud: “Aqa cek tᵉttwabarked, mmi Dawud. Min ma i ɣa tegged, aqa ad tawḍed ɛawed.” \add Xenni\add* yuyur Dawud abrid nnes u Cawul iɛqeb ɣar wemcan nnes \add mani tuɣa izeddeɣ\add*.
\b
\b
\c 27
\s1 Dawud di temmurt n Ifilisṭiniyyen
\m 
\v 1 Inna Dawud deg wuř nnes: “Řexxu ɛad ijj n wass uca ad ttwanɣeɣ x ufus n Cawul. War iqqim ḥaca ad arewřeɣ deɣya ɣar temmurt n Ifilisṭiniyyen, maḥend ad iqḍeɛ i Cawul řayas zi jjihet inu maḥend ad xafi yarzu ɛad \add ktar\add* di marra tammurt n Israil. \add Ammu\add* i ɣa nejmeɣ i ufus nnes.”
\v 2 Dawud ikkar, netta d setta-mya n yeryazen nni tuɣa ɣares iǧan, ɛdun ɣar mmis n Maɛuk, ajeǧid n Jat.
\v 3 Iqqim Dawud ɣar Axis, netta d yeryazen nnes, \add kuř\add* aryaz ak-d taddart nnes. Dawud \add izdeɣ din\add* ak-d tnayen n temɣarin nnes, Axinuɛam zi Yazraɛil u Abijayil, tamɣart n Nabal, zi Karmil.
\v 4 \add Umi\add* nnan i Cawul, aqa Dawud yarweř ɣar Jat, war yarni iqqim ad xas yarzu ɛad ktar.
\m 
\v 5 Inna Dawud i Axic: “Mařa ufiɣ necc řxaḍar di tiṭṭawin nnec, xenni ewc ayi ijj n wemcan deg ict zi tneddam nnec n temmurt, ḥima zemmareɣ ad zedɣeɣ din. Mayemmi i ɣarek i ɣa izdeɣ umsexxar nnec akidek di tendint n ujeǧid?”
\v 6 Deg wass nni iwca as Axic \add tandint n\add* Ṣiqlaɣ. S uya tuɣa teǧa Ṣiqlaɣ n ijeǧiden n Yahuda ař ass-a.
\v 7 Ussan i ikka Dawud di temmurt n Ifilisṭiniyyen, tuɣa d ijj n useggʷas d arebɛa n iyuren.
\m 
\v 8 Dawud iffeɣ ak-d iryazen nnes u nitni keccḍen Ijacuriyyen d Ijarziyyen d ayt n Ɛamaliq, minzi ina tuɣa zeddɣen zeg wecḥař uya di temmurt, jjihet n Cur ař tammurt n Miṣra.
\v 9 Dawud iwta tammurt u war ijji ad iddar uřa d ijj n weryaz niɣ uřa d ict n temɣart. Iṭṭef ɛawed uǧi d ifunasen d tfunasin d yeɣyař d iřeɣman d warruḍ uca iɛqeb, yusa-dd ɣar Axic.
\v 10 U Axic inna: “Mani truḥem ass-a maḥend ad tkeccḍem?” Inna Dawud: “Ɣar ljanub n Yahuda!”, niɣ: “Ɣar ljanub n \add temmurt n\add* Iyarḥamitiliyyen!”, niɣ: “Ɣar ljanub n \add temmurt n\add* Iqiniyyen!”
\v 11 War ijji Dawud ad iddar uřa d ijj n weryaz niɣ uřa d ict n temɣart ḥima ad dd-yas ɣar Jat. Inna: “Ḥima nitni war xaneɣ ttɛiwiden walu, ad inin: ‘Ta i igga Dawud!’” Ammu i iqqim ittegg di marra ussan i ikka di jjwayeh n Ifilisṭiniyyen.
\v 12 Axic ittiqq di Dawud, inna: “S tidett netta issarzeg ixef nnes ɣar řgens nnes, ɣar Israil, uca x uyenni aqa netta ad yiři d amsexxar inu i řebda.”
\b
\b
\c 28
\s1 Cawul iruḥ ɣar ict n temɣart di Ɛayn-Dur
\m 
\v 1 Deg wussan nni, řami ssmunen Ifilisṭiniyyen řɛeskar nsen i umenɣi, ḥima ad mmenɣen ak-d Israil, imsar, aqa Axic inna i Dawud: “Ittxeṣṣa ad tessned mliḥ, aqa cek ad kidi teffɣed s uɣiř di řɛeskar, cek d yeryazen nnec.”
\v 2 \add Xenni\add* inna Dawud i Axic: “Di man aya ad tẓared min izemmar ad yegg umsexxar nnec!” Axic inna i Dawud: “S uya ad cek ggeɣ d aɛessas xafi di marra ussan.” \f ◼ \fr 28:2 \fk aɛessas xafi\ft - s Tɛibranit ‘aɛessas i uzeǧif inu’.\f*
\m 
\v 3 Camwil tuɣa immut d marra Israil tuɣa icḍen xas. Nitni neḍřen t di Rama, di tendint nnes. Cawul tuɣa issuffuɣ inni issawařen ak-d imettan uřa d igezzanen zi temmurt. \x ◘ \xo 28:3 \xt 1 Ṣm. 25:1\x*
\m 
\v 4 Ifilisṭiniyyen munen marra. Nitni usin-dd uca wtin iqiḍan nsen ɣar Cunam u Cawul issmun marra Israil u nitni wtin iqiḍan nsen ɣar Jilbuɛa.
\v 5 Umi iẓra Cawul řmargeḥ n řɛeskar n Ifilisṭiniyyen, tusa as-dd tiggʷudi u wuř nnes idweř itteqdiddis s waṭṭas.
\v 6 Cawul isseqsa SIDI, maca SIDI war xas dd-yarri ca, war iǧi s tirja, uřa s Urim, uřa s inabiyyen.
\v 7 \add Xenni\add* inna Cawul i imsexxaren nnes: “Arzum ayi-dd ict n temɣart iddebbaran x buḥbeřat n imettan, ḥima necc ad ɣares raḥeɣ u ad tt sseqsiɣ.” Imsexxaren nnes nnan as: “Xzar, di Ɛayn-Dur aqa din ict n temɣart tenni iddebbaran x buḥbeřat n imettan.”
\v 8 Cawul issneqřeb ixef nnes, yarḍ arruḍ nneɣni uca yuyur. Tnayen n yeryazen ruḥen akides u nitni iwḍen di ǧiřet ɣar temɣart, uca inna netta: “Gezzen ayi zi buḥbeř n ijj n umettin uca řaɣa ayi-dd x wenni d am i ɣa iniɣ.”
\v 9 \add Xenni\add* tenna xas temɣart: “Aqa da cek tessned \add mliḥ\add* min igga Cawul, mammec tuɣa itteḥḥa inni issawařen ak-d imettan d igezzanen zi temmurt. Mayemmi d ayi tᵉttegged řfex, ḥima ad ayi tenɣed?”
\v 10 Cawul \add maca\add* ijjuǧ as ɣar SIDI, inna: “\add S tidett am\add* iddar SIDI, war cem iřeqqef di tmesřact-a ca řɛib!”
\v 11 \add Xenni\add* tenna temɣart: “Man wen i xef-dd i ɣa řaɣiɣ i cek?” Netta inna “Řaɣa ayi-dd x Camwil!”
\v 12 \add Umi\add* teẓra temɣart Camwil, tesɣuy deg ujenna u tessiweř temɣart ak-d Cawul, tenna as: “Mayemmi d ayi tcemted? Cek aqa d Cawul!”
\v 13 Inna as ujeǧid: “War tteggʷed ca, maca min tᵉttwařid cem?” \add Xenni\add* tenna temɣart i Cawul: “Necc ttwařiɣ inni yarewsen deg irebbiten i dd-ittgeɛɛaden zi temmurt.”
\v 14 Netta inna as: “Mammec tegga tiddi nnes?” Nettat tenna: “Ijj n uwessar ittgeɛɛed u yarḍ s yijj n useřham.” \add Xenni\add* issen Cawul, aqa-t d Camwil, yuḍar netta s uɣembub nnes ɣar temmurt uca ibendeq.
\m 
\v 15 Uca Camwil inna: “Mayemmi d ayi thewřed, tejjid ad xafi dd-řaɣan?” Cawul inna: “Necc ttwaḥṣareɣ aṭṭas, maɣar Ifilisṭiniyyen ttmenɣan akidi u AREBBI iḥeyyed xafi u war iqqim ittarra-dd xafi ɛad, war iǧi x tebridin n inabiyyen uřa s tirja. S uyenni řaɣiɣ-dd xak, maḥend ad ayi tessecned min ɣa ggeɣ.”
\v 16 \add Xenni\add* inna Camwil: “Mayemmi d ayi tᵉttseqsid, \add mařa\add* SIDI iḥeyyed xak u Netta idweř ḍidd nnec?
\v 17 SIDI simant nnes igga am mammec tuɣa zzayi inna u netta iqřeɛ i cek tageldit zeg ufus nnec, iwca i-tt i jjar nnec, i Dawud.
\v 18 Minzi cek war tesřid ca ɣar tmijja n SIDI u cek war tessiwḍed ca řḥaduq n weɣḍab nnes ɣar Ɛamaliq, x uya i d ac igga SIDI ass-a aya.
\v 19 SIDI ad kidek igg uřa d Israil deg ufus n Ifilisṭiniyyen, u tiwecca ad tiřid cek d iḥenjiren nnec ɣari. Uřa d řɛeskar n Israil ad t igg SIDI deg ufus n Ifilisṭiniyyen.”
\v 20 \add Xenni\add* iwḍa Cawul deɣya, ibeqqeḍ di temmurt, tuɣa itteggʷed aṭṭas zeg wawařen n Camwil, uca jjehd war dayes iqqim, minzi war icci aɣrum, ass d ǧiřet kemmřen.
\m 
\v 21 Tamɣart tuyur ɣar Cawul, uca teẓra i-t yarjef aṭṭas. Tenna as: “Xzar, tayya nnec tesřa ɣar tmijja nnec u necc sebbřeɣ tudart inu, sřiɣ ɣar wawařen i d ayi tennid.
\v 22 Xenni řexxu maca seř ɣar tmijja n tayya nnec! Necc ad ac qeddmeɣ ijj n uřeqqim n weɣrum. Ecc ḥima ad tᵉttwassjheded xmi ɣa tᵉṭṭfed abrid.”
\v 23 \add Maca\add* netta yugi, inna: “Necc war ttᵉtteɣ!” \add Maca\add* imsexxaren nnes uřa d tamɣart ḥṣaren t ařami isřa netta ɣarsen, uca netta ikkar zi temmurt, iqqim x qama. \f ◼ \fr 28:23 \fk ɣarsen\ft - s Tɛibranit ‘ɣar tmijja nsen’.\f*
\v 24 Tamɣart tuɣa ɣares ijj n uɛejmi imseř di taddart uca tɣarṣ as deɣya. Nettat teksi awren, teggʷa arecti u tegga zzayes aɣrum břa antun.\f ◼ \fr 28:24 \fk aɛejmi\ft - niɣ ‘amwa’, ‘ayenduz’ niɣ ‘yuggu’.\f*
\v 25 Nettat tqeddem \add aya\add* i Cawul d imsexxaren nnes uca ccin nitni. Awarni aya kkaren u areggʷḥen di ǧiřet nni.
\b
\b
\c 29
\s1 Dawud d řbacat n Ifilisṭiniyyen
\m 
\v 1 Ifilisṭiniyyen ssmunen marra řɛeskar nsen ɣar Afiq uca Israil tuɣa iwta iqiḍan nnes ɣar tařa nni \add iǧan\add* ɣar Yazraɛil.
\v 2 Uca řbacat \add n tneddam\add* n Ifilisṭiniyyen ẓwan ɣar din s řmyawat d řuřuf nsen uca iẓwa Dawud d yeryazen nnes ak-d Axic ɣar uɣezdis aneggaru.
\v 3 \add Xenni\add* nnan řḥukkam n Ifilisṭiniyyen: “Min da tteggen Iɛibraniyyen-a?” Yarra-dd Axic x řḥukkam n Ifilisṭiniyyen: “Ma wa war iǧi d Dawud, amsexxar n Cawul, ajeǧid n Israil, wenni tuɣa ɣari iǧan aseggʷas d wass? Zeg wass i ɣari dd-yeɛdu ař ass-a necc war dayes ufiɣ uřa d ijj n řɛib.”
\m 
\v 4 Ffuggmen xas aṭṭas řḥukkam n Ifilisṭiniyyen. Nnan as řḥukkam n Ifilisṭiniyyen: “Sekk aryaz ad iɛqeb, ḥima ad idweř ɣar wemcan nnes nni i d as tessecned. War izemmar akidneɣ ihwa ɣar umenɣi, ḥima xenni war iddikkwiř d řeɛdu nneɣ deg umenɣi. Maɣar s minzi izemmar wanita ad iṣřeḥ ak-d sidis nnes? Ma war iǧi ak-d izeǧifen n yeryazen-a? \x ◘ \xo 29:4 \xt 1 Im. 12:20\x*
\v 5 Ma wanita war iǧi d Dawud wenni x ɣennjent d ceḍḥent s nnubtat, nnant: ‘Cawul netta iɣřeb x řuřuf nnes, \add maca\add* Dawud netta x ɛecra n řuřuf nnes?’” \x ◘ \xo 29:5 \xt 1 Ṣm. 18:7\x*
\m 
\v 6 Uca iřaɣa-dd Axic i Dawud inna as: “\add S tidett am\add* iddar SIDI, cek d aṣdiq. Ufuɣ nnec d weɛqab nnec akidi di řɛeskar aqa aten mliḥ di tiṭṭawin inu, maɣar necc war dayek ufiɣ uřa d ca n řɣecc zeg wass i ɣari dd-tusid ař ass-a. \add Maca\add* cek war teǧid mliḥ di tiṭṭawin n řbacat \add n tneddam\add*.
\v 7 Xenni řexxu, ɛqeb, uyur di řehna, \add ḥima\add* war tᵉttegged qaɛ ca n řɣecc di tiṭṭawin n řbacat \add n tneddam\add* n Ifilisṭiniyyen.”
\v 8 \add Xenni\add* inna Dawud i Axic: “Maɣar min ggiɣ? Min tufid deg umsexxar nnec zeg wass \add amezwaru\add* i d ayi tuɣa zzat i wudem nnec ař ass-a, ařami war ruḥeɣ akidwem ad menɣeɣ ak-d řɛedyan n sidi inu, ajeǧid?”
\v 9 Axic yarra-dd, inna i Dawud: “Necc ssneɣ tt, minzi cek d lemliḥ di tiṭṭawin inu am yijj n lmalak n AREBBI, maca řḥukkam n Ifilisṭiniyyen nnan: ‘Netta war akidneɣ itteffeɣ ɣar umenɣi.’
\v 10 S uyenni kkar tiwecca zic s imsexxaren n sidi nnec, inni akidek dd-yusin. Mařa tekkarem s wass zic uca iṣbeḥ řḥař, ffɣem \add xenni\add*.”
\v 11 Dawud ikkar zic, netta d yeryazen nnes, ḥima ad uyuren di ṣṣbeḥ, ad dd-ɛeqben ɣar temmurt n Ifilisṭiniyyen. Ifilisṭiniyyen \add maca\add* ffɣen, geɛɛden ɣar Yazraɛil.
\b
\b
\c 30
\s1 Dawud intaqem zeg Iɛamaliqiyyen
\m 
\v 1 \add Umi\add* dd-yusa Dawud d yeryazen nnes ɣar Ṣiqlaɣ deg wass wiss třata, tuɣa imsar, aqa ayt n Ɛamaliq keccḍen ljanub uřa d Ṣiqlaɣ. Nitni wtin Ṣiqlaɣ, qqden as timessi
\v 2 uca ḥebbsen timɣarin nni din \add iǧan\add*. War nɣin uřa d ijj, ameẓyan niɣ d ameqqran, maca iwyen ten uca uyuren abrid nsen.
\v 3 Yusa-dd Dawud ak-d yeryazen nnes ɣar tendint, uca xzar, aqa tᵉttwassecmeḍ \add tendint\add* s tmessi u timɣarin d iḥenjiren d tḥenjirin tuɣa ttwaḥewwsen.
\v 4 Dawud d řgens i ɣares \add iǧan\add* ssgeɛɛden tmijja nsen, sɣuyen ařami war daysen iqqim jjehd ḥima ad sɣuyen.
\v 5 Uřa d tnayen n temɣarin n Dawud ttwaḥewwsent, Axinuɛam zi Yazraɛil u Abijayil zi Karmil.
\v 6 Tuɣa Dawud tᵉttwaḥṣared aṭṭas, minzi řgens tuɣa issawař maḥend ad t arejmen, maɣar řeɛmur n marra řgens tuɣa arezgen, \add kuř\add* aryaz x \add txessart\add* n iḥenjiren nnes d tḥenjirin nnes. \add Maca\add* Dawud issejhed ixef nnes di SIDI, AREBBI nnes.
\m 
\v 7 Inna Dawud i ukehhan Abyatar, mmis n Aximalik: “Awi-dd \add da\add* ɣari apalṭu \add n ukehhan\add*!” U Abyatar yiwi-dd apalṭu \add n ukehhan\add* ɣar Dawud.
\v 8 \add Xenni\add* isseqsa Dawud i SIDI: “Ma ad ḍfareɣ bandiyya-ya? Ma ad xasen ḥarteɣ?” SIDI yarra-dd xas: “Ḍfar i-ten, maɣar cek ad xasen tḥarted u ad tfekked \add imeḥbas\add* nican.”
\v 9 Iffeɣ-dd Dawud, netta d setta-mya n yeryazen nni tuɣa ɣares. \add Umi\add* dd-iwḍen nitni ař tiɣzart n Basur, bedden \add din\add* inni iqqimen ɣar ḍeffar,
\v 10 \add maca\add* Dawud iqqim iḍeffar \add bandiyya nni\add*, netta d arebɛa-mya n yeryazen akides. Mitayn n yeryazen, inni tuɣa yuḥřen aṭṭas maḥend ad ẓwan tiɣzart n Bacur, qqimen bedden \add din\add*.
\m 
\v 11 Nitni ufin ijj n weryaz d Amiṣri deg iyyar uca iwyen t ɣar Dawud. Nitni wcin as aɣrum u netta icca u nitni wcin as \add ɛawed\add* aman maḥend ad isu.
\v 12 Arnin as ict n tesɣart n ijj n weɣrum n tazart yuẓɣen d tnayen n iɣrumen n zzbib u netta icca, idweř as-dd buḥbeř nnes, maɣar netta tuɣa war icci war iswi třata n wussan d třata n ǧiyaři.
\v 13 \add Xenni\add* inna as Dawud: “Wi cek yiřan u manis cek?” \add Xenni\add* inna uḥudri Amiṣri: “Necc d ijj n umsexxar n ijj n weryaz n Ɛamaliq u sidi inu ijja ayi, řami heřceɣ třata n wussan zeg wami.
\v 14 Neccin tuɣa nkecceḍ \add tammurt n\add* ljanub n Ikaritiyyin, tenni ɣar Yahuda, uřa d \add tammurt n\add* ljanub n Kalib, u neccin nessecmeḍ Ṣiqlaɣ s tmessi.”
\v 15 Dawud inna as: “Ma tzemmared ad ayi tnedhed ɣar bandiyya-ya n ixewwanen?” Netta inna: “Jaǧ ayi ɣar AREBBI, aqa cek war d ayi tneqqed u war d ayi tessɛeddud i sidi inu! Xenni necc ad cek nedheɣ ɣar bandiyya-ya.”
\v 16 Uca indeh i-t din, u xzar, nitni tuɣa qqimen ttwabezzɛen x marra tammurt, ccin, swin u ceḍḥen zi ssibbet n tkeccaḍt tameqqrant i tuɣa dd-iwyen zi temmurt n Ifilisṭiniyyen u zi temmurt n Yahuda.
\m 
\v 17 Dawud iwta xasen zi tbambast ař tameddit n wass i-tt-i-dd-iḍfaren uca uřa d ijjen zzaysen war injim, mɣir arebɛa-mya n iḥudriyyen nni inyin x iřeɣman, arewřen.
\v 18 \add Ammu\add* dd-ifekk Dawud marra min kksen ayt n Ɛamaliq. Dawud ifekk-dd uřa d tnayen n temɣarin nnes.
\v 19 Zeg umeẓyan ař ameqqran, zeg iḥenjiren d tḥenjirin, zi tkeccaḍt u zi marra min zzaysen kksen, war iweddar walu. Marra yarra i-t-i-dd Dawud.
\v 20 Iksi Dawud ɛawed marra uǧi d ifunasen d tfunasin. Nedhen \add ten\add* ɣar zzat i řeksibet \add n yixef\add* nsen, nnan: “Ta d takeccaḍt n Dawud.”
\m 
\v 21 \add Umi\add* dd-yiweḍ Dawud ɣar mitayen n yeryazen, inni tuɣa yuḥřen aṭṭas ḥima ad ḍfaren Dawud \add ɛad\add*, inni ijja Dawud ɣar teɣzart n Bacur, aqa ffɣen-dd nitni ɣar umsagar ak-d Dawud u ak-d řgens nni tuɣa ɣares. Dawud iqarreb-dd ɣarsen uca isseqsa x umeddur nsen.
\v 22 \add Xenni\add* yarra-dd kuř aryaz war iḥřin d wenni war isekkwin jar yeryazen nni tuɣa dd-iffɣen ak-d Dawud, nnan: “Maɣar nitni war kidneɣ ffiɣen, x uyenni war d asen nᵉttic walu zi tkeccaḍt i dd-nfekk, mɣir i \add kuř\add* aryaz tamɣart nnes d iḥenjiren nnes. D ina zemmaren nitni ad awyen uca ad \add kidsen\add* areggʷḥen.”
\v 23 \add Maca\add* Dawud inna: “War iɛeddeř ad teggem amenni, aytma, aqa SIDI d wenni d aneɣ iwcin \add aya\add* u Netta iḥḍa aneɣ u iwca bandiyya i d aneɣ dd-iwḍan deg ufus nneɣ.
\v 24 Wi ɣarwem i ɣa isřen ɣar wawař nwem? Maɣar tasɣart n wenni iffɣen ɣar umenɣi \add ad tiři\add* am tesɣart n wenni iqqimen ɣar řexzin. Nitni ad \add tt\add* bḍan \add jmiɛ\add*.”
\v 25 Ammu i tt teqqim zeg wass nni, minzi netta igga i-tt d ict n tewṣeyyet d ict n lfariḍa di Israil ař ass-a.
\b
\s1 Dawud issekk tirzefin i imɣaren n Yahuda
\m 
\v 26 \add Umi\add* yareggʷeḥ Dawud ɣar Ṣiqlaɣ, issekk netta \add tirzefin\add* zi tkeccaḍt ɣar imɣaren n Yahuda, imeddukkař nnes, \add am i d asen\add* inna: “Ta d ict n lbaraka i kenniw zi tkeccaḍt n řɛedyan n SIDI”.
\v 27 Issekk \add i imɣaren\add* di Bayt-Il, i yinni di Ramat di ljanub, i yinni di Yattir,
\v 28 i yinni di Ɛaruɛir, i yinni di Sifmut, i yinni di Icitimuɛa,
\v 29 i yinni di Raxil, i yinni \add tuɣa izeddɣen\add* di tneddam n Iyarḥamtiliyyen, i yinni \add izeddɣen\add* di tneddam n Iqiniyyen,
\v 30 i yinni di Ḥurma, i yinni di Kur-Ɛacan, i yinni di Ɛatak,
\v 31 i yinni di Ḥabrun u ɣar marra imucan mani tuɣa ikka Dawud, netta ak-d iryazen nnes.
\b
\b
\c 31
\s1 Řmewt n Cawul
\m 
\v 1 Mmenɣen Ifilisṭiniyyen ak-d Israil. Iryazen n Israil arewřen zzat i wudem n Ifilisṭiniyyen uca wḍan d imettan x temmurt n idurar n Jilbuɛa. \x ◘ \xo 31:1 \xt [1 Im. 10:1-12]\x*
\v 2 Ifilisṭiniyyen ḍfaren Cawul d arraw nnes břa qeṭṭu uca Ifilisṭiniyyen nɣin Yunatan d Abinadab d Malkicuɛa, arraw n Cawul.
\v 3 Idweř umenɣi ak-d Cawul iwɛar. Imjebbaden, iryazen s řqews, ufin t u netta tuɣa itteggʷed aṭṭas zeg imjebbaden \add n řqews\add*.
\m 
\v 4 \add Xenni\add* inna Cawul i uḥemmař n řesnaḥ nnes: “Suffeɣ-dd ssif nnec, snuqqeb ayi zzayes! Niɣ ad taɣ ad dd-asen inni war ittwaxetnen, maḥend ad ayi ssnuqqben u ad zzayi stehzan.” \add Maca\add* aḥemmař n řesnaḥ nnes war ixs \add ad tt igg\add*, maɣar netta tuɣa iggʷed aṭṭas. \add Xenni\add* iksi Cawul ssif uca ijja ixef nnes ad xas iwḍa.
\v 5 Umi aḥemmař n řesnaḥ iẓra, aqa Cawul immut, igga uřa d netta ad iwḍa s yixef nnes x ssif nnes uca immut akides.
\v 6 Ammu i immut Cawul deg wass nni, \add imun\add* ak-d třata n iḥenjiren nnes u ak-d uḥemmař n řesnaḥ nnes \add uřa ak-d\add* marra iryazen nnes.
\m 
\v 7 \add Umi\add* ẓrin yeryazen n Israil, inni tuɣa ɣar uɣezdis nneɣni n řewḍa n teɣzurt d inni tuɣa x ujemmaḍ n L’Urdun, aqa iryazen n Israil arewřen u aqa Cawul d třata n iḥenjiren nnes ttwanɣen, semḥen nitni di tneddam nsen uca arewřen. \add Řexdenni\add* usin-dd Ifilisṭiniyyen uca dewřen zeddɣen daysent.
\v 8 Tiwecca nnes, umi dd-usin Ifilisṭiniyyen, ḥima ad keccḍen inni ittwanɣen, imsar, aqa ufin Cawul d třata n iḥenjiren nnes, inni tuɣa iwḍan x wedrar n Jilbuɛa.
\v 9 Nitni qessen as azeǧif, ssarxun as řesnaḥ uca ssekken \add ireqqasen\add* di temmurt n Ifilisṭiniyyen, ḥima ad ssiwḍen řexbar aṣebḥan ɣar taddart n řexyařat n l’aṣnam nsen u jar řgens. \x ◘ \xo 31:9 \xt 1 Im. 10:9\x*
\v 10 Řesnaḥ n Cawul ssarsen t di taddart \add n zzawect\add* n ‘Ɛactarutin’, u řxecbet nnes uyřen tt ɣar řḥiḍ n Bayt-Can.
\m 
\v 11 \add Umi\add* imezdaɣ n Yabic-Jilɛad sřan min ggin Ifilisṭiniyyen di Cawul,
\v 12 kkaren marra iryazen imeḥḍen, uyuren ǧiřet tmun uca ksin řxecbet n Cawul d řxecbat n iḥenjiren nnes zi řḥiḍ n Bayt-Can uca iwḍen ɣar Yabic uca sscemḍen tent dinni.
\v 13 Xenni ksin iɣsan nsen, neḍřen ten sadu tacejjart n tmarist n Yabic uca ẓummen sebɛa n wussan. \f ◼ \fr 31:13 \fk tacejjart n tmarist\ft - s tlatinit ‘Tamarix’.\f* 
